\id JHN - Akoose 
\h Jɔnɛ 
\toc1 Nkalaŋ ḿ bwâm ḿme Yesuɛ ngáne Jɔnɛ átélé 
\toc2 Jɔnɛ 
\toc3 Jɔn 
\mt2 Nkalaŋ ḿ bwâm ḿme Yesuɛ ngáne 
\mt1 Jɔnɛ 
\mt3 átélé 
\imt1 Ndibned ń kálag 
\im Nkalaŋ ḿ bwâm ngáne Jɔnɛ átélé ńlûmte aá Yesuɛ adíi Eyale é Dyǒb éche édé á ngíndé ne á ngíndé. Échê Eyale êntǐm moonyoŋ édyɛ̄ɛ̄-ʼɛ átîntê e bad. Ḿmɛ́n nkalaŋ, Jɔnɛ atelé mɔ́ âbɛl bad ábe béláa mɔ́ bédúbe nɛ́n bán Yesuɛ, Mwǎn a Dyǒb mɔ́ adé Nsoodɛ awě Dyǒb dénhɔ̄bpē aá mɔ́ɔ̄lōm. Anlúméd-tɛ aá nzé bad bédúbpé mɔ́ bɛ́kǔd eʼsoósoŋ. 
\ip Á kálag tê wɛ́n á mbooted, Jɔnɛ alûmte ngáne baahɔ́g béndūbɛ̄ɛ̄ Yesuɛ békwɛntɛ́n-nɛ âhíd mɔ́, álūmtē-ʼɛ ngáne bémpēe-ʼɛ bétə́ŋgánnáá mɔ́, béekwɛntɛneʼ-ɛ mɔ́ adúbe. Eʼpɛd 13-17 éʼhɔ́be tə̂ŋgɛne abɛ́ áde Yesuɛ ne ábē bembapɛɛ bémbɛ̄ɛ̄ póndé esyəə́l kə́ə́ŋ ne epun éche békóbé mɔ́ ne mam ḿme ánlāāʼɛ́ bɔ́ ene póndé esyəə́l. Jɔnɛ ahɔ́bé ámpē aá nzé mod adúbpé Krǐstəə ǎkǔd aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ. 
\iot Nkabtéd ń kálag 
\io1 Ndibned \ior 1.1-18\ior* 
\io1 Jɔnɛ, Ndusɛnɛ ne bembapɛɛ béʼsō ábe Yesuɛ \ior 1.19-51\ior* 
\io1 Nsɔ́n ḿme Yesuɛ \ior 2.1-12.50\ior* 
\io1 Eʼpun bé asóg ábe Yesuɛ á Jerusalɛm ne bɛnbɛn ne Jerusalɛm \ior 13.1-19.42\ior* 
\io1 Mpuu ḿme Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́ ne alúmed áde álúmtáá bad yə̌l \ior 20.1-31\ior* 
\io1 Nsógtɛn: Yesuɛ alúmté yə̌l ámpē á Galilia \ior 21.1-25\ior* 
\c 1  
\s1 Eyale êntǐm moonyoŋ 
\p  
\v 1 Á mbooted, byánán Dyǒb dɛ́hə̌g nkǒŋsé Eyale êmmad abɛ́. Eyale émbɛ̄ ne Dyǒb. Échê Eyale ébédɛ́ɛ Dyǒb.  
\v 2 Kə́ə́ŋse á mbooted Eyale émbɛ̄ hǒm ahɔ́g ne Dyǒb.  
\v 3 Dyǒb dêmbɛnléd échê Eyale âhəg bwěm éʼsyə̄ə̄l. Chǒm ké ehɔ́g éesaá éche Dyǒb dênhəgké ésebɛ́ ne Eyale.  
\v 4 Aloŋgé ásyə̄ə̄l dénhūū ne Eyale, ádê aloŋgé dɔ́-ʼaá ápíínédé baányoŋ eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde.  
\v 5 Ábɛ̂ eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde éʼpɛneʼ á ehíntɛ́n-tê, ehíntɛ́n éēhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄ bɔ́ abɔ́ded.\f + \fr 1:5 \fq Ehíntɛ́n-nɛ éēhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄ bɔ́ abɔ́ded \ft káa \fq ehíntɛ́n énkênchemmé bɔ́.\f* 
\p  
\v 6 Mod nhɔ́g ampɛ̌ awě Dyǒb dénlōmmē. Dǐn démbɛ̄ mɔ́ bán Jɔnɛ.  
\v 7 Jɔnɛ ampɛ̌ âláa bad tə̂ŋgɛne ábê eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde, âbɛl nɛ́n bad bésyə̄ə̄l béwôg, bédúbe-ʼɛ.  
\v 8 Saké mwěn abédé ábê eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde. Ampɛ̌ âbíd mbóŋ tə̂ŋgɛne ábê eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde.  
\v 9 Eyale chɔ́ɔ ébédé eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde éʼ mbále ábe éʼnyînteʼ moonyoŋ asyəə́l ekíde. Mɔ́-ʼaá apagéʼáá á nkǒŋsé-te.  
\v 10 Abédé á nkǒŋsé-te, boŋ kénɛ́ɛ Dyǒb dênhəgké nkǒŋsé ne mɔ́, nkǒŋsé ménkênchemmé mɔ́.  
\v 11 Ampɛ̌ áwē dyad boŋ ábē bad bénkênkobpé mɔ́.  
\v 12 Ké nɛ̂, ambɛ̌ doŋge á bad kunze âbɛ́ bǎn bé Dyǒb. Ábé bad bébédɛ́ɛ bad ábe bênkob mɔ́ ne adúbe áde béndūbɛ̄ɛ̄ mɔ́.  
\v 13 Béesaá bǎn bé Dyǒb nyaa echě moonyoŋ áchyáaʼɛ́ mwǎn. Bénkêmbáá bǎn bé Dyǒb byánán moonyoŋ mɔ́ achyáá bɔ́. Dyǒb děn dɔ́ɔ ádé awâb Titɛ́ɛ. 
\p  
\v 14 Eyale êntǐm moonyoŋ, édyɛ̄ɛ̄ átîntê echɛ̂d. Anlón ne nsimé, anlúméd-tɛ syánē ngáne mbále e Dyǒb ékóó abɛ́. Dennyín échē ehúmé, ehúmé éche sáá ábágé mɔ́ nɛ́ɛ ḿmē mpɔm ḿ mwǎn.  
\v 15 Jɔnɛ anhɔ́b mam áyə̄l echê, anhə́ə́d aá, “Anɛ́n mod mɔ́ɔ ńláŋgéʼáá nyé mɛɛ́, ‘Mod ahúɛʼ ámbīd echêm awě atómé mɛ, áyə̄le bédɛ̂chyáá mɛ, né adé ámīn.’ ”  
\v 16 Alón áde álóné ne nsimé ábɛ́lé syáā moosyəə́l dekudé nnam ámbīd e nnam.  
\v 17 Wɛ́ɛ Mosɛɛ dɔ́ɔ Dyǒb dêmpoódté mbéndé. Boŋ nsimé ne mbále béhúú ne Yesu Krǐstəə.  
\v 18 Modmod eényīnɛ̄ɛ̄ Dyǒb mbêd, éetómɛɛ́ ḿmē mpɔm ḿ mwǎn awě adé Dyǒb abɛ́-ʼɛ mɔ́ á akéb. Mwěmpɛn mɔ́ akidényīn mɔ́. Mɔ́ abɛlé boŋ Titɛ̂ Dyǒbɛ abyɛ́ɛn. 
\s1 Jɔnɛ, Ndusɛnɛ ahɔ́bé aá  //  mɔ́ɔsaá Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté 
\r (Mat 3.1-12; Mak 1.1-8; Luk 3.1-18) 
\p  
\v 19 Baámbáá bé Israɛl bé dyad á Jerusalɛm bénlōm beprisɛ ne bad bémpēe bé túmbé e Levi wɛ́ɛ Jɔnɛ, bán békɛ bésɛded mɔ́ bánken nzɛ́-módɛ́ ádíí.  
\v 20 Enkêmbaŋgé ahɔ́b, boŋ ampanléd bɔ́ áte aá, “Saké mɛ ndé Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté.”  
\v 21 Hɛ́ɛ bésɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ bánken, “Nzé-ɔ̄ édíí? Wɛ-ɛɛ́ edé Elaijaa?” Ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Aáy, meésaá mɔ́.” Bênsɛdéd mɔ́ ámpē bánken, “Wɛ-ɛɛ́ edé nkal éʼdəə́dəŋ awe bésinɛɛ́-yɛ?” Antimtɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Aáy.”  
\v 22 Kə́ə́ŋne á asog dɔ́ɔ bésɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ bánken, “Nzé-ɔ̄ édíí? Láá sé âbɛl sétim ámbīd âláa bad ábe bélómé sé. Nzɛ́-módɛ́ wɛwɛ ehɔ́bé wɛɛ́ mɔ́dé?”  
\v 23 Hɛ́ɛ Jɔnɛ átimtanné bɔ́ ne eʼyale ábe nkal éʼdəə́dəŋ Yesayaa ánhɔ̄bpē aá, 
\q1 “Mɛ́ɛ ndé ehɔ́b éche mod awě ahə̂ŋteʼ á ehyáŋge aá, 
\q1 ‘Nyétíi nzii eche Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́.’ ” 
\m  
\v 24 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́ Befarisia bɔ́ɔ bénlōm ábê bad ábe bémpɛ̌ wɛ́ɛ Jɔnɛ.  
\v 25 Bênsɛdéd mɔ́ ámpē bánken, “Nzé weésɛ̌ Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté, weésɛ̌-ʼɛ Elaijaa káa Nkal éʼdəə́dəŋ awe bésinɛɛ́, cheé-ɔ̄ édusanné bad?”  
\v 26 Hɛ́ɛ Jɔnɛ átimtanné bɔ́ aá, “Ndusan ne mendíb, boŋ mod adé átîntê echɛ̂n awě nyéēbíiʼɛ́.  
\v 27 Mɔ́ adé ane awě ǎpɛ̌ ámbīd echêm. Meékwognedɛɛ́ âhune ké ḿmē nkɔɔd mé metámbé.” 
\p  
\v 28 Ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l mêmbɛnléd á dyad á Bɛtani á múde mé edíb é Jodan ḿmíníí wɛ́ɛ Jɔnɛ ádúsánnáá bad. 
\s1 Yesuɛ, Mwǎn-a-Ńdyɔŋ ḿ mbód a Dyǒb 
\p  
\v 29 Nɛ́ɛ bǐn éʼsáŋgé, Jɔnɛ anyín nɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ áhúɛʼɛ́ níníí. Hɛ́ɛ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “Nyénɔneʼ, Mwǎn-a-Ńdyɔŋ ḿ mbód a Dyǒb mɔ̂nɛ. Mɔ́ ahúdeʼ mbéb ḿ bad bé nkǒŋsé.  
\v 30 Anɛ́n mod mɔ́ɔ ńláŋgéʼáá nyé áde ménhɔ̄bpē mɛɛ́ ‘Mod ǎpɛ̌ ámbīd echêm awě atómé mɛ, áyə̄le bédɛ̂chyáá mɛ, né adé ámīn.’  
\v 31 Ké mměn menkêmbííʼɛ́ mɔ́, boŋ mempɛ̌ ńdusán bad ne mendíb âbɛl bad bé Israɛl bébíi mɔ́.”  
\v 32 Hɛ́ɛ Jɔnɛ ábídɛɛ́ mbóŋ nɛ́n aá, “Menyín nɛ̂ŋgáne Edəə́dəŋ é Dyǒb ébídé ádyōb nɛ́ɛ élə̄ə̄, ésud mɔ́ á nló mîn, ébɛ́-ʼɛ ne mɔ́.  
\v 33 Ké nɛ̂, menkênsóŋtɛ́nné mɛɛ́ mɔ̂ nɛ. Boŋ Dyǒb áde dénlōm mɛ aá ńdusan bad ne mendíb dêmmǎd mɛ aláa aá, ‘Mod awě wɛ́nyīnnē nɛ́ɛ edəə́dəŋ é Dyǒb ésúdé á nló mîn, boŋ étyéém áhed, mɔ́ɔ̄dusɛ́n bad ne Edəə́dəŋ éche Ésáá.’  
\v 34 Nnyíné ḿmɛ́n mekan mésyə̄ə̄l, mbíde-ʼɛ mbóŋ nɛ́n mɛɛ́ mɔ́ adé Mwǎn a Dyǒb.” 
\s1 Bembapɛɛ béʼsō ábe Yesuɛ 
\p  
\v 35 Nɛ́ɛ bǐn éʼsáŋgé ámpē, Jɔnɛ ambɛ́ áhed ne ábē bembapɛɛ bébɛ.  
\v 36 Annyín nɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ átómɛɛ́. Ádě ányíné mɔ́, anhɔ́b aá, “Nyénɔneʼ, Mwǎn-a-Ńdyɔŋ ḿ mbód a Dyǒb mɔ̂ nɛ.”  
\v 37 Ádě ábê bembapɛɛ bébɛ béwógé nɛ̂, bêmbootéd Yesuɛ ahíd.  
\v 38 Áde Yesuɛ ánɔ́né ámbīd boŋ anyín nɛ̂ŋgáne béhídɛɛ́ mɔ́ ansɛdéd bɔ́ aáken, “Cheé nyéhɛdɛɛ́?” Bêntimtɛ́n mɔ́ bán, “Rabai” (awě adé bán meléede) “Héé édyɛʼɛ́?”  
\v 39 Anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nyéhyag, nyényîn wɛ́ɛ ńdyɛɛʼɛ́.” Né-ɔɔ́, bênkɛ̌ anyín wɛ́ɛ ádyɛɛʼɛ́. Áde bépédé áhed ébédé dyam ngə́ŋ éniin é ngukɛ́l. Bêndyɛɛ́-ʼɛ áhed kə́ə́ŋ bǐn éʼhíntɛ́n bɔ́.  
\v 40 Átîntê e ábê bembapɛɛ bébɛ ábe bénwōg dyam áde Jɔnɛ ánhɔ̄bpē boŋ béhíd-tɛ Yesuɛ, nhɔ́g abédé dǐn bán Andreya. Andreya abédɛ́ɛ Simɔn Petro mwǎnyaŋ.  
\v 41 Né-ɔɔ́ dyam déʼsō, ankɛ̌ mwǎnyaŋ Simɔnɛ ahɛd. Anyíné-ʼaá mɔ́ boŋ álāŋgē mɔ́ aá, “Sênyíné Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté” (nɛ́dē Krǐstəə).  
\v 42 Dɔ́ɔ Andreya ápɛ́ɛ́né Simɔnɛ wɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ. Yesuɛ anɔné-ʼaá Simɔnɛ chóóŋ, boŋ áhɔ̄bē aá, “Edíi Simɔnɛ, mwǎn awě Jɔnɛ. Bɛ́chəgé wɛ bɔɔb bán Sɛpasɛ.” (Ádɛ́n dǐn ádíi melemlem nɛ́ɛ Petro, nɛ̂ ádé ndim e aláá.) 
\s1 Yesuɛ achɛ́nlé Filibɛ bɔ́ Nataniɛl 
\p  
\v 43 Nɛ́ɛ bǐn éʼsáŋgé, Yesuɛ ammǎd aá mɔ́kag á mbwɔ́g e Galilia. Dɔ́ɔ ákíí Filibɛ atán boŋ álāŋgē mɔ́ aá, “Hídé mɛ.”  
\v 44 Filibɛ abédɛ́ɛ mod a dyad á Betsaida, melemlem mé dyad ádě Andreya bɔ́ Petro bémbīdtē.  
\v 45 Filibɛ anyín Nataniɛlɛ. Hɛ́ɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ nɛ́n aá, “Sênyíné ane mod awě Mosɛɛ ântenlé mam áyə̄l echê áwe mbéndé-te. Mɔ́ɔ kə́ə́ŋne bekal-bé-eʼdəə́dəŋ bêntenlé mam á yə̌l. Adíi Yesuɛ mod a dyad á Nazarɛt, mwǎn awě Josɛbɛ.”  
\v 46 Hɛ́ɛ Nataniɛlɛ ásɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ aáken, “Dyam á bwâm áhéé áhɛle ábíd á Nazarɛt?” Dɔ́ɔ Filibɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Hyɛ̌ ényîn.”  
\v 47 Áde Yesuɛ ányíné Nataniɛlɛ ahúɛʼ, dɔ́ɔ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ áyə̄l echê aá, “Nyénɔne, mwǎn a Israɛl nɛ́n sóm-sóm, awě mbɛltéd ńtyéémé!”  
\v 48 Hɛ́ɛ Nataniɛlɛ ásɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ aáken, “Chán émwédé mɛ abíi?” Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ákwɛntanné aá, “Filibɛ adɛ̂hɔ́b aá mɔ́chəge wɛ, nnyíné wɛ á alín á ngəl sé.”  
\v 49 Hɛ́ɛ Nataniɛlɛ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “A meléed, edíi Mwǎn a Dyǒb. Wɛ-ɛɛ́ edé kə̂ŋ e bad bé Israɛl.”  
\v 50 Yesuɛ antimtɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Edúbpé áyə̄le ńláŋgé wɛ mɛɛ́ nnyíné wɛ á alín á ngəl sé. Wɛɛ́nyīn mam ḿmě métómé nɛ́n.”  
\v 51 Hɛ́ɛ ábádɛɛ́ aá, “Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, nyɛ́ɛ̄nyīn nɛ́ɛ dyǒb ánédnédé nyênyín-nɛ nɛ́ɛ ángɛl é Dyǒb échə́gkɛɛ́ ésudé-ʼɛ Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ ámīn.” 
\c 2  
\s1 Eʼwóŋgé á dyad á Kana 
\p  
\v 1 Ámbīd e eʼpun éʼbɛ, eʼwóŋgé bémbɛ̄ á dyad á Kana á mbwɔ́g e Galilia. Yesuɛ nyaá ambɛ́ áhed.  
\v 2 Bénlēbē Yesuɛ ne ábē bembapɛɛ bɔ́mpē á eʼwóŋgé wɛ̂.  
\v 3 Mǐm mêmmaá áte. Hɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ nyaá ápédé áwē boŋ álāŋgē mɔ́ aá, “Mǐm mémáá bɔ́.”  
\v 4 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Á-nyaŋ, weetə̂ŋgɛnɛɛ́ mɛ dyam áde ńtə́ŋgɛ́né abɛl aláa. Echem póndé eépédɛ́ɛ́.”  
\v 5 Hɛ́ɛ nyaá ákíí bembəledɛ bé ngande bɛ̂ aláa aá, “Nyébɛl kéchéé éche áláŋgé nyé aá nyébɛl.”  
\v 6 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, mbeé é meláá ébédé bɛnbɛn ne áhed. Échê ndín é mbeé chɔ́ɔ bad bé Israɛl bébɛ́nládtáá âhɛ́ mendíb áte á nwobe ń yə̌l á póndé e mekáne echâb. Ké ehéé etedéʼáá dyam mbwɔ́kɛl e líta e mendíb.  
\v 7 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ bembəledɛ bé ngande bɛ̂ aá, “Nyélóned mbeé chê ne mendíb.” Né-ɔɔ́, bénlōnēd échê mbeé hɔɔd ne mendíb.\fig Bembəledɛ bé ngande bélônte mbeé ne mendíb ngáne Yesuɛ áhɔ́bé|src="CN01667C.tif" size="col" ref="2.7" \fig* 
\v 8 Dɔ́ɔ álâŋgɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “Nyékɔbe-ɔɔ́ mendíb bɔɔb, nyékɛɛn wɛ́ɛ mod awě alyə́gteʼ mekan mé ncháged.” Né-ɔɔ́, bêmbɛ̌l áned.  
\v 9 Áde ane mod áwóglɛ́né ḿmê mendíb ḿme mémáá mǐm atim, enkêmbííʼɛ́ wɛ́ɛ mébídé, (boŋ bembəledɛ ábe bênkɛ̌ ḿmê mendíb akɔbe bémbíi). Dɔ́ɔ áchə́gé mod awě akude sɔ́mbé,  
\v 10 boŋ álāŋgē mɔ́ aá, “Mod tɛ́ɛ́ abɛlé asébe achágtɛ́n bad mǐm ḿmě mébóó. Bad bémaa-ʼáa mɔ́ amwɛ́ bwâmbwam, boŋ ábagé bɔ́ ḿmě méeboo. Boŋ wɛ, etimé ekǒŋgé ḿme mébóó kə́ə́ŋ ne bɔɔb.”  
\v 11 Ḿmɛ́n menyáké ḿmě Yesuɛ ábɛ́lé á Kana á mbwɔ́g e Galilia mɔ́ɔ mébédé ábē eʼchemléd éʼsō. Hɛ̂ dɔ́-ʼaá álúmté échē ehúmé, ábē bembapɛɛ bênsǔm-mɛ ḿmab nlém áwē. 
\p  
\v 12 Nɛ́ɛ nɛ́n ámáá atóm, Yesuɛ ansyɔgé á dyad á Kapenahum nchoo ne nyaá, baányaŋ ne ábē bembapɛɛ. Bêndyɛɛ́-ʼɛ áwed nguse é eʼpun. 
\s1 Yesuɛ anané bekáb bé nyoŋgé á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb 
\r (Mat 21.12-13; Mak 11.15-17; Luk 19.45-46) 
\p  
\v 13 Ádě póndé e Ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn ékwógé bad bé Israɛl apɛ, Yesuɛ ankɛ̌ á dyad á Jerusalɛm.  
\v 14 Ádě ápédé áwed, ankɛ̌ á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb. Antán nɛ́ɛ bad békábɛɛ́ dyɔn. Bésóméʼ-ʼáá nyag, mbód ne mbəŋgé, bepɛle-bé-mɔné-ʼɛ bépɛnlé mɔné.  
\v 15 Hɛ́ɛ átédé nkɔɔd, ámané etaŋgú ánanné bɔ́ nchoo ne échab mbód ne nyag á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb wɛ̂. Ampáŋtéd mɔné ḿmě bad bépɛ́nléʼáá áte, ákūnē-ʼɛ betébelɛ ábe bépɛ́nléʼáá ḿmê mɔné ámīn mekuu ámīn.  
\v 16 Anláá bad ábe bésóméʼáá mbəŋgé aá, “Nyébídɛn beləə bén á ebwɔ́g. Nyéētimté ndáb echě echem Sáŋ ndáb e dyɔn.”  
\v 17 Ádě ábē bembapɛɛ bényíné nɛ̂, dɔ́ɔ békámtɛ́né epɛd é kálag e Dyǒb éche éhɔ́be nɛ́n bán “A-Sáŋ, kə́n echě ńwóó áyə̄le echoŋ ndáb ěwūū mɛ.” 
\p  
\v 18 Hɛ́ɛ benkamlɛnɛ bé bad bé Israɛl bétímé ámbīd, bésɛdté mɔ́ bánken, “Eʼchemléd éʼhéé éhɛle elúméd sé âbɛl sébíi bán ewóó kunze âbɛl enɛ́n ndín e dyam?”  
\v 19 Yesuɛ antimtɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Nyépâŋ enɛ́n Ndáb-e-Dyǒb, mɛ̌lōŋ chɔ́ ámpē áyə̄le eʼpun éʼláán.”  
\v 20 Dɔ́ɔ ábê bad béhɔ́bɛɛ́ bánken, “Enɛ́n ndáb echě bétédé móom mé mwɛ̌ méniin ne mwɛ̌ ntóób chɔ́ɔ éhɔ́bɛɛ́ wɛɛ́ mɔ́ɔ̄lōŋ áyə̄le eʼpun éʼláán-ɛ?”  
\v 21 Boŋ ndáb echě Yesuɛ áhɔ́béʼáá ebédɛ́ɛ dásɔ̄ eche yə̌l.  
\v 22 Né-ɔɔ́ ámbīd eche Yesuɛ áwédé boŋ Dyǒb ápūūd mɔ́, dɔ́ɔ ábē bembapɛɛ békámtɛ́né dyam ádě ánlāāʼɛ́ bɔ́. Béndūbē mam ḿmě méténlédé á kálag e Dyǒb, bédúbé-ʼɛ eʼyale ábe Yesuɛ ánhɔ̄bpē. 
\s1 Yesuɛ abíí mod asyəə́l nlém áte 
\p  
\v 23 Á póndé e Ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn, áde Yesuɛ ámbɛ̄ɛ̄ á dyad á Jerusalɛm, bad híin béndūbē mɔ́ ngáne bényīnnē menyáké ḿmě ábɛlɛɛ́.  
\v 24 Boŋ ké nɛ̂, Yesuɛ enkênsummé nlém áwāb, áyə̄le ambíí moosyəə́l áte.  
\v 25 Modmod enkêntə́ŋgɛ́nné mɔ́ dyam aláa tə̂ŋgɛne mod ampée áyə̄le mwěn ammǎd moonyoŋ asyəə́l nlém abíi áte. 
\c 3  
\s1 Yesuɛ bɔ́ Nikodemusɛ 
\p  
\v 1 Mod nhɔ́g abédé bán Nikodemusɛ. Abédɛ́ɛ nhɔ́g awě alyə́gtéʼáá bad bé Israɛl abɛ́-ʼɛ epepé é bad bé Farisia.  
\v 2 Mbwɛ nhɔ́g ampɛ̌ wɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ nkuu, álāŋgē mɔ́ aá, “A-meléed, sêchemé nɛ́n bán, edíi meléede awě Dyǒb álómé. Áyə̄le nzé Dyǒb déesɛ̌ ne mod, eéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ ábɛlé mekan mé menyáké ḿmě ébɛlɛɛ́.”  
\v 3 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Ne mbále, modmod eéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ asɔ́l á nkamlɛn ń Dyǒb ésebán achyáádté ámpē.”  
\v 4 Nikodemusɛ-ʼɛ ansɛdéd mɔ́ aáken, “Chán mod awě amaá akwog áhɛle se achyáád ekɔ́ɔ́lé-ekɔ́ɔ́lé? Éesaá mbále nɛ́n bán eéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ asɔ́l á abum ádē nyaá ngen échě élóntɛ́né ébɛ âbɛl béchyáa mɔ́ ámpē-yɛ?”  
\v 5 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ átimtanné mɔ́ aá, “Ne mbále, nlâŋge wɛ mɛɛ́, nzé béēchyáa mod ne mendíb ne Edəə́dəŋ éēhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ asɔ́l á nkamlɛn ń Dyǒb.  
\v 6 Ane awě achyáádté ne moonyoŋ a ekob, adíí moonyoŋ. Awě mɔ́-ʼɛ achyáádté ne Edəə́dəŋ é Dyǒb adíí Edəə́dəŋ.  
\v 7 Weebág menyáké ngáne ńhɔ́bé mɛɛ́ ‘Mod atə́ŋgɛ́né achyáád ekɔ́ɔ́lé.’  
\v 8 Nzé epub éhɔ́bé bán chɔ́ étómeʼ, pɛd echě édə́ə́ akɛ chɔ́ɔ ékagké. Ewógeʼ ntɔgag ḿme ébɛlɛɛ́ boŋ weebíɛ́ʼɛ́ wɛ́ɛ ébídɛɛ́ kéʼɛ wɛ́ɛ ékagké. Melemlem nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ édíí ne mod ké ahéé awě achyáádté ne Edəə́dəŋ é Dyǒb.”  
\v 9 Hɛ́ɛ Nikodemusɛ ásɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ aáken, “Chán nɛ́n áhɛlɛsɛ ábɛnled?”  
\v 10 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Nɛ́ɛ édíí meléede ambáá a bad bé Israɛl weéhɛ̄lēʼ ḿmɛ́n mekan asôŋtɛn-nɛ?  
\v 11 Ne mbále, nlâŋge wɛ mɛɛ́, dyam áde sébíí dɔ́ɔ séhɔ́bɛɛ́. Sébīde-ʼɛ mbóŋ ne dyam ádě sényíné. Boŋ nyé modmod nyéēkwɛntɛnɛɛ́ chǒm éche séhɔ́bɛɛ́ adúbe.  
\v 12 Nɛ́ɛ ńlâŋgɛɛ́ nyé mekan ḿme médé mekan mé nkǒŋsé, nyéedúbpe, chán-nɔ̄ nyɛ́mwɛɛ́ adúbe nzé nláŋgé nyé mekan ḿmě médé mekan mɛ nkoŋ ḿ mîn?  
\v 13 Modmod eékīīʼɛ́ á nkoŋ ḿ mîn étōmɛɛ́ Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ awě abídé áwed boŋ ápɛ á nkǒŋsé.”  
\v 14 Ngáne Mosɛɛ âmbomɛ́ɛ́ nyə̌ á akon\f + \fr 3:14 \ft Nyə̌ eche Mosɛɛ âmbomɛ́ɛ́ ebédɛ́ɛ nyə̌ echê âmbɛnlé. Nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ Dyǒb démbɛnlé âchood bad ábe nyə̌ énlēdtē á ehyáŋge. Nzé bad bênnɔ̌n ene nyə̌, bédyɛ̄ɛ̄ bwâm. Nɔm 21.9.\f* boŋ atíí dɔ́ ámīn á ehyáŋge, melemlem nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ bɛ́tīīʼɛ́ Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ.  
\v 15 Nɛ́n dɛ́bɛnléd âbɛl boŋ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adúbpé mɔ́ ákud aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ. 
\p  
\v 16 Dyǒb átómtɛ́né bad bé nkǒŋsé adəŋ. Né-ɔɔ́ anlóm ḿmē mpɔm ḿ Mwǎn âbɛl kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adúbpé mɔ́ eewág boŋ ákud aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ.  
\v 17 Dyǒb dénkênlómmé awe Mwǎn á nkǒŋsé âkáad bad. Aloŋgé á bad dɔ́ɔ ánlōmmē mɔ́ âsoŋ.  
\v 18 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adúbpé mɔ́ eékwaá nkáásé, boŋ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě eedúbpe mɔ́, amaá nkáásé akwɛ áyə̄le eedúbpɛɛ́ mpɔm ḿ Mwǎn ń Dyǒb.  
\v 19 Nɛ́n dɔ́ɔ mbakú e Dyǒb édíí: Eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde éʼpédé á nkǒŋsé, boŋ baányoŋ bédə́ə́ ehíntɛ́n tómaa eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde áyə̄le ḿmāb mbɛltéd ńdé mbéb.  
\v 20 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě abɛle mbéb, akɔɔ́ ábê eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde, éepaá-ʼaá á eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde-tê âbáŋ nɛ́n ḿmē mbɛltéd mé mbéb méēbīdē áwed.  
\v 21 Boŋ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě abɛle mam mé mbále, abídeʼ á eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde âbɛl nɛ́n bad bényîn bán kéchéé échě ábɛlɛɛ́ awógne Dyǒb. 
\s1 Mbóŋ echě Jɔnɛ tə̂ŋgɛne Yesuɛ 
\p  
\v 22 Ámbīd e nɛ̂, Yesuɛ ne ábē bembapɛɛ bênkɛ̌ á mbwɔ́g e Judeya. Bɔ́bɔ̄ɔ bêndyɛɛ́ áwed nguse é eʼpun, ádusán-nɛ bad.  
\v 23 Jɔnɛ mɔ́mpē adusánáá bad á dyad á Anɔn bɛnbɛn ne á dyad á Salim áyə̄le mendíb mémbɛ áhed bwâmbwam. Bad békágéʼáá áwē, ádusán-nɛ bɔ́.  
\v 24 Nɛ́n ábédé byánán bɛ́hɛ̄ Jɔnɛ á mbwɔg.  
\v 25 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, doŋge dé bembapɛɛ ábe Jɔnɛ bépéntánnáá ne mod a Israɛl tə̂ŋgɛne nwobe ń yə̌l.  
\v 26 Dɔ́ɔ bépédé wɛ́ɛ Jɔnɛ boŋ bélāŋgē mɔ́ bán, “A-meléed, ekamtan mod awě nyúmɔ̄ nyêbédé á pɛd e edíb é Jodan eníníí? Mod awě éhɔ́béʼáá mam á yə̌l echê. Nɔnéʼ! Mɔ́ɔ adusan bad níníí! Bad híin békagke áwē.”  
\v 27 Jɔnɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Modmod eéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ ákud chǒm, ésebán Dyǒb ábágé mɔ́ chɔ́.  
\v 28 Nyéběn nyêdé mɛ mbóŋ nɛ́n bán menhɔ́b mɛɛ́ saké mɛ ndé Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté. Dyǒb dénlōm mɛ áʼsō âboŋsɛn bad áyə̄le epɛ éche Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté.  
\v 29 Mod awě akude sɔ́mbé mɔ́ɔ awóó sɔ́mbé. Boŋ nsón-a-echoŋ a mod awě akude sɔ́mbé, awě atyéeme mɔ́ á nkəg áwōglān mɔ́, abâg menyiŋge nzé awóge mɔ́ ehɔ́b. Né-ɔɔ́, nɛ́n dɔ́ɔ ákə́ə́ boŋ nlón ne menyiŋge.  
\v 30 Edúbé échē étə́ŋgɛ́né nɛ́ɛ échə́gkɛɛ́, échêm-mɛ ésudeʼ.” 
\s1 Ane awě abídé ádyōb atómé moosyəə́l 
\p  
\v 31 Ane awě abídé ádyōb atómé moosyəə́l. Ane awě mɔ́-ʼɛ achyáádté á nkǒŋsé adíi mod a nkǒŋsé, áhɔ̄bē-ʼɛ mam mé nkǒŋsé, boŋ ane awě abídé ádyōb adé ámīn e moosyəə́l.  
\v 32 Chǒm éche ányíné ne éche áwógé chɔ́ɔ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ boŋ ké nɛ̂, modmod eedúbpɛ́ɛ́ mɔ́.  
\v 33 Boŋ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě akobé chǒm échě áhɔ́bé, né akwɛntɛ́né ne nlém ńsyə̄ə̄l aá Dyǒb ádé mbále.  
\v 34 Pɔ́le e Dyǒb chɔ́ɔ mod awě Dyǒb álómé áhɔ́bɛɛ́ áyə̄le Dyǒb déenɔnɛ́ɛ́ ámbīd nzé abageʼ mod échē Edəə́dəŋ.  
\v 35 Titɛ́ɛ adəə́ awe Mwǎn, abagé-ʼɛ mekan mésyə̄ə̄l áwē mekáá.  
\v 36 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě asumé nlém wɛ́ɛ ane Mwǎn, akudé aloŋgé ádě déemaáʼ. Boŋ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě eébɛ̄lēʼ ngáne áhɔ́bé éekudté aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ, ǎbɛ̄ akud nkɔ́gsɛn ń Dyǒb. 
\c 4  
\s1 Yesuɛ ne mmwaád a Samaria 
\p  
\v 1 Yesuɛ ambíí aá Befarisia béwógé nɛ́n bán mɔ́kude ekud é bembapɛɛ tómaa ne Jɔnɛ, mɔ́dusan-nɛ bɔ́.  
\v 2 (Kénɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ mwěn éedusannaá bad, ábē bembapɛɛ bɔ́ɔ bédúsánnáá bad).  
\v 3 Awóg áde Befarisia bénwōgkē nɛ̂ dêmbɛ̌l Yesuɛ anhidé á mbwɔ́g e Judeya átim ámbīd á mbwɔ́g e Galilia.  
\v 4 Byánán ǎpɛ á Galilia antə́ŋgɛ́n nɛ́ɛ ápóó a mbwɔ́g e Samaria.  
\v 5 Á mbwɔ́g e Samaria wɛ̂ ampɛ̌ á dyad áde béchəgɛɛ́ bán Sika. Ádɛ́n dyad démbɛ̄ bɛnbɛn ne ndɔɔb echě Jakɔbɛ ámbɛɛ́ mwǎn Josɛbɛ se eʼbɔɔ́d.  
\v 6 Áyə̄le ene ndɔɔb echóg éche bélímé éche bébwɛ́léʼáá mendíb áte émbɛ̄ áhed. Échɛ́n echóg é mendíb ébédɛ́ɛ éche Jakɔbɛ. Ngáne ekɛ énkɔ̄mēdtē Yesuɛ andyɛɛ́ á nkəg mé échê echóg é mendíb. Nɛ́n ábédé dyam-ɛ́ɛ ádé kəd. 
\p  
\v 7 Hɛ́ɛ mmwaád a Samaria nhɔ́g áhyédé mendíb abwɛl. Yesuɛ anláá mɔ́ aá, “Hɛ́ mɛ mwǎ mendíb mé amwɛ́.”\fig Yesuɛ aá mmwaád a Samaria áhɛ̂ mɔ́ mwǎ mendíb mé amwɛ́|src="BA03029BW.tif" size="col" ref="4.7" \fig* 
\v 8 Enɛ́n póndé Yesuɛ ábɛ̄ bembapɛɛ bênkɛ̌ á dyad-tê âchan ndyééd.  
\v 9 Hɛ́ɛ ane mmwaád átimtanné mɔ́ aá “Ebɛ́ mod a Israɛl, mɛ-ʼɛ mbɛ́ mmwaád a Samaria, échɔ̄mē mɛ mendíb-ɛ?” (áyə̄le bad bé Israɛl ne bad bé Samaria béechemtannaá.)  
\v 10 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ákwɛntanné mɔ́ aá, “Nzé wembíí mendɛ mé Dyǒb, ebíí-ʼɛ mod awě ahɛdne wɛ mendíb, né ehɛ̌dné mɛ mendíb. Né mbagé-ʼɛ wɛ mendíb ḿme mébage aloŋgé.”  
\v 11 Ane mmwaád ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “A-Sáŋ, ké chǒm éche bébwɛnlɛɛ́ mendíb weewóoʼɛ́, echóg é mendíb-pɛ échábé ásē, hɛ́ɛ wɛ́tēdtē ḿmê mendíb ḿmē mébage aloŋgé.  
\v 12 Echɛd sáá ambáá Jakɔbɛ mɔ̂nlyə́gnéd sé échɛ́n echóg é mendíb. Mwěn, ábē bǎn ne ábē eʼlém éʼsyə̄ə̄l, hɛ́n-ɛɛ́ bémwágéʼáá mendíb. Nɛ́dē ehɔ́be bɔɔb wɛɛ́ mɔ́tōmē Jakɔbɛ-yɛ.”  
\v 13 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě amwédé ḿmɛ́n mendíb, píd ěbɛ̄ ekób mɔ́.  
\v 14 Boŋ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě ǎmwɛ̄ mendíb ḿme mɛ́bɛɛ́ mɔ́ píd éekóbpé mɔ́ mbêd. Mendíb ḿme mɛ́bɛɛ́ mɔ́, mɛ́bɛ̄ mɔ́ áte nɛ́ɛ n'yɛ́lɛ́ ḿme méēlēnɛ̄ʼ. Ḿmê mendíb mɛ́bɛ̌ mɔ́ aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ.”  
\v 15 Hɛ́ɛ ane mmwaád álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “A-Sáŋ, bɛɛ́ mɛ ḿmê mendíb âbɛl nɛ́n píd eekóbé mémpē, meépāg-kɛ hɛ́n âbwɛl mendíb ámpē.” 
\p  
\v 16 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Kǎg, ékɛ échəg awoŋ nchóm, boŋ étim ámbīd hɛ́n.”  
\v 17 Ane mmwaád antimtɛ́n Yesuɛ aá, “Mewóoʼɛ́ nchóm.”  
\v 18 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “Ekalé mbále wɛɛ́ mɔ́ɔwóoʼɛ́ nchóm. Áyə̄le ekéwōŋ bechóm bétáan, ké ane mod-tɛ awě nyúmɔ̄ nyêdé bɔɔb eésaá awoŋ nchóm. Dyam áde éhɔ́bé ádé mbále.”  
\v 19 Awóg áde ane mmwaád áwógé nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ álâŋgɛɛ́ Yesuɛ aá, “A-Sáŋ, nnyíne nɛ́n mɛɛ́ edíi nkal éʼdəə́dəŋ.  
\v 20 Á mbɔɔd-mîn hɛ́n dɔ́ɔ ábɛ̄d besáá bébágéʼáá Dyǒb edúbé, boŋ nyé bad bé Israɛl nyêhɔ́be bán á Jerusalɛm dɔ́ɔ bétə́ŋgɛ́né Dyǒb edúbé abɛ.”  
\v 21 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Á-mmwaád nɛ́n, sóŋtɛ́n chǒm éche ńlâŋgɛɛ́ wɛ. Póndé ehúɛʼ echě nyéebaá Titɛ́ɛ edúbé á mbɔɔd-mîn hɛ́n kéʼɛ á Jerusalɛm.  
\v 22 Nyé bad bé Samaria nyêbage chǒm éche nyéebíiʼɛ́ edúbé. Boŋ sé bad bé Israɛl sêbage mɔ́ edúbé ngáne sébíí mɔ́ áyə̄le nɛ́n eʼsoósoŋ éʼhúú dásɔ̄ ne bad bé Israɛl.  
\v 23 Boŋ póndé ehúɛʼ, emaá-ʼɛ ne apɛ, echě bad ábe bébage Titɛ́ɛ edúbé ne nlém nhɔ́g bɛ́bɛɛ́ mɔ́ échê edúbé á Edəə́dəŋ ne á mbále-tê. Échê ndín é bad chɔ́ɔ Titɛ́ɛ áhɛdɛɛ́ aá bébage mɔ́ edúbé.  
\v 24 Dyǒb ádíi Edəə́dəŋ, bad-tɛ ábe bébage mɔ́ edúbé bétə́ŋgɛ́né mɔ́ chɔ́ abɛ á Edəə́dəŋ ne á mbále-tê.”  
\v 25 Hɛ́ɛ ane mmwaád álâŋgɛɛ́ Yesuɛ aá, “Mbíí mɛɛ́ Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté ǎpɛ̌. Póndé echě ápɛɛ́, ǎtə̄nlēd sé mekan mésyə̄ə̄l áte.”  
\v 26 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Mɛ awě sóo dekaleʼ mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé mɔ́.” 
\p  
\v 27 Ene póndé chěn dɔ́ɔ ábē bembapɛɛ bépédé. Yə̌l enkɔ́m bɔ́ áte ânyín nɛ́ɛ ákanlɛɛ́ mmwaád. Boŋ bɔ́ modmod eésɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ aáken, “Cheé éhɛdɛɛ́?” Ké-ʼɛ “Cheé nyé ane mmwaád nyékalɛɛ́?”  
\v 28 Ane mmwaád antɛdé apom dé mendíb, átim ámbīd á dyad-tê, ákɛ aláá bad aá,  
\v 29 “Nyéhyag, nyényîn mod awě áláŋgé mɛ mam mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme ńkémbɛnlé. Nyé bán, saké Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté awě bésinɛɛ́ nɛ́n-ɛ?”  
\v 30 Dɔ́ɔ ábê bad béhídté á dyad-tê âkɛ dé atán Yesuɛ. 
\p  
\v 31 Ene póndé, bembapɛɛ ábe Yesuɛ béchááʼáá mɔ́ bán, “A-meléed dyɛ́ ndyééd.”  
\v 32 Boŋ Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Nwóó ndyééd e adyɛ́ echě nyéēbíiʼɛ́.”  
\v 33 Hɛ́ɛ ábē bembapɛɛ bésɛdtɛɛ́ nhɔ́g ne aníníí bánken, “mod múmɔ́ apiínédé mɔ́ ndyééd-ɛ?”  
\v 34 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “Echem ndyééd edíi âbɛl nsɔ́n ḿme mod awě alómé mɛ, áhɔ́bé aá ḿbɛl, âmad-tɛ mɔ́.  
\v 35 Ngɔ́mē nyêyɔ̌gké ahɔ́b bán ámbíd e ngɔn éniin, né póndé e mbote epedéʼ? Nyénɔneʼ, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛ́ɛ nyékɛ́led dǐd áte, nyényîn ngáne mbote émáá mboŋsɛ́n abɛ́, âpád á nzag-tê.  
\v 36 Ké bɔɔb mod awě apáde adé ḿme nsábe akud, alade mbote é aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ, âbɛl nɛ́n mod awě awéne bɔ́ mod awě apáde bɔ́ moosyəə́l bébɛ̂ menyiŋge.  
\v 37 Né-ɔɔ́ ngan echě békalɛɛ́ nɛ́n bán, ‘mod nhɔ́g awénɛɛ́, aníníí-ʼɛ ahúd edé mbále.’  
\v 38 Mɛ-ɛɛ́ nlómé nyé mbote âkɛ dé apád éche nyéēwénɛɛ́. Bad bémpēe bébɛ́lé nsɔ́n, nyé-ʼɛ nyêtombwan bɔ́ nsɔ́n.” 
\s1 Bad bé Samaria híin bédúbpé 
\p  
\v 39 Bad bé Samaria híin ábe bémbīd ádê dyad béndūbē Yesuɛ áyə̄le mam ḿmē ane mmwaád ánlāāʼɛ́ bɔ́. Ane mmwaád anláá bɔ́ aá, “Aláŋgé mɛ mekan mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme ńkémbɛnlé.”  
\v 40 Né-ɔɔ́, áde bad bé Samaria bépédé áwē, bénchāŋ mɔ́ bán ádyɛɛ áwāb dyad. Né-ɔɔ́, andyɛɛ́ áwed eʼpun éʼbɛ.  
\v 41 Bad híin bémpēe béndūbē mɔ́ áyə̄le áde ayə́ge.  
\v 42 Bénlāā ane mmwaád bán, “Saké dyam áde élāŋgē sé děmpɛn dɔ́ɔ ákə́ə́ boŋ sêdúbé Yesuɛ, boŋ séběn sêwógné etúu, sêbíí-ʼɛ bán mwěn-ɛɛ́ akǒŋté Nsoodɛ a nkǒŋsé abɛ́.” 
\s1 Yesuɛ achǒŋté mwǎn  //  a mod ambáá a ngɔ́menaa 
\p  
\v 43 Ámbīd e eʼpun éʼbɛ Yesuɛ anhidé á mbwɔ́g e Samaria, ákɛ á mbwɔg e Galilia.  
\v 44 Yesuɛ mwěn anhɔ́b aá, nkal éʼdəə́dəŋ eewóóʼɛ́ edúbé áwē dyad.  
\v 45 Áde ápédé á mbwɔ́g e Galilia, bad bênkob mɔ́. Bênkob mɔ́ áyə̄le bémbɛ̄ á Ngande e Nnyíme ámīn á Jerusalɛm, bényín-nɛ mam mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme ámbɛnlé. 
\p  
\v 46 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ átímé ámbīd á Kana, wɛ́ɛ ântimédté mendíb mǐm. Áhed-tɛ dɔ́ɔ mod ambáá a ngɔ́menaa ábédé awě mwǎn ákónléʼáá á dyad á Kapenahum.  
\v 47 Áde ane mod áwógé bán Yesuɛ ábídé á mbwɔ́g e Judeya apedé á mbwɔ́g e Galilia, ampɛ̌ áwē, acháŋ mɔ́ aá áchood mwǎn, awě ambɛ́ bɛnbɛn ne kwééd.  
\v 48 Yesuɛ anláá mɔ́ aá, “Nyé modmod nyéedúbpɛ́ɛ́ kə́ə́ŋ né nyênyíné eʼchemléd ne menyáké.”  
\v 49 Ane mod ambáá a ngɔ́menaa anláá mɔ́ aá, “A-Sáŋ, hyǎg, dékag kwééd edé ehɔ́b bán chɔ́ ekóbe awem mwǎn.”  
\v 50 Yesuɛ antimtɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Kǎg, awoŋ mwǎn ǎbɛ̄ á aloŋgé.” Ane mod andúbé eʼyale ábe Yesuɛ, ákɛ̄-ʼɛ.  
\v 51 Áde ane mod ádíí adé á nzii e esú dɔ́ɔ ábē bembəledɛ bébómné mɔ́, boŋ bélāŋgē mɔ́ bán, “awoŋ mwǎn ǎbɛ̄ á aloŋgé.”  
\v 52 Dɔ́ɔ ásɛ́dté bɔ́ póndé echě ane mwǎn âmbootédté bwâm abɛ́. Bénlāā mɔ́ bán, “Ahéb dêntɛdé mɔ́ chǎn á ngə́ŋ pɔ́g.”  
\v 53 Dɔ́ɔ ane mod ákámtɛ́né aá ḿmê melemlem mé póndé mɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ ánlāāʼɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Awoŋ mwǎn ǎbɛ̄ á aloŋgé.” Né-ɔɔ́, bɔ́ɔbɛ eche ndáb béndūbē Yesuɛ. 
\p  
\v 54 Ábɛ́n eʼchemléd bɔ́ɔ bémbɛ̄ eʼchemléd ábe éʼlóntɛ́né éʼbɛ ábe Yesuɛ ámbɛnlé áde ábídé á mbwɔ́g e Judeya boŋ ápɛ̄ á mbwɔ́g e Galilia. 
\c 5  
\s1 Yesuɛ achǒŋté epɛd é mod 
\p  
\v 1 Ámbīd e ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l, Yesuɛ ankɛ̌ á Jerusalɛm á ngande e bad bé Israɛl.  
\v 2 Á Jerusalɛm wɛ̂, bɛnbɛn ne Nsəl mé Eʼkɛ́ mé Ńdyɔŋ ḿ mbód, etoŋ ébédé áhed. Échɛ́n etoŋ béchə́géʼáá chɔ́ á ehɔ́b é bad bé Israɛl bán Bɛtzata. Énwōŋ mebepé métáan.  
\v 3 Á mebepé-te wɛ̂, bad bé nkole bénkūmɛ̄n áhed, ábe békwédé ndím, ábe bédé eʼpɛd éʼ bad ne ábe béwédé epɛd.\f + \fr 5:3 \ft Doŋge á kálag ábádé nchoo 3b-4: \fq Ábê bad bé nkole bémbɛ̄ áhed âsin bán mendíb mépuuted áte. \fv 4 \fv*\fq Ébédé nɛ́n bán, póndé-tɛ́ ángɛl eche Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́ ehyagáá asud á etoŋ-tê wɛ̂ épuutéd chɔ́ áte. Nzé êmbɛnléd-tɛ nɛ̂, mod a nkole ké ahéé awě ansébé asɔ́l áwēd-te nkole ḿmááʼáá mɔ́.\f* 
\v 5 Mod nhɔ́g abédé áhed awě akékolé á etûn é móom mé mwɛ̌ méláán ne mwɛ̌ waam.  
\v 6 Áde Yesuɛ ápédé áhed annyín ngáne ane mod ánáŋgé ásē, abíí-ʼɛ aá nkole ḿbémé mɔ́ á yə̌l. Dɔ́ɔ ásɛ́dté mɔ́ aáken, “Edəə́ bwâm adyɛɛ-yɛ?”  
\v 7 Ane mod antimtɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “A-sáŋ, meewóoʼɛ́ mod awe ǎsɔ̄lēd mɛ á etoŋ-tê nzé mendíb mépúútédé áte. Nlédte ahɔ́b mɛɛ́ ńsɔ̂l, né mod ampée amaá asɔ́l.”  
\v 8 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Syəə́ ásē, étêd échoŋ ebúm, ékag.”  
\v 9 Ábwɔ̄g-ábwɔ̄g ane mod andyɛ̌ bwâm, ányə̄g échē ebúm áte, ábootéd-tɛ akɛ. 
\p Epun éche nɛ́n dêmbɛnlédté ébédɛ́ɛ á mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me-áte.  
\v 10 Né-ɔɔ́, anyín áde bad bémbáá bé Israɛl bényíné ane mod awě Yesuɛ ândidté bwâm, bênsɛdéd mɔ́ bánken, “Chii ádé mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me-áte, nzé dehídé-ʼɛ mbéndé echɛ̂d, weetə̂ŋgɛnɛɛ́ ebúm apém se ébwāgneʼ.”  
\v 11 Boŋ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Mod awě adidé mɛ bwâm anláá mɛ aá, ‘Téd échoŋ ebúm, ékag?’ ”  
\v 12 Hɛ́ɛ bésɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ bán, “Nzɛ́ adé ane mod awě áláŋgé wɛ aá, étêd échoŋ ebúm ékag?”  
\v 13 Boŋ ane mod mwěn enkênkoŋgé Yesuɛ abíi, ngáne Yesuɛ âmmadté asɔ́l á amute-tê áde démbɛ̄ áhed.  
\v 14 Ámbīd enɛ̂ Yesuɛ annyín ane mod á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb. Áde ányíné mɔ́, anláá mɔ́ aá, “Nɔnéʼ, emaá bwâm adyɛɛ. Weébɛ̄lē mbéb ámpē ésebɛ́ nɛ̂, né wɛ̌tōm atag ngáne étágéʼáá nɛ̂.”  
\v 15 Hɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ ane mod áhídté, boŋ ákɛ álāŋgē bad bémbáá bé Israɛl aá Yesuɛ mɔ́ɔ adidé mɔ́ bwâm.  
\v 16 Né-ɔɔ́, bad bémbáá bé Israɛl bêmbootéd Yesuɛ mekuu ahíd áyə̄le achǒŋté mod á mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me-áte.  
\v 17 Yesuɛ antimtɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Echem Sáŋ ayɔ̌gké nsɔ́n abɛl, mɛ-ʼɛ ámpē ntə́ŋgɛ́né nsɔ́n abɛl.”  
\v 18 Enɛ́n pɔ́le echě Yesuɛ ánhɔ̄bpē, embɛ̌l yə̌l ennabé bad bé Israɛl atod áte âwúu mɔ́, áyə̄le saké mbéndé e mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me-áte, chěmpɛn ábóó boŋ achəgé Dyǒb aá Sáá, nɛ́dē alûmteʼ aá bɔ́ Dyǒb bétə́ə́. 
\s1 Ngíne e Mwǎn a Dyǒb ehúú ne Dyǒb 
\p  
\v 19 Né-ɔɔ́, Yesuɛ antimtɛ́n ábê bad bémbáá bé Israɛl aá, “Á mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, Mwǎn a Dyǒb eébɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄ dyam ké ahɔ́g ne mɔ́ mwěn. Mekan ḿme ányínɛɛ́ Sáá abɛleʼ mɔ́ɔ mɔ́mpē ábɛlɛɛ́. Kéchéé éche Sáá ábɛlɛɛ́ chɔ́ɔ mɔ́mpē ábɛlɛɛ́.  
\v 20 Ngáne édíí nɛ́n bán Sáá adəə́ Mwǎn, alûmte mɔ́ chǒm tɛ́ɛ́ éche ábɛlɛɛ́. Ǎlūmēd-tɛ mɔ́ ndəle é mekan éche étómé ḿmɛ́n, âbɛl ékɔ́med nyé yə̌l áte.  
\v 21 Ngáne Sáá ápuudtɛɛ́ bad boŋ ábagé-ʼɛ bɔ́ aloŋgé, melemlem nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ Mwǎn mɔ́mpē ábagɛɛ́ aloŋgé wɛ́ɛ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě ádə́ə́ aloŋgé abɛ.  
\v 22 Melemlem-ʼaá Sáá éēkāādtɛ̄ɛ̄ modmod. Abagé Mwǎn ngíne esyəə́l âkáad bad.  
\v 23 Abɛlé nɛ̂ âbɛl boŋ bébage Mwǎn edúbé melemlem ngáne bébagɛɛ́ Sáá. Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě eébage Mwǎn edúbé, né eébagɛɛ́ ké Sáá awě alómé Mwǎn edúbé.  
\v 24 Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě awógé ábêm eʼyale boŋ adúbé mod awě alómé mɛ, akudé aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ, béekáád-taá mɔ́. Amaá atóm á kwééd, asɔ́lé á aloŋgé.  
\v 25 Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé mɛɛ́, póndé ehúɛʼ, emaá-ʼɛ apɛ, echě bad ábe béwédé bɛ́wōgkē ehɔ́b e Mwǎn a Dyǒb, bad ábe bɛ́wōg-kɛ chɔ́ bɛ́bē á aloŋgé.  
\v 26 Ngáne aloŋgé áhúú ne Sáá, melemlem nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ ábɛ́lé aá aloŋgé áhúu ne Mwǎn ámpē.  
\v 27 Abagé-ʼɛ Mwǎn ngíne âkáad bad áyə̄le Mwǎn adíi ane awě béchəgɛɛ́ bán Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ.  
\v 28 Nɛ́n déēkɔ̄mtē nyé yə̌l áte; póndé ehúɛʼ echě bad bésyə̄ə̄l ábe béwédé bɛ́wɔ̄gkē échē ehɔ́b,  
\v 29 bébíd-tɛ á soŋ-tê: Bad ábe bébɛ́lé mboŋ, bɛ́puú âbɛ́ á aloŋgé, ábe bɔ́-ʼɛ bébɛ́lé mbéb bɛ́puú békud nkɔ́gsɛn. 
\s1 Mbóŋ áyə̄l wɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ 
\p  
\v 30 “Dyamdyam déesaá áde ńhɛle ḿbɛ̄l ne mměn. Ngáne echem Sáŋ áláŋgé mɛ aá ńkáad nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ ńkáadtɛɛ́, né-ɔɔ́ mbakú echêm etyéémé. Etyéémé áyə̄le meekáádtɛ́ɛ́ ngáne mměn ńdə́ə́, boŋ nkáadteʼ ngáne mod awě alómé mɛ áhɛdɛɛ́. 
\p  
\v 31 “Nzé mbídé echem yə̌l mbóŋ né ene mbóŋ echě ḿbídɛɛ́ eékobnedɛɛ́.  
\v 32 Boŋ mod ampée adé awě abíde mɛ mbóŋ, mbíí-ʼɛ nɛ́n mɛɛ́, mbóŋ echě ábídɛɛ́ mɛ ekǒbnédé.  
\v 33 Nyênlóm bad wɛ́ɛ Jɔnɛ, mɔ́-aá abídé mbóŋ tə̂ŋgɛne mbále.  
\v 34 Éesaá nɛ́n bán, moonyoŋ atə́ŋgɛ́né mɛ mbóŋ abíd. Boŋ nláŋgé nyé tə̂ŋgɛne mbóŋ eche Jɔnɛ, âbɛl nyédúbe mɛ, nyékud eʼsoósoŋ.  
\v 35 Jɔnɛ abédɛ́ɛ nɛ́ɛ etrúkáŋ éche échodneʼ, épɛnté-ʼɛ ekíde. Nyêmbɛ́ menyiŋge âhíd ábɛ̂ eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde áyə̄le esóŋ é póndé.  
\v 36 Boŋ nwóó mbóŋ echě etómé ké mbóŋ echě Jɔnɛ ámbīdtē. Nsɔ́n ḿme echem Sáŋ ábágé mɛ aá ḿbɛl ḿmad, mměn ḿbíde mbóŋ nɛ́n bán echem Sáŋ mɔ́ɔ alómé mɛ.  
\v 37 Echem Sáŋ awě alómé mɛ mwěn ámpē abíde mɛ mbóŋ. Nyéēwógɛ́ɛ́ mɔ́ ehɔ́b, nyéēnyíné-ʼaá mɔ́ mbêd.  
\v 38 Nyéedúbpɛɛ́ ane awě álómé, né-ɔɔ́ nyéēmwagké bán échē eyale édyɛɛ nyé á nlém-tê.  
\v 39 Nyêkídteʼ Eyale é Dyǒb ahɛd áte áyə̄le nyêwêmtan bán nyɛ́ɛ̄kǔd aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ áwēd-te. Échɛ́n Eyale chěn-ɛ́ɛ éhɔ́be áyə̄l echêm.  
\v 40 Ké nɛ̂, nyéēhɛ̄dɛ̄ɛ̄ apɛ áwêm âbɛl boŋ nyékud aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ. 
\p  
\v 41 “Saké edúbé é baányoŋ ńhɛdɛɛ́.  
\v 42 Boŋ mbíí nyaa é bad éche nyédíí, mbíí-ʼɛ mɛɛ́ nyéewôŋnɛɛ́ Dyǒb edəŋge á nlém-tê.  
\v 43 Mpedé á dǐn áde echem Sáŋ, nyéēkobɛɛ́ mɛ, boŋ nzé mod ampée apedé á dǐn ádē děn, nyɛ́ɛ̄kob mɔ́.  
\v 44 Nzé nyêkɛneʼ nhɔ́g ne aníníí, nyéwōgē bwâm, boŋ nyéēbɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄ ngáne Dyǒb děn dɛ́kɛnné nyé. Chán-nɔ̄ nyɛ́dūbɛ̄ɛ̄ mɛ?  
\v 45 Ké nɛ́ɛ nyéekobɛɛ́ mɛ, nyéewémtán bán, mɛ-ɛɛ́ mɛ̌lāā echem Sáŋ mɛɛ́ nyéēkobɛɛ́ mɛ. Mosɛɛ awě nyélyə́gé nlém áwē mwěn-nɛɛ́ akǒŋté ane abɛ́ awě ǎhɔ̄b aá, nyêbɛlé mbéb.  
\v 46 Nzé nyênkǒŋ Mosɛɛ adúbe né nyêdúbpé mɛ, áyə̄le nɛ́n, áyə̄l echêm dɔ́ɔ ântenlé mam ḿme átélé.  
\v 47 Boŋ nɛ́ɛ nyéedúbpɛɛ́ mekan ḿme átélé, chán nyɛ́dūbɛ̄ɛ̄ ábêm eʼyale?” 
\c 6  
\s1 Yesuɛ adídté ndun e mod 
\r (Mat 14.13-21; Mak 6.30-44; Luk 9.10-17) 
\p  
\v 1 Ámbīd e ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l, Yesuɛ ne ábē bembapɛɛ bênchabé edib é Galilia éche béchəgɛɛ́ bán edib é Tiberia.  
\v 2 Ndun e mod ehídéʼáá mɔ́ áyə̄le bényínéʼáá menyáké ḿme ábɛ́léʼáá ngáne áchóóŋtéʼáá bad bé nkole.  
\v 3 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ne ábē bembapɛɛ békíí á ekone-mîn boŋ bédyɛ̄ɛ̄ ásē.  
\v 4 Póndé e Ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn e bad bé Israɛl embɛ́ bɛnbɛn.  
\v 5 Asad áde Yesuɛ ásádé dǐd annyín ngáne ndun e mod éhúɛʼɛ́ mɔ́ bɛnbɛn. Dɔ́ɔ ásɛdtɛɛ́ Filibɛ aáken, “Hɛ́ɛ dɛ́channé ndyééd echě dɛ́bɛɛ́ ábɛ́n bad âdyɛ́?”  
\v 6 Ansɛdéd mɔ́ nɛ̂ âkəg mɔ́ áyə̄le mwěn ammad abíi chǒm éche ábɛnlé.  
\v 7 Filibɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Étēd tómaa ne mbwɔ́kɛl é kábpe ébɛ âchan ndyééd éche ěkwognéd ábɛ́n bad bésyə̄ə̄l adyɛ́ âbɛl boŋ mod tɛ́ɛ́ ádyɛ̂ mwǎtiíd.”  
\v 8 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ awě mbapɛɛ ampée, Andreya, Simɔn Petro mwǎnyaŋ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá,  
\v 9 “Mwǎ kódemod adé hɛ́n awě awánlé eʼwɛle éʼtáan ábe bébɛ́nlé ngun é báli, awánlé-ʼɛ súu ébɛ, boŋ chán enɛ́n ndyééd éhɛlɛɛ́-sɛ ékwɔ̄g enɛ́n ndun e mod?”  
\v 10 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ ábe bembapɛɛ aá, “Nyéláa ábê bad, bédyɛɛ ásē.” Nkəə́kəə ambud abɛ́ á pɛd e ádê abwɔ́g a hǒm. Né-ɔɔ́, ábê bad bésyə̄ə̄l bêndyɛɛ́ ásē. Á amute-tê wê, baachóm bébédé dyam eʼkə́lé éʼtáan.  
\v 11 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ átédé ábê eʼwɛle, ásāgnān Dyǒb, boŋ ábē bembapɛɛ békabpé bad. Ambɛ̌l melemlem ne échê súu. Mod-tɛ́ɛ́ andyɛ́ ngáne áhɛ́déʼáá.  
\v 12 Áde bɔ́ moosyəə́l bémáá akód, Yesuɛ anláá ábē bembapɛɛ aá, “Nyélad ndyééd echě elyəgé ásē. Ndyééd ké pɔ́g eebébéʼ.”  
\v 13 Né-ɔɔ́, áde bémáá adyɛ́ bênlǎd ndyééd echě enlyə̌g ásē, enlón eʼlóŋ dyôm ne éʼbɛ.  
\v 14 Anyín áde ábē bad bényíné ḿmɛ́n menyáké ḿme Yesuɛ ábɛ́lé bénhɔ̄b bán “Ne mbále, nkal eʼdəə́dəŋ awě bénhɔ̄bpē bán ǎpɛ̄ á nkǒŋsé mɔ́ nɛ́n.”  
\v 15 Yesuɛ ambíí aá béhɛde mɔ́ akób ânyáged mɔ́ âbɛ́ kə̂ŋ. Né-ɔɔ́, antǐm ámbīd á ekone-mîn. 
\s1 Yesuɛ akií á mendíb mîn 
\r (Mat 14.22-33; Mak 6.45-52) 
\p  
\v 16 Ngukɛ́l, bembapɛɛ ábe Yesuɛ bênkɛ̌ á edib.  
\v 17 Bênsɔ́l á bɔ̌lɛ-tê, béchabpé edib, bétimnád á Kapenahum. Ehíntɛ́n êmmǎd apɛ áde Yesuɛ éēpédɛ́ɛ́ wɛ́ɛ bédíí.  
\v 18 Enɛ́n póndé epub é ngíne étóméʼáá, épuutád-tɛ mendíb áte.  
\v 19 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́ bembapɛɛ bêmmǎd akɛ ké máyl méláán kéʼɛ méniin, dɔ́ɔ bényíné Yesuɛ akag á mendíb mîn, átimnád bɛnbɛn ne ábab bɔ̌lɛ. Mbwɔ́g ń ngíne ménkōb bɔ́.  
\v 20 Boŋ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé, nyéebááʼ.”  
\v 21 Hɛ́ɛ bétédé mɔ́ á bɔ̌lɛ-tê ne menyiŋge, ábwɔ̄g-ábwɔ̄g bépɛ̄ɛ̄n-nɛ bɔ̌lɛ á nkin wɛ́ɛ békágéʼáá. 
\s1 Yesuɛ mɔ́ adé ewɛle éche ébageʼ aloŋgé 
\p  
\v 22 Nɛ́ɛ bǐn éʼsáŋgé, ndun e mod echě enlyə̌g á múde mé edib ḿmíníí wɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ne ábē bembapɛɛ bémbīdtē, bênchem bán, ngukɛ́l echě entóm, bɔ̌lɛ eʼhɔ́g běnpɛn bɔ́ɔ bémbɛ̄ áhed. Bémbīī-ʼɛ bán Yesuɛ enkênsɔ́nlé áwēd-te ne ábē bembapɛɛ. Bémbīī bán ábē bembapɛɛ běnpɛn bɔ́ɔ bênkɛ̌.  
\v 23 Myɔ̌lɛ mémpēe ḿme mémbīd á dyad á Tiberia mêmpɛ̌ á nkin mé edib bɛnbɛn ne hǒm áde ene ndun e mod éndyɛ̄ɛ̄ eʼwɛle ámbīd echě Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́ ámáá Dyǒb aságnɛn.  
\v 24 Áde ene ndun e mod ényíné nɛ́n bán, Yesuɛ ne ábē bembapɛɛ béesaá áhed, bénsɔ̄l á myɔ̌lɛ-tê wɛ̂, békɛ̄ á Kapenahum, âkɛ dé ahɛd Yesuɛ. 
\p  
\v 25 Áde ábê bad bépédé á pɛd e edib eníníí, bényīn Yesuɛ. Bênsɛdéd mɔ́ bán, “A-meléed, póndé ehéé épédé hɛ́n?”  
\v 26 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, saké menyáké ḿmě ḿbɛ́lé ńkə́ə́ boŋ nyéhɛdé mɛ. Nyêhɛde mɛ áyə̄le eʼwɛle ábe nyédyédé boŋ nyêkód-tɛ.  
\v 27 Nyéewág ntǔ áyə̄le ndyééd echě ebɔɔdeʼ, boŋ nyéwâg ntǔ áyə̄le ndyééd echě ebâg abɛ́ ne abɛ́ á aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ, chɔ́-ʼaá ebage aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ. Ene ndyééd chɔ́ɔ Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ ábɛɛ́. Mɔ́ɔ Dyǒb Titɛ́ɛ áhédé eʼchem aá ábɛl nɛ̂.”  
\v 28 Dɔ́ɔ ábê bad bênsɛdéd Yesuɛ bánken, “Cheé sétə́ŋgɛ́né abɛl, âbɛl boŋ sébɛl mekan ḿme Dyǒb áhɛdɛɛ́ aá, sébɛl?”  
\v 29 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Dyam áde Dyǒb áhɛdɛɛ́ aá nyébɛl ádíi âdúbe mɛ awě álómé.”  
\v 30 Bêntimtɛ́n Yesuɛ bán, “Menyáké méhéé wɛ́bɛnlé ḿme sɛ́nyīnnē boŋ sêdúbé wɛ. Cheé mmǒn wɛ́koŋgé abɛl?  
\v 31 Ábɛ̄d betaa béndyɛ̄ mána á ehyáŋge ngáne éténlédé á kálag e Dyǒb nɛ́n bán, ‘Ambag bɔ́ eʼwɛle ábe éʼbídé ádyōb aá bédyɛ̂.’ ”  
\v 32 Yesuɛ anhɔ́b aá, “Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, saké Mosɛɛ mɔ́ɔmbɛ̌ nyé ewɛle éche ehúú ádyōb, boŋ echem Sáŋ mɔ́ɔmbɛ̌ nyé ewɛle éche ehúú ádyōb.  
\v 33 Áyə̄le mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé échê ewɛle éche Dyǒb ábágé, échě éhúú ádyōb, echě ábagɛɛ́ baányoŋ bé nkǒŋsé aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ.” 
\p  
\v 34 Dɔ́ɔ bélâŋgɛɛ́ Yesuɛ bán, “A-Sáŋ, bagé sé échɛ́n ewɛle póndé ésyə̄ə̄l.”  
\v 35 Yesuɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé ewɛle éche ébage aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ. Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě apedé áwêm, nzaa éekóbpé mɔ́ ámpē. Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adúbpé mɛ, píd éekóbpé mɔ́ ámpē.  
\v 36 Nláŋgé nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́ nyênyíné mɛ boŋ nyéedúbpɛɛ́ mɛ.  
\v 37 Bad bésyə̄ə̄l ábe echem Sáŋ ábágé mɛ, bɛ́pɛ̌ áwêm. Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě apedé áwêm, méebáŋgé mɔ́ akob.  
\v 38 Áyə̄le meebídɛɛ́ ádyōb âbɛl ngáne ébóŋnédé mɛ. Mpedé âbɛl ngáne ébóŋnédé echem Sáŋ awě alómé mɛ.  
\v 39 Boŋ nɛ́n ádíi mewêmtɛn ḿme ane awě alómé mɛ, aá átîntê bad bésyə̄ə̄l ábe ábágé mɛ, meebɔ́dé ké nhɔ́g, boŋ aá ḿpuud bɔ́ moosyəə́l á epun é asóg.  
\v 40 Echem Sáŋ ahɛde aá moosyəə́l awě anyíné mwǎn, adúbé-ʼɛ mɔ́, ákud aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ. Mɛ̌puúd-tɛ bɔ́ á epun é asóg.” 
\p  
\v 41 Ábê bad bé Israɛl bêmbootéd anyoo áte tə̂ŋgɛne Yesuɛ, ahɔ́b áde áhɔ́bé aá, “Mɛɛ́ ndé ewɛle éche ébídé ádyōb.”  
\v 42 Hɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ béhɔ́bɛɛ́ bánken, “Saá Yesuɛ, mwǎn awě Josɛbɛ nɛ́n-ɛ? Ngɔ́mē debíí sáá ne nyaŋ? Chán-nɔ̄ áhɛlɛsɛ áhɔ̄bē aá mɔ́bīdē ádyōb?”  
\v 43 Yesuɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nyésôg anyoo áte.  
\v 44 Modmod éēhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ ápɛ áwêm, ésebán Titɛ́ɛ awě alómé mɛ apɛɛ́né mɔ́ áwêm. Mɛ̌puúd-tɛ mɔ́ á epun é asóg.  
\v 45 Éténlédé ngáne bekal béʼdəə́dəŋ béhɔ́bé nɛ́n bán ‘Dyǒb dɛ́yə̄gēd bɔ́ moosyəə́l.’ Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě awógeʼ, áyə̄gkē-ʼɛ wɛ́ɛ Titɛ́ɛ, apag áwêm.  
\v 46 Éesaá nɛ́n bán, mod ké nhɔ́g akɛ́nyīn Titɛ́ɛ. Ane awě abídé wɛ́ɛ Dyǒb mwěmpɛn mɔ́ɔ akɛ́nyīn Titɛ́ɛ.  
\v 47 Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adúbpé mɛ ǎkǔd aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ.  
\v 48 Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé ewɛle éche ébage aloŋgé.  
\v 49 Ábɛ̄n betaa béndyɛ̄ mána á ehyáŋge, boŋ ké nɛ̂, bénwɛ̄.  
\v 50 Boŋ ewɛle éche ébídé ádyōb édé nyaa echě kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adyédé chɔ́ éewáá.  
\v 51 Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé ewɛle éche ébage aloŋgé éche ébídé ádyōb. Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adyédé échê ewɛle, ǎbɛ̄ á aloŋgé á ngíndé ne á ngíndé. Échɛ́n ewɛle éche mɛ́bɛɛ́ nyé édíi echem yə̌l echě mɛ́bɛ̌ âbɛl boŋ ńkɔde aloŋgé dé nkǒŋsé.” 
\p  
\v 52 Áde ábê bad béwógé nɛ̂, bênlǐŋ, běn ne běn bébootéd-tɛ mpentɛn ń ngíne, bésɛdté bánken, “Chán anɛ́n mod áhɛle atéd eche yə̌l, ábɛ syánē aá dédyâg?”  
\v 53 Yesuɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, nzé nyéedyéde yə̌l e Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ nyêmwɛ́-ʼɛ ḿmē mekií, nyéekudté aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ.  
\v 54 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adyédé echem yə̌l, amwɛ́-ʼɛ ḿmêm mekií, ǎkǔd aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ, mɛ̌puúd-tɛ mɔ́ á epun é asóg.  
\v 55 Áyə̄le echem yə̌l chɔ̂ ekǒŋté ndyééd abɛ́, ḿmêm mekií-ʼɛ mékoŋ mmíítéd abɛ́.  
\v 56 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adyédé echem yə̌l, amwɛ́-ʼɛ ḿmêm mekií, alyəgé adé ne mɛ, mɛ-ʼɛ nlyəgé ndé ne mɔ́.  
\v 57 Titɛ́ɛ awě akəə boŋ bad bébɛ́ á aloŋgé, mɔ́ alómé mɛ, mɔ́ akəə́-ʼɛ boŋ mbɛ́ á aloŋgé. Melemlem nɛ́ɛ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adyédé echem yə̌l, mɛ́bɛnlé abɛ́ á aloŋgé.  
\v 58 Né-ɔɔ́, mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé ewɛle eche ébídé ádyōb. Meésaá nɛ̂ŋgáne ewɛle éche ábɛ̄n betaa béndyɛ̄ɛ̄, boŋ ké nɛ̂ béwɛ́. Boŋ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě ǎdyɛ̄ echem yə̌l ǎbɛ̄ á aloŋgé á ngíndé ne ngíndé.” 
\p  
\v 59 Yesuɛ anhɔ́b ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l áde áyə́gtéʼáá á ndáb e mekáne e bad bé Israɛl á Kapenahum. 
\s1 Eʼyale ábe Yesuɛ éʼpɛɛneʼ aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ 
\p  
\v 60 Áde bad híin ábe béhídéʼáá Yesuɛ béwógé ḿmɛ́n mekan bénhɔ̄b bán, “Ádɛ́n ayə́ge álɛ́lé ahíd. Nzɛ́ɛ́ ahɛle ákob ene ndín e dyam?”  
\v 61 Yesuɛ ambíí aá, bényoŋge áte áyə̄l echê, né-ɔɔ́ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nɛ̂ áwag nyé á yə̌l-ɛ?  
\v 62 Chán-nɔ̄ nyɛ́hɔ̄bpē áde nyɛ́nyīnnē Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ apummeʼ ámbīd ámīn wɛ́ɛ ámbīdtē!  
\v 63 Edəə́dəŋ é Dyǒb chɔ́ɔ ébageʼ aloŋgé. Ekob é yə̌l éesaá dyamdyam. Eʼyale ábe ńláŋgé nyé éʼdíi edəə́dəŋ ne aloŋgé.  
\v 64 Boŋ ké nɛ̂, nyé doŋge á bad nyéedúbpɛɛ́.” (Bootya á póndé éche Yesuɛ ábóótédé ayə́ged, ambíí bad ábe béedúbé, abíí-ʼɛ mod awě ǎsōm mɔ́.)  
\v 65 Ambád ahɔ́b aá, “Nɛ́n dɔ́ɔ ákə́ə́ boŋ nláá nyé mɛɛ́ modmod eéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ ápɛ awêm kə́ə́ŋ né echem Sáŋ abɛlé boŋ ápɛ̄ áwêm.” 
\p  
\v 66 Bootya enɛ póndé nɛ̂ dênkə̌ŋ bad ábe béhídéʼáá Yesuɛ bésóg mɔ́ ahíd, bétīm-mɛ ámbīd.  
\v 67 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ásɛdtɛɛ́ ábē bembapɛɛ dyôm ne bébɛ aá, “Nyémpē nyêhɛde atim ámbīd-ɛ?”  
\v 68 Simɔn Petro ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “A-Sáŋ, wɛ́ɛ nzɛ́ɛ́ sɛ́kɛɛ́? Wɛ-ɛɛ́ ewóó eʼyale ábe éʼkəəʼ boŋ mod ákūd aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ.  
\v 69 Sêdúbpé sêbíí-ʼɛ bán, wɛ-ɛɛ́ edé Ane-awě-Asáá awě abídé wɛ́ɛ Dyǒb.”  
\v 70 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ákwɛntanné bɔ́ aá, “Éesaá mbále bán mpwɛdé nyé bad dyôm ne bébɛ-yɛ? Boŋ ké nɛ̂, nyé mod nhɔ́g adíi mod a Satan.”  
\v 71 Judasɛ, mwǎn a Simɔn Iskariɔdɛ mɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ áhɔ́béʼáá. Kénɛ́ɛ ámbɛ̄ɛ̄ mbapɛɛ nhɔ́g átîntê e bembapɛɛ dyôm ne bébɛ, mɔ́ ankɛ̌ Yesuɛ ntúrɛ́. 
\c 7  
\s1 Yesuɛ ne baányaŋ 
\p  
\v 1 Ámbīd e ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l, Yesuɛ akagéʼáá mebwɔ́g ne mebwɔ́g á mbwɔ́g e Galilia. Enkêndəŋgé akɛ á mbwɔ́g e Judeya áyə̄le bad bé Israɛl béhɛ́déʼáá mɔ́ awúu.  
\v 2 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, Ngande e Eʼbem \f + \fr 7:2 \fk Ngande e Eʼbem: \ft ebédɛ́ɛ ngande echě bad bé Israɛl bébɛ́léʼáá âkamtɛn póndé echě ábāb betaa bédyɛ́ɛ́ʼáá á eʼbem-tê áde bébédé á ehyáŋge, áde béhídté á Egipto.\f* e bad bé Israɛl embɛ́ bɛnbɛn.  
\v 3 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ baányaŋ bélâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ bán, “Etə́ŋgɛ́né ádɛ́n abwɔ́g á hǒm ahide, ékɛ á mbwɔ́g e Judeya âbɛl bad ábe béhíde wɛ bényîn menyáké ḿme ébɛlɛɛ́.  
\v 4 Mod eébɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄ nsɔ́n á eʼkoŋnéd-te, nzé ahɛde aá mɔ́byɛ́ɛn. Ngáne ébɛlɛɛ́ ḿmɛ́n mekan mésyə̄ə̄l ébɛl nkǒŋsé ńsyə̄ə̄l ḿbíi wɛ.”  
\v 5 (Ké Yesuɛ baányaŋ bénkêndúbɛ́ɛ́ mɔ́.)  
\v 6 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “Echem póndé eépédɛ́ɛ́. Boŋ ne nyé, echɛn póndé edé póndé ésyə̄ə̄l.  
\v 7 Nkǒŋsé méehɛlɛ́ɛ́-sɛ ńkɔ̄ɔ̄ nyé. Boŋ ńkɔ́ɔ́ mɛ áyə̄le mpanlad bɔ́ ḿmāb mewusé áte.  
\v 8 Nyébɔ́ nyékag á ngande. Méekaá áwed áyə̄le echem póndé eépédɛ́ɛ́.”  
\v 9 Yesuɛ amaá-ʼaá ahɔ́b nɛ̂, abɛ́ abɛ́ á Galilia. 
\s1 Yesuɛ akií Ngande e Eʼbem á Jerusalɛm 
\p  
\v 10 Ámbīd e póndé áde Yesuɛ baányaŋ bémáá akɛ á Ngande e Eʼbem, mɔ́mpē ankɛ̌ áwed. Boŋ enkênlúmédté yə̌l. Ankɛ̌ nyaa echě bad bénkêmbííʼɛ́ ndín e mod echě ádíí.  
\v 11 Benkamlɛnɛ bé Israɛl béhɛ́déʼáá mɔ́ á ngande-tê, bésɛdté bánken, “Héé múmɔ́ ádíí?”  
\v 12 Átîntê e ndun e mod echě embɛ́ á ngande-tê wɛ̂, doŋge á bad béhɔ́béʼáá bán, “Adíi mod a bwâm,” ábíníí-ʼɛ bán, “Aáy, adoge bad dogɛ́n.”  
\v 13 Boŋ bɔ́ modmod bénkêmbídédté yə̌l áwed áyə̄le bébááʼáá bad bémbáá bé Israɛl. 
\p  
\v 14 Áde ngande ékwógé apɛ átîntê, Yesuɛ ankɛ̌ asɔ́l á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb, ábootéd ayə́ged.  
\v 15 Yə̌l enkɔ́m benkamlɛnɛ áte bwâmbwam tə̂ŋgɛne ádē ayə́ge. Né-ɔɔ́, bênsɛdéd bánken, “Chán anɛ́n mod ámwédé ḿmɛ́n mam mésyə̄ə̄l abíi áde éekiiʼɛ́ á esukɛ́lɛ é mbéndé?”  
\v 16 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ákwɛntanné bɔ́ aá, “Ayə́ged áde ń'yə́gtɛɛ́ déesaá ádêm. Ádíi áde mod awě alómé mɛ.  
\v 17 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě awémtɛ́né abɛl ngáne Dyǒb áhɛdɛɛ́, ǎbīī ké ádêm ayə́ge ahúú ne Dyǒb kéʼɛ áhúú ne mměn.  
\v 18 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě ahɔ́bne echě kunze, abɛle nɛ̂ âhɛde eche yə̌l edúbé. Boŋ mod awě ahɛdteʼ mod awě alómé mɔ́ edúbé, asáá nlém á abum, eésaá mod a metóm.  
\v 19 Éesaá mbále nɛ́n bán, Mosɛɛ abagé nyé mbéndé-yɛ? Ké nɛ̂, nyé modmod eehídɛ́ɛ́ mbéndé éched. Cheé ékə́ə́ boŋ nyéhɛdé mɛ awúu?”  
\v 20 Dɔ́ɔ ene ndun e mod ékwɛntanné mɔ́ bán, “Edəə́dəŋ é mbéb édé wɛ áte. Benzébádé béhɛde wɛ awúu?”  
\v 21 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Nsɔ́n nhɔ́g ḿme ḿbɛ́lé, ńkɔ́mté nyé moosyəə́l yə̌l áte.  
\v 22 Mosɛɛ ambɛ̌ nyé mbéndé aá, nyéyage ábɛn bǎn (kénɛ́ɛ édíí bán, saké Mosɛɛ mɔ́ɔmbootéd. Ábɛ̄n betaa bɔ́ɔ bêmbootéd). Né-ɔɔ́, nyêyage bad á Mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me-áte.  
\v 23 Nzé béyágé mod á mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me-áte, âbɛl béēbōōʼ mbéndé e Mosɛɛ, cheé ékə́ə́ boŋ nyéliŋné mɛ áyə̄le ńdídé mod bwâm á mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me-áte.  
\v 24 Nyéekáádté dyam áde ḿbɛ́lé ngáne nyényíné, nyékáad ngáne éhɛdnadté.” 
\s1 Bán Yesuɛ mɔ̂dé Ane awě bésinɛɛ́-yɛ? 
\p  
\v 25 Hɛ́ɛ dɔ́ɔ doŋge á bad bé Jerusalɛm béhɔ́bɛɛ́ bánken, “Saá mod awě béhɛdɛɛ́ awúu mɔ̂ nɛ́n-ɛ?  
\v 26 Nyénɔnéʼ, akanle bad á tə̂l e ékwɛ́ɛ, bad bémbáá béesaá-ʼaá mɔ́ dyamdyam aláa. Kapɔ́g bébíí bán ne mbále, mɔ̂dé Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté-yōō!  
\v 27 Boŋ éehɛlɛ́ɛ́-sɛ ébɛ́ nɛ̂, áyə̄le debíí bán póndé echě Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté ápɛɛ́, modmod éebííʼɛ́ wɛ́ɛ ábídé. Debíí wɛ́ɛ anɛ́n mod ábídé.”  
\v 28 Yesuɛ ambɛ́ áyə̄gtēʼ á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb. Áde áyə́gtɛɛ́ dɔ́ɔ áchə́gté ehɔ́b ámīn aá, “Ɛɛ, nyêbíí mɛ bwâm, nyêbíí-ʼɛ wɛ́ɛ ḿbídé. Meépedɛɛ́ hɛ́n ne mměn. Ane awě alómé mɛ adé mbále. Nyéebíiʼɛ́ mɔ́,  
\v 29 boŋ mɛ pɛn mbíí mɔ́ áyə̄le áwē dɔ́ɔ mbídé, mɔ́-ʼaá alómé me.”  
\v 30 Áde áhɔ́bé nɛ̂, béhɛ́déʼáá mɔ́ akób, boŋ modmod enkêmbánné mɔ́ ké ekáá á yə̌l, áyə̄le eche póndé enkêmpaá.  
\v 31 Ké nɛ̂ bad híin átîntê ene ndun e mod béndūbē mɔ́. Béhɔ́béʼáá bánken, “Áde Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté ápɛɛ́, ǎbɛ̌l eʼchemléd bé menyáké, ḿme ńtómé ḿme anɛ́n mod ábɛ́lé-yɛ?” 
\s1 Befarisia bélómé bad âkób Yesuɛ 
\p  
\v 32 Befarisia bénwōg nɛ́ɛ bad bényoŋgɛɛ́ áte, béhɔ́bɛɛ́ ḿmɛ́n mekan tə̂ŋgɛne Yesuɛ. Né-ɔɔ́ bɔ́ɔbɛ beprisɛ bémbáá bénlōm bembəledɛ âkób mɔ́.  
\v 33 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “Ndíi ndé ne nyé, boŋ mwǎmpīn ḿ póndé mɛ̌sū ámbīd wɛ́ɛ ane awě alómé mɛ.  
\v 34 Ámbīd enɛ̂, nyɛ́ɛ̄hɛ̌d mɛ, boŋ nyéenyínné, wɛ́ɛ mɛ́bɛ̄ɛ̄-ʼɛ nyéehɛnlé apɛ áhed.”  
\v 35 Nɛ̂ dêmbɛ̌l benkamlɛnɛ bésɛdté nhɔ́g ne aníníí bánken, “Héé anɛ́n mod múmɔ́ áhɛdɛɛ́ akɛ, wɛ́ɛ syánē déehɛnlé mɔ́ anyín? Ahɛde akɛ á aloŋ á Grikia wɛ́ɛ ábɛ̄d bad bédíí á ebwɔ́g âyə́ged bad bé Grikia-yɛ?  
\v 36 Ahɔ́beʼ aá dɛɛ́hɛ̌d mɔ́ boŋ déenyínné mɔ́. Aá déehɛnlé-ʼɛ apɛ wɛ́ɛ mɔ́bɛ̄ɛ̄. Cheé nɛ̂ álûmtɛɛ́?” 
\s1 Eʼdíb bé mendíb mé aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ 
\p  
\v 37 Epun é asóg é ngande éche éntōmtɛ̄n etógnɛ́n abɛ́ áyə̄le ene ngande émpɛ̌. Yesuɛ antyéém ámīn, dɔ́ɔ áchə́gté ehɔ́b ámīn, áhɔ̄bē aá, “kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě píd ékóbé áhyag áwêm áhyɛ ámwɛ̂ mendíb.  
\v 38 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adúbpé mɛ, Kálag e Dyǒb ehɔ́be aá, ‘eʼdíb bé mendíb mé aloŋgé bɛ́bīdē mɔ́ áte éʼsobpe.’ ”  
\v 39 Edəə́dəŋ éche Ésáá chɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ áhɔ́béʼáá. Chɔ́ɔ bad ábe béndūbē mɔ́ béntə̄ŋgɛ̄nnē akud. Ene póndé né Edəə́dəŋ éche Ésáá éēpēdɛ̄ɛ̄ wɛ́ɛ ábê bad áyə̄le ene póndé ne Dyǒb déēlūmtɛ̄ɛ̄ ehúmé éche Yesuɛ. 
\s1 Bad békábné áte á atɔ́n áde Yesuɛ 
\p  
\v 40 Doŋge á bad átîntê ene ndun e mod ábe bénwōg nɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ ḿmɛ́n mekan bénhɔ̄b bán, “Ne mbále, anɛ́n mod adíi nkal éʼdəə́dəŋ awě ǎpɛ̌.”  
\v 41 Bad bémpēe béhɔ́béʼáá bán, “Mɔ̂dé Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté awě ǎpɛ̌.” Ké nɛ̂, bémpēe béhɔ́béʼáá bán, “Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté eéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ abíd á Galilia.  
\v 42 Éténlédé á Kálag e Dyǒb nɛ́n bán, Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté ǎbīd á túmbé e Dabid á dyad á Bɛtɛlhɛm wɛ́ɛ Dabidɛ ámbīdtē.”  
\v 43 Né-ɔɔ́, bad bênkabɛ́n áte á atɔ́n áde Yesuɛ.  
\v 44 Doŋge á bad béhɛ́déʼáá mɔ́ akób boŋ modmod enkêmbánné mɔ́ ké ekáá á yə̌l. 
\s1 Baámbáá bé Israɛl béekwɛntɛnɛɛ́ Yesuɛ adúbe 
\p  
\v 45 Kə́ə́ŋne ásɔ̄g bembəledɛ bé Ndáb-e-Dyǒb bêntǐm wɛ́ɛ beprisɛ bémbáá ne Befarisia. Hɛ́ɛ beprisɛ bémbáá ne Befarisia bésɛdtɛɛ́ bɔ́ bánken, “Cheé ékə́ə́ boŋ nyéepɛɛne mɔ́ hɛ́n?”  
\v 46 Hɛ́ɛ ábê bembəledɛ béhɔ́bɛɛ́ bán, “Modmod eéhɔ́bɛ́ɛ́ ndín é mam éche anɛ́n mod áhɔ́bɛɛ́.”  
\v 47 Dɔ́ɔ Befarisia bésɛdtɛɛ́ bɔ́ bánken, “Nɛ́dē ane mod adogé kə́ə́ŋne nyémpē-yɛ?  
\v 48 Nyêkényīn nɛ́ɛ mod ambáá kéʼɛ Farisia nhɔ́g ádúbpé mɔ̂? Ké nhɔ́g eédúbpɛ́ɛ́ mɔ́.  
\v 49 Enɛ́n ndun e mod eebíiʼɛ́ mbéndé e Mosɛ. Né-ɔɔ́ ebómán édé ne bɔ́.”  
\v 50 Farisia nhɔ́g awě béchə́géʼáá bán Nikodemusɛ awě ansébé Yesuɛ akɛ dé anyín, anláá bɔ́ aá,  
\v 51 “Eche syánē mbéndé eébagɛɛ́ kunze nɛ́n dékɔ́gsɛn mod áde déekáadtɛɛ́ mɔ́, âwóglɛn dyam áde ábɛ́lé.”  
\v 52 Áde áhɔ́bé nɛ̂, bêntimtɛ́n mɔ́ bánken, “We ámpē ebídé á Galilia-yɛ? Hɛ̌d áte á Kálag e Dyǒb, wɛ̌nyīn nɛ́n wɛ̌ nkal éʼdəə́dəŋ eebídɛ́ɛ́ á Galilia.” 
\s1 Mmwaád awě akábé asón 
\p  
\v 53 Ámbīd enɛ̂ moosyəə́l ansú áwe ndáb. 
\c 8  
\nb  
\v 1 Yesuɛ pɛn ankɛ̌ á Ekone é Menzab.  
\v 2 Nɛ́ɛ bǐn éʼsáŋgé mbwɛmbwɛ, antǐm ámbīd á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb. Ndun e mod empɛ̌ áwē. Andyɛɛ́ ásē ábootéd bɔ́ ayə́ged.  
\v 3 Bemeléede bé mbéndé ne Befarisia bêmpɛɛ́n mmwaád nhɔ́g áwē, awě békóbé nɛ́ɛ ákábɛɛ́ asón á ndáb e eʼwóŋgé. Béntīī ane mmwaád átîntê echâb,  
\v 4 boŋ bélāŋgē Yesuɛ bán, “A-meléed, békóbé anɛ́n mmwaád nɛ́ɛ ákábɛɛ́ asón á ndáb e eʼwóŋgé.  
\v 5 Á mbéndé eche syánē, Mosɛɛ anhɔ́b aá, enɛ́n ndín e mmwaád bélûm chɔ́ meláá kə́ə́ŋ áwɛ̂, chán-nɔ̄ wɛ-ʼɛ éhɔ́bé?”  
\v 6 Bênsɛdéd mɔ́ nɛ̂ âhíi mɔ́ melám, âbɛl nɛ́n békóbɛn mɔ́ awusé. Boŋ Yesuɛ anwúlɛ́n ásē, ábootéd bwěm atel á ndɔɔb-tê ne ábē eʼmii.  
\v 7 Áde bébádnɛ́né mɔ́ asɛded, antíí yə̌l ámīn, aláá bɔ́ aá, “Nyé ké ahéé awě eébɛ́lé mbéb ábɛ̂ mod aʼsó âlúm mɔ́ meláá.”  
\v 8 Anwúlɛ́n mɔ́ ásē ámpē áteléʼ ábē bwɛ̌m á ndɔɔb-tê.  
\v 9 Áde ábɛ̂ bad béwógé nɛ̂ bêmbootéd ahide nhɔ́gē-nhɔ́gē. Bad bémbáá bɔ́ɔ bénsēbē akɛ, boŋ bésad béhīdēʼ. Kə́ə́ŋ ne á asóg Yesuɛ mwěmpɛn anlyə̌g, ane mmwaád-tɛ abɛ́ atyéém áhed.  
\v 10 Áde Yesuɛ átíídé yə̌l ámīn, dɔ́ɔ ásɛdtɛɛ́ ane mmwaád aá, “Á-mmwaád nɛ́n, héé bad ábe bépɛ́ɛ́né wɛ hɛ́n bédíí? Modmod eélyəgɛɛ́ hɛ́n awě ahɔ́bé aá béwúu wɛ-yɛ?”  
\v 11 Ane mmwaád ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “A Sáŋ modmod.” Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Né mɛ̌mpē méehɔ́bpé mɛɛ́ béwúu wɛ. Kǎg wɛ, boŋ weébɛ̄lē mbéb ámpē.”\f + \fr 8:11 \ft Ekud e kálag éʼsó éewóoʼɛ́ échɛ́n epɛd (7.53-8.11). \f* 
\s1 Yesuɛ mɔ̂dé eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde bé nkǒŋsé 
\p  
\v 12 Yesuɛ anláá ábê bad ámpē aá, “Mɛɛ́ ndé eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde éʼ bad bé nkǒŋsé. Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě ahíde mɛ, éekaá á ehíntɛ́n-tê, boŋ ǎkǔd eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde ábe éʼbageʼ aloŋgé.”  
\v 13 Dɔ́ɔ Befarisia bélâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ bán, “Ebíde echoŋ yə̌l mbóŋ, né-ɔɔ́ mbóŋ echôŋ eékobnedɛɛ́.”  
\v 14 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Kénɛ́ɛ mměn ḿbídɛɛ́ echem yə̌l mbóŋ, echem mbóŋ edé mbále, áyə̄le mbíí wɛ́ɛ ḿbídé, mbíí-ʼɛ wɛ́ɛ ńkagké, boŋ nyé, nyéebíiʼɛ́ wɛ́ɛ mbídé, nyéebíi-ʼáa wɛ́ɛ ńkagké.  
\v 15 Nyêkáadte bad á nyaa e moonyoŋ. Meekáádtɛ́ɛ́ modmod.  
\v 16 Ké menkáád-tɛ ké káádtɛ́n, echêm mbakú edé mbále, áyə̄le meekáádtɛ́ɛ́ ne mměn, boŋ nkáadte, ne ane awě alómé mɛ.  
\v 17 Nɛ́ɛ béhúde ké nɛ̂ áte, á mbéndé echɛ̂n, éténlédé nɛ́n bán nzé bad bébɛ bébídé dyam mbóŋ, boŋ béhɔ́bé melemlem mé dyam, né ene mbóŋ edé mbóŋ e mbále.  
\v 18 Nyébíi-ɔɔ́ nɛ́n bán nwóó mbóŋ ébɛ, mměn ne mod awě alómé mɛ, awě adé echem Sáŋ.”  
\v 19 Hɛ́ɛ dɔ́ɔ Befarisia bésɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ bán, “Héé sóó ádíí?” Ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Nyéebíiʼɛ́ mɛ, nyéebíi-ʼáa ké echem Sáŋ. Nzé nyêmbíí mɛ, né nyêbíí kə́ə́ŋne echem Sáŋ.” 
\p  
\v 20 Yesuɛ anhɔ́b ábɛ́n eʼyale áde áyə́gtɛɛ́ á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb-te, bɛnbɛn ne wɛ́ɛ békoŋgɛɛ́ mɔné. Boŋ modmod enkênkóbpé mɔ́, áyə̄le eche póndé echě békóbɛɛ́ mɔ́ enkêmpaá. 
\p  
\v 21 Yesuɛ anláá ábê bad ámpē aá, “Mɛ̌kɛ̌, nzé mmaá-ʼɛ akɛ, nyɛ́ɛ̄hɛ̌d mɛ, boŋ nyéenyínné, né-ɔɔ́ nyɛ́ɛ̄wɛ̄ áwɛn mbéb-te. Wɛ́ɛ mɛ́bɛ̄ɛ̄, nyéehɛnlé apɛ áhed.”  
\v 22 Hɛ́ɛ bad bémbáá bé Israɛl bésɛdtɛɛ́ bán, “Ahɔ́beʼ aá, wɛ́ɛ mɔ́kɛɛ́ aá syánē déehɛnlé apɛ áhed, múmɔ́ ahɛde yə̌l awúu-yɛ?”  
\v 23 Anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nyêdíi bad ábe bébídé ásē wɛ́n, boŋ mɛ pɛn, mbídé ámīn. Nyêbídé á nkǒŋsé wɛ́n, mɛ pɛn, meebídɛɛ́ á nkǒŋsé wɛ́n.”  
\v 24 Nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ ákə́ə́ boŋ ńlāŋgē nyé mɛɛ́, “Nyɛ́ɛ̄wɛ̄ áwɛn mbéb-te. Nzé nyéedúbpe bán, ‘Ndíi Mod Awě Ńdíí,’ né nyɛ́ɛ̄wɛ̄-ʼɛ áwɛn mbéb-te.”  
\v 25 Hɛ́ɛ bésɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ bánken, “Nzɛ́-módɛ́ édíí?” Dɔ́ɔ ákwɛntanné bɔ́ aá, “Nyaa e mod echě ńláŋgé nyé se á mbooted mɛɛ́ ndé chɔ́ɔ ńdíí.  
\v 26 Nwóó mam híin ahɔ́b tə̂ŋgɛne nyé, ne ákáad nyé. Boŋ mod awě alómé mɛ adíí mod a mbále, mekan ḿmě ńlâŋge-ʼáa nyé hɛ́n á nkǒŋsé médíi mekan ḿmě ńwógé áwē.”  
\v 27 Áde Yesuɛ áhɔ́bé nɛ̂, bénkênsóŋtɛ́nné bán Sáá awě adé ámīn mɔ́ɔ áhɔ́bɛɛ́.  
\v 28 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “Póndé echě nyɛ́madté Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ abane ámīn, dɔ́ɔ nyɛ́bīīʼɛ́ bán, ‘Ndé mod awě ńhɔ́bé mɛɛ́ ndé.’ Nyêbíí-ʼɛ bán, meébɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄ dyamdyam ne kunze echêm, boŋ dyam áde ńhɔ́bɛɛ́ ádíi dyam áde echem Sáŋ áyə́gté mɛ.  
\v 29 Ane awě alómé mɛ, adé-ʼɛ ne mɛ, eétɛdtɛɛ́ mměmpɛn, áyə̄le mbɛleʼ mekan ḿmě mébóŋnédé mɔ́.”  
\v 30 Bad híin ábe bénwōg nɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ ḿmɛ́n mekan, béndūbē mɔ́. 
\s1 Nzɛ́ɛ́ adé sáá awě bad bé Israɛl? 
\p  
\v 31 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ bad bé Israɛl ábe béndūbē mɔ́ aá, “Nzé nyêdíi nyêhídeʼ ádêm ayə́ge, né nyêkǒŋté ábêm bembapɛɛ abɛ́.  
\v 32 Né nyɛ́ɛ̄bīī mbále, né ene mbále ěhūd-tɛ nyé á mehaŋ-tê.”  
\v 33 Bênkwɛntɛ́n bán, “Sêdíi nchyáátɛ́n ḿme Abrahamɛ. Séēbédɛ́ɛ́-ʼáa ntâŋ a mod mbêd. Chán-nɔ̄ éhɛle éhɔ̄bē wɛɛ́ séebáá á mehaŋ-tê?”  
\v 34 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé mɛɛ́, kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě abɛle mbéb adíi ntâŋ a mbéb.  
\v 35 Ntâŋ eebágké á túmbé-te abɛ́ ne abɛ́, boŋ mwǎn a túmbé, adíi mwǎn a túmbé póndé ésyə̄ə̄l.  
\v 36 Né-ɔɔ́, nzé Mwǎn ahúdé nyé á mehaŋ-tê, né dyamdyam déetédté nyé ntâŋ ámpē.  
\v 37 Mbíí mɛɛ́ nyêdíi nchyáátɛ́n ḿme Abrahamɛ, boŋ ké nɛ̂, nyêhɛde mɛ awúu, áyə̄le nyéēhɛ̄dɛ̄ɛ̄ ádêm ayə́ge ahíd.  
\v 38 Nlâŋge nyé mekan ḿme echem Sáŋ álúmté mɛ. Nyé-ʼɛ nyêbɛle mekan ḿme echɛn sáŋ áláŋgé nyé.” 
\p  
\v 39 Bênkwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ bán, “Abrahamɛ adíi echɛd sáŋ.” Yesuɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nzé nyênkǒŋ bǎn ábe Abrahamɛ abɛ́, né nyêbɛleʼ mekan ḿme Abrahamɛ ábɛ́léʼáá.  
\v 40 Mekan mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme ńkémbɛnlé ńdíi âláa nyé mbále echě ńwógé wɛ́ɛ Dyǒb. Kénɛ̂, nyêhɛde mɛ awúu. Abrahamɛ eébɛleʼaá, enɛ́n ndín e dyam.  
\v 41 Nyêbɛle mekan ḿme echɛn sáŋ ábɛlɛɛ́.” Bênkwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ bán, “Dyǒb děmpɛn-ɛɛ́ séwóó nɛ́ɛ echɛd Sáŋ, béēchyáa-ʼáa sé á asón.”  
\v 42 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “Nzé Dyǒb dênkǒŋ echɛn Sáŋ abɛ́, né nyêdəə́ mɛ, áyə̄le ḿbídé wɛ́ɛ Dyǒb ndé-ʼɛ hɛ́n bɔɔb. Meépedɛɛ́ ne mměn, boŋ mɔ́ alómé mɛ.  
\v 43 Nzɔm echě ekəə́ boŋ nyéēhɛ̄dēʼ mɛ ehɔ́b awóg, edíi nyéēhɛ̄dɛ̄ɛ̄ ábêm eʼyale awóg.  
\v 44 Nyêdíi bǎn ábe echɛn sáŋ, Satanɛ, ḿme mewêmtɛn mɔ́-ʼaá nyédə́ə́ ahíd. Se á mbooted, adíi ane awě awúɛʼ bad, eékwógnédɛ́ɛ́ mbále mbêd, áyə̄le mbále eésaá mɔ́ áte. Nzé akale metóm, né abɛle ḿme nsɔ́n áyə̄le adíi nkal a metóm, abɛ́-ʼɛ sáá a metóm.  
\v 45 Nyéedúbpɛ́ɛ́ mɛ, áyə̄le nkanle nyé mbále.  
\v 46 Nyé ahéé ahɛle alúméd aá, mbɛlé mbéb? Nzé nkanle nyé mbále, cheé-ɔ̄ ékə́ə́ boŋ nyéedúbpé mɛ?  
\v 47 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě ahúú ne Dyǒb, awóge eyale é Dyǒb. Nzɔm echě ekəə́ boŋ nyéewóglán edíi, nyéesaá bǎn bé Dyǒb.” 
\s1 Bad bé Israɛl béekobɛɛ́ ayə́ge áde Yesuɛ 
\p  
\v 48 Hɛ́ɛ ábê bad bé Israɛl bétimtanné Yesuɛ bánken, “Éesaá mbále bán, sênkǎl mbále áde séhɔ́bé bán, edíi mod a Samaria, edəə́dəŋ é mbéb édé-ʼɛ wɛ áte-yɛ?”  
\v 49 Ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Edəə́dəŋ é mbéb eésaá mɛ áte. Mbage echem Sáŋ edúbé, boŋ nyépɛn nyéēbāgɛ̄ɛ̄ mɛ edúbé.  
\v 50 Mměn meéhɛ̄dtɛ̄ɛ̄ yə̌l edúbé, boŋ mod adé awě ahɛdeʼ aá ńkud edúbé, mɔ́-ʼaá, abage mbakú echě etə́ŋgɛ́né.  
\v 51 Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé mɛɛ́, kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě abɛleʼ chǒm-ɛ́ɛ ń'yə́gtɛɛ́, éewáá mbêd.”  
\v 52 Dɔ́ɔ ábê bad bélâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ bán, “Bɔɔb dɔ́ɔ sébíí bán, edəə́dəŋ é mbéb édé wɛ áte. Abrahamɛ anwɛ́, bekal béʼdəə́dəŋ bɔ́mpē bénwɛ̄. Boŋ bɔɔb éhɔ̄bē wɛɛ́ mod awě adúbpé wɛ, éewáá mbêd.  
\v 53 Echɛd sáŋ Abrahamɛ anwɛ́. Ewémtɛ́né wɛɛ́ mɔ́tōmē mɔ́-yɛ? Bekal-bé-eʼdəə́dəŋ bɔ́mpē bénwɛ̄. Nzɛ́-módɛ́ wɛwɛ éwêmtanné wɛɛ́ mɔ́dē?”  
\v 54 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ákwɛntanné bɔ́ aá, “Nzé nhɛdte echem yə̌l edúbé, né échê edúbé éesaá dyamdyam. Echem Sáŋ awě nyéhɔ́bɛɛ́ bán mɔ́ adé nyé sáá, mɔ́ abage mɛ edúbé.  
\v 55 Nyéēbīīʼɛ́ mɔ́ mbêd, boŋ mbíí mɔ́. Nzé nhɔ́bé mɛɛ́ meebíiʼɛ́ mɔ́, né ndé nkal a metóm nɛ́ɛ nyé. Boŋ mbíí mɔ́, mbɛle-ʼɛ mam ḿme áhɔ́bɛɛ́.  
\v 56 Echɛn sáŋ Abrahamɛ ambɛ́ menyiŋge aá, mɔ́ɔ̄nyīn epun éche mɛ́pɛɛ́, annyín-nɛ chɔ́, abɛ́-ʼɛ menyiŋge bwâmbwam.”  
\v 57 Dɔ́ɔ bésɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ bán, “Áde wéēpēdɛ̄ɛ̄ móom mé mwɛ́ métáan, wɛɛ́ mɔ́nyīnē Abrahamɛ-yɛ?”  
\v 58 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, byánán bɛ́chyāā Abrahamɛ, ‘Ndé.’ ”  
\v 59 Áde ábê bad béwógé nɛ̂, dɔ́ɔ bébóótédé meláá ahɛd, âlúm mɔ́. Boŋ Yesuɛ ansɔɔ́m, abíd-tɛ á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb. 
\c 9  
\s1 Yesuɛ achǒŋté mod awě béchyááné ndím 
\p  
\v 1 Áde Yesuɛ átómɛɛ́, dɔ́ɔ ányíné mod awě béchyááné ndím.  
\v 2 Dɔ́ɔ ábē bembapɛɛ bésɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ bán, “A-meléed, mbéb ḿme nzɛ́ɛ́ ńkə́ə́ boŋ béchyáá anɛ́n mod ne ndím? Mbéb ḿmē mwěn-ɛ, káa ḿme sáá bɔ́ nyaŋ?”  
\v 3 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Saké ḿme mbéb ńkə́ə́, saá-kaá ḿme sáá bɔ́ nyaŋ. Boŋ nɛ́n ábɛ́nlédé âbɛl ngíne e Dyǒb ébîd áwed áwē yə̌l.  
\v 4 Ngáne bǐn éʼdíi ényînnɛɛ́ ámīn, detə́ŋgɛ́né débɛl nsɔ́n ḿme ane awě álómé mɛ. Ehíntɛ́n ékwógé apɛ áde mod éehɛnlé nsɔ́n abɛl.  
\v 5 Bɔɔb áde ńdíí á nkǒŋsé, mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde bé nkǒŋsé.”  
\v 6 Áde Yesuɛ ámáá ahɔ́b nɛ̂, ansob aléed á ndɔɔb, atɔ́b dɔ́ boŋ áwɔ̄gtē ane mod a ndím á mǐd,  
\v 7 álāŋgē mɔ́ aá, “Kǎg, éwobe eʼsó á etoŋ é Silom” (ádê dǐn ádé nɛ́n bán, “Bélómé”). Né-ɔɔ́, ane mod ankɛ̌, áwōbē-ʼɛ mǐd. Antǐm ámbīd, ányînneʼ. 
\p  
\v 8 Hɛ́ɛ bad ábe bémbīī mɔ́ ne bad ábe bényínáá ngáne áchɔ́mɛɛ́ bwěm, bésɛdtɛɛ́ bán, “Saá anɛ́n mod ayɔ̌gké adyɛɛ ásē, áchɔ̄mē bwěm-ɛ?”  
\v 9 Doŋge dénhɔ̄b bán, “Mɔ̂dé,” ábíníí-ʼɛ bán, “Aáy! Awágne mɔ́ wágnɛ́n.” Boŋ ane mod mwěn anhɔ́b aá, “Mměn-ɛɛ́ ndé.”  
\v 10 Dɔ́ɔ bésɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ bán, “Chán-nɔ̄ émwédé abooted dé anyínɛn?”  
\v 11 Ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Mod awě béchəgɛɛ́ bán, Yesuɛ, antɔ́b elɔɔb, awɔ́géd mɛ chɔ́ á mǐd, aláá-ʼɛ mɛ aá ńkɛ á etoŋ é Silom, ńkɛ ńwobe mǐd. Né-ɔɔ́, menkɛ̌. Awobe áde ńwóbpé mǐd, ḿbootéd-tɛ anyínɛn.”  
\v 12 Bênsɛdéd mɔ́ bán, “Héé ane mod adíí?” Ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Meebíiʼɛ́.” 
\s1 Befarisia béhɛ́dé áte ngáne  //  Yesuɛ áchóŋté mod a ndím 
\p  
\v 13 Bênkɛɛ́n ane mod awě ankwɛ̌ ndím wɛ́ɛ Befarisia.  
\v 14 Epun éche Yesuɛ ántɔ̄bpē elɔɔb ánēdē-ʼɛ ane mod mǐd áte, ébédɛ́ɛ Mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me-áte.  
\v 15 Befarisia bênsɛdéd ane mod awě ankwɛ̌ ndím ámpē bánken, “Chán émwédé abootéd dé anyínɛn.” Hɛ́ɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “Antɔ́b elɔɔb awɔ́géd mɛ á mǐd. Áde ńwóbpé eʼsó, ḿbootéd-tɛ anyínɛn.”  
\v 16 Hɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ doŋge á Befarisia béhɔ́bɛɛ́ nɛ́n bán, “Anɛ́n mod awě abɛlé ádɛ́n dyam, eéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ abɛ́ mod awě Dyǒb álómé, áyə̄le eékoŋgɛɛ́ mbéndé e Mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me-áte.” Boŋ ábíníí-ʼɛ béhɔ́béʼáá bánken, “Chán mod a mbéb áhɛlɛsɛ ábɛléʼ échɛ́n ndín e menyáké?” Nɛ́n dêmpɛɛ́n nkabɛ́n átîntê echâb.  
\v 17 Né-ɔɔ́, Befarisia bênsɛdéd ane mod ámpē bánken, “Ngáne éhɔ́bé wɛɛ́ mɔ̂bɛlé boŋ ényînneʼ, cheé éwóó ahɔ́b á yə̌l echê?” Hɛ́ɛ ane mod ákwɛntanné bɔ́ aá, “Adíi nkal éʼdəə́dəŋ.” 
\p  
\v 18 Ké nɛ̂, bad bé Israɛl bénkêndúbɛ́ɛ́ bán, ane mod ansébé ndím akwɛ. Nɛ̂ dêmbɛ̌l bénchɛ̄lē sáá bɔ́ nyaŋ.  
\v 19 Bênsɛdéd bɔ́ bánken, “Nyɛ́ɛ̄ nyêchyáá anɛ́n mod awě nyéhɔ́bé bán, béchyáá ne ndím-ɛ? Chán-nɔ̄ ébɛ́nlédé boŋ ányīnnē bɔɔb?”  
\v 20 Dɔ́ɔ sáá bɔ́ nyaŋ békwɛntanné bán, “Sêbíí bán awɛd mwǎn mɔ̂dé, sêbíí-ʼɛ bán bénchyāā mɔ́ ne ndím.  
\v 21 Boŋ séēkooʼɛ́ abíi ngáne ámwédé anyínɛn, séebíi-ʼáa mod awě abɛlé boŋ ányīnneʼ. Nyésɛdte mɔ́, eésaá mwěndem, mwěn áhɔ̂b.”  
\v 22 Bénhɔ̄b nɛ̂ áyə̄le bébááʼáá bad bé Israɛl. Bad bé Israɛl bénhɔ̄b bán, kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adúbpé aá Yesuɛ mɔ̂dé Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté, bɛ́nan mɔ́ á ndáb e mekáne.  
\v 23 Nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ dênkə̌ŋ boŋ sáá bɔ́ nyaŋ béhɔ́b bán, “Nyésɛdte mɔ́, eésaá mwěndem, mwěn áhɔ̂b.” 
\p  
\v 24 Hɛ́ɛ ábê bad bé Israɛl béchɛ̂nlɛɛ́ ane mod awě Yesuɛ ândidté bwâm ngen échě élóntɛ́né ébɛ, boŋ bélāŋgē mɔ́ bán, “Kǎl echoŋ mbále á dǐn á Dyǒb. Sêbíí bán anɛ́n mod awě achǒŋté wɛ adíi mod a mbéb.”  
\v 25 Dɔ́ɔ ane mod átimtanné bɔ́ aá, “Meebíiʼɛ́ mɛ ké adé mod a mbéb kéʼɛ eésaá. Dyam ahɔ́g áde ḿbíí, ádé nɛ́n, menkwɛ̌ ndím boŋ bɔɔb nnyînneʼ.”  
\v 26 Hɛ́ɛ bésɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ bánken, “Cheé âmbɛnlé boŋ ébootéd anyínɛn?”  
\v 27 Ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Mmaá nyé aláa boŋ kénɛ̂, nyéedúbpɛ́ɛ́ mɛ. Cheé nyéhɛdɛɛ́ bán ńláa nyé ámpē? Nyémpē nyêhɛdeʼ ábē bembapɛɛ abɛ́-yɛ?”  
\v 28 Hɛ́ɛ bésyə́əʼɛ́ mɔ́, béhɔ̄bē bán, “Wɛ-ɛɛ́ edé mbapɛɛ awě ane mod. Sêdíi bembapɛɛ ábe Mosɛɛ.  
\v 29 Sêbíí bán, Dyǒb dénhɔ̄b wɛ́ɛ Mosɛɛ, boŋ séebíiʼɛ́ wɛ́ɛ anɛ́n mod pɛn ábídé.”  
\v 30 Ane mod ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Nɛ́n ádé nkɔ̂mtɛn ń yə̌l áte. Nyéebíiʼɛ́ wɛ́ɛ ábídé, boŋ kénɛ̂ abɛlé nnyînneʼ.  
\v 31 Debíí bán, Dyǒb déekwɛntánné mekáne mé bad bé mbéb, boŋ akwɛntan mekáne ḿme bad ábe bébage mɔ́ edúbé, bébɛlé-ʼɛ mam ḿme áhɛdɛɛ́.  
\v 32 Taasɛ nkǒŋsé ḿbootad mod eéwōgɛ̄ɛ̄ mbêd, bán mod abɛlé mod awě béchyááné ndím anyînneʼ.  
\v 33 Nzé anɛ́n mod awě achǒŋté mɛ enkêmbɛ́ mod a Dyǒb, né eéhɛleʼaá-sɛ ábɛl enɛ́n ndín e dyam.”  
\v 34 Dɔ́ɔ ábê bad békwɛntanné mɔ́ bán, “Béchyáá wɛ á mbéb-te, ékwōg-kɛ á mbéb-te, boŋ bɔɔb éhɛdé sé ayə́ged-ɛ?” Hɛ́ɛ dɔ́ɔ bébídté mɔ́ á ndáb e mekáne. 
\s1 Ndím e edəə́dəŋ 
\p  
\v 35 Áde Yesuɛ áwógé bán bébídté ane mod awě ânchoódté á ndáb e mekáne, anhɛd mɔ́. Áde ányíné mɔ́, ansɛdéd mɔ́ aáken, “Edúbpé Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ-ɛ?”  
\v 36 Ane mod antimtɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “A-Sáŋ nzɛ́ɛ́ adé Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ, láá mé âbɛl nɛ́n ńdúbe mɔ́?”  
\v 37 Yesuɛ anláá mɔ́ aá, “Emaá mɔ́ anyín, nyúmɔ̄-ʼaá nyêkaleʼ nɛ́n.”  
\v 38 Hɛ́ɛ ane mod áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “A-sáŋ, ndúbpé!” Abwɔ́g-kɛ mebóbóŋ âbɛ mɔ́ edúbé.  
\v 39 Yesuɛ anhɔ́b aá, “Mpedé á nkǒŋsé wɛ́n, âkáad bad âbɛl nɛ́n bad ábe békwédé ndím bényínɛn, ábe bɔ́-ʼɛ bényînneʼ, békwɛ ndím.” 
\p  
\v 40 Áde doŋge á Befarisia ábe bɔ́ɔbɛ Yesuɛ bémbɛ̄ áhed béwógé nɛ̂, bênsɛdéd mɔ́ bánken, “Sêdúbpé bán, weehɔ́bɛ́ɛ́ wɛɛ́ sémpē sêkwedé ndím?”  
\v 41 Yesuɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nzé nyênkwɛ ndím, né mbéb méesaá nyé á yə̌l. Boŋ bɔɔb áde nyéhɔ́bɛɛ́ bán nyênyínneʼ, mbéb ńdíí ńdé nyé á yə̌l.” 
\c 10  
\s1 Ngan e Nnɔn a ńdyɔŋ ḿ mbód  //  ne éche mbód 
\p  
\v 1 Yesuɛ anhɔ́b aá, “Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé mɛɛ́, kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě eépoo á mmwɛ mé abem á mbód, boŋ átim achə́gé pɛd empée, adíi nchîb, abɛ́-ʼɛ mod e ewúɛn.  
\v 2 Mod awě apooʼ á mmwɛ mé abem mɔ̂dé Nnɔn a ńdyɔŋ ḿ mbód.  
\v 3 Mod awě anɔne abem adibnad mɔ́ ekob. Achəge mbód tɛ́ɛ́ ne dǐn, ábīdnē-ʼɛ chɔ́.  
\v 4 Abídné-ʼaá chɔ́, atómɛ́n chɔ́, chɔ́-ʼɛ éhīdē mɔ́, áyə̄le ébíí éche ehɔ́b.  
\v 5 Boŋ échê mbód éehídɛ́ɛ́ nken mbêd. Ébɛléʼ ébāāʼ mɔ́ á yə̌l báán, áyə̄le éechemɛ́ɛ́ éche ehɔ́b.”  
\v 6 Yesuɛ ankalé bɔ́ enɛ́n ngan boŋ bénkênsóŋtɛ́nné. 
\s1 Yesuɛ aá mɔ́ɔ mɔ́dē  //  Nnɔn a ńdyɔŋ ḿ mbód a bwâm 
\p  
\v 7 Né-ɔɔ́, Yesuɛ ambád ámpē aá, “Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛ-ɛɛ́, mɛ́ɛ ndé mmwɛ mé ekob wɛ́ɛ mbód épooʼɛ́.  
\v 8 Byánán mɛ̌pɛ̌, bad bésyə̄ə̄l ábe bésébpé apɛ bébédɛ́ɛ bechîb ne bad bé ewúɛn, boŋ mbód éekênwógɛ́nné bɔ́.  
\v 9 Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé ekob. Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě apoó áwêm, ǎkǔd eʼsoósoŋ. Ǎsɔ̄l, abíd-tɛ ésebán mod atagte mɔ́. Ǎkud-tɛ kéchéé éche áhɛdɛɛ́.  
\v 10 Nchîb apag dásɔ̄ âchíb, âwúu ne âbébed. Mpedé âbɛl boŋ békud aloŋgé áde álóné mbon.  
\v 11 Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé nnɔn-a-mbód a bwâm. Nnɔn-a-mbód a bwâm adé mboŋsɛ́n âwɛ́ á nló ḿme éche mbód.  
\v 12 Mod awě bétédé á nsɔ́n tédɛ́n, ânɔn mbód, áde mwěn éesaá nnɔn-a-mbód, áde éesaá-ʼaá nwóó-mbód, ányínɛɛ́ nyínɛ́n nɛ́ɛ ngə ehúɛʼɛ́, áchēnē mbód, atóm mehélé. Ene póndé dɔ́ɔ ngə ésogɛɛ́ mbód, échíníí-ʼɛ épáŋtéd áte.  
\v 13 Ane mod atóme mehélé áyə̄le adíi mod awě bétédé á nsɔ́n tédɛ́n, eewôŋnɛɛ́ échê mbód póndé.  
\v 14 Mɛ́ɛ ndé nnɔn-a-mbód a bwâm. Mbíí échem mbód, échem mbód-tɛ ébíí mɛ.  
\v 15 Melemlem nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ Titɛ́ɛ ábíí mɛ, mɛ-ʼɛ mbíí mɔ́. Mbǒŋsɛ́né-ʼɛ âwɛ́ á nló ḿme échem mbód.  
\v 16 Nwóó-ʼɛ mbód émpēe éche éesɛ̌ á abem-tê wɛ́n, ntə́ŋgɛ́né chɔ́mpē apɛɛn, chɔ́mpē éwōg échem ehɔ́b, né-ɔɔ́, abem dɛ́bɛ̄ ahɔ́g, nnɔn-a-mbód-tɛ nhɔ́g.  
\v 17 Titɛ́ɛ adəə́ mɛ, áyə̄le mbǒŋsɛ́né âwɛ́ âbɛl ńkud ádêm aloŋgé ámbīd ámpē.  
\v 18 Modmod eékobnɛ́ɛ́ mɛ ádêm aloŋgé, boŋ mbage dɔ́ ne mměn. Nwóó ngíne âbɛ ádêm aloŋgé, nwóó-ʼɛ ngíne âtéd dɔ́ ámpē. Nɛ́n dɔ́ɔ Titɛ́ɛ áláŋgé mɛ aá ḿbɛl.” 
\p  
\v 19 Ábɛ́n eʼyale ábe Yesuɛ bêmpɛɛ́n nkabɛ́n átîntê e bad bé Israɛl ámpē.  
\v 20 Bɔ́ bad híin béhɔ́béʼáá nɛ́n bán, “Edəə́dəŋ é mbéb édé mɔ́ áte, apedé mǐn. Chán nyéhɛle nyéwōglān mɔ́?”  
\v 21 Boŋ bémpēe béhɔ́béʼáá bán, “Mod awě edəə́dəŋ é mbéb édíí áte eehɔ́bɛ́ɛ́ échɛ́n ndín e mekan. Edəə́dəŋ é mbéb éhɛle ébɛ̄l mod awě akwedé ndím anyínɛn-ɛ?” 
\s1 Bad bé Israɛl bébáá Yesuɛ á yə̌l 
\p  
\v 22 Ngande e Nnamed ń Ndáb-e-Dyǒb ékóbtéʼáá á Jerusalɛm. Nɛ́n ábédé á pondé éche ahéb ábágkē bwâmbwam.  
\v 23 Yesuɛ ahyɔ́mméʼáá á abepé á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb áde béchə́géʼáá bán Abepé áde Solomonɛ.  
\v 24 Bad bé Israɛl bênləŋnéd mɔ́, bésɛdté mɔ́ bán, “Póndé ehéé wɛwɛ wɛ́sōgkē sé abane á edibelónɛ́ɛ́-te? Nzé wɛ-ɛɛ́ edé Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté, épanléd sé áte.”  
\v 25 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Mmaá nyé aláa, boŋ nyéedúbpɛɛ́. Nsɔ́n ḿme ḿbɛlɛɛ́ á dǐn áde awêm Titɛ́ɛ, měn ḿbíde mɛ mbóŋ.  
\v 26 Boŋ nyéedúbpɛ́ɛ́ áyə̄le nyéesaá échêm mbód.  
\v 27 Échem mbód éwóge échêm ehɔ́b. Mbíí chɔ́, chɔ́-ʼaá éhíde mɛ.\fig Nnɔn-a-mbód alyə́gte ḿmē ńdyɔŋ ḿ mbód|src="bk00007c.tif" size="span" ref="10.27" \fig* 
\v 28 Mbage bɔ́ aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ, béewáá-ʼaá mbêd. Modmod eéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ ásog bɔ́ áwêm mekáá.  
\v 29 Chǒm echě awêm Titɛ́ɛ ábágé mɛ étómé chǒm ésyə̄ə̄l, \f + \fr 10:29 \fq Chǒm echě awêm Titɛ́ɛ ábágé mɛ étómé chǒm ésyə̄ə̄l: \ft doŋge á kálag déʼsó áwóó \fq Titɛ́ɛ awě abagé mɛ bɔ́, atómé chǒm ésyə̄ə̄l.\f* modmod eéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ ásog bɔ́ á mekáá ḿme Titɛ́ɛ.  
\v 30 Sé Titɛ̂ sêdíi mod nhɔ́g.” 
\p  
\v 31 Bad bé Israɛl béntēd meláá ámpē âlúm Yesuɛ.  
\v 32 Boŋ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nlúmté nyé ekud é nsɔ́n ḿ bwâm éche ébídé ne echem Sáŋ. Nyêhɛde me meláá alúm, âwúu mɛ. Ḿmê nsɔ́n ńhéé nyéhɛdɛɛ́ mɛ meláá alúmɛn.”  
\v 33 Dɔ́ɔ békwɛntanné bán, “Séēhɛ̄dɛ̄ɛ̄ wɛ meláá alúm áyə̄le nsɔ́n ḿ bwâm ḿme ébɛ́lé. Boŋ sêlúme wɛ meláá áyə̄le esyə́ə́ Dyǒb.”  
\v 34 Yesuɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Ngɔ́mē éténlédé áwɛn Kálag e Mbéndé nɛ́n bán, Dyǒb áhɔ́bé aá, ‘Nyêdíi myǒb.’  
\v 35 Debíí nɛ́n bán, eyale é Dyǒb éekwagké. Dyǒb dênchə̌g bad ábe ánlōmɛ̄nnē échē eyale aá bédíi myǒb.  
\v 36 Mɛ-ɛɛ́ Dyǒb ánámté boŋ alóm-mɛ á nkǒŋsé, chán-nɔ̄ nyéhɛle nyéhɔ̄bē bán, nsyə́ə́ Dyǒb áyə̄le ńtúmé ahɔ́b mɛɛ́ ndíi Mwǎn a Dyǒb?  
\v 37 Nzé meébɛ̄lē nsɔ́n ḿme Titɛ́ɛ, nyéedúbpé mɛ.  
\v 38 Boŋ nzé édé nɛ́n bán mbɛle mɔ́, nyêdúbé ḿmê nsɔ́n ké nyéedúbpe mměn, âbɛl nɛ́n nyébíi nyésôŋtɛn-nɛ ngen pɔ́g ne ésyə̄ə̄l nɛ́n bán, Titɛ́ɛ adé mɛ áte, mɛ-ʼɛ mbɛ́ mɔ́ áte ngen pɔ́g ne ngen ésyə̄ə̄l.” 
\p  
\v 39 Ḿmɛ́n mam ḿme ánhɔ̄bpē mêmbɛ̌l bênwanɛ́n mɔ́ akób ámpē, boŋ ambíd bɔ́ á mekáá. 
\p  
\v 40 Ámbīd enɛ̂, Yesuɛ antǐm ámbīd á pɛd e edíb é Jodan eníníí, á abwɔ́g á hǒm wɛ́ɛ Jɔnɛ, Ndusɛnɛ ádúsánnáá bad, ádyɛ̄ɛ̄ áhed.  
\v 41 Ndun e mod epagéʼáá áwē. Ábê bad béhɔ́béʼáá bán, “Jɔnɛ, Ndusɛnɛ eébɛleʼaá menyáké boŋ kéchéé éche áhɔ́bé tə̂ŋgɛne anɛ́n mod édé mbále.”  
\v 42 Né-ɔɔ́, ndun e mod echě embɛ́ áhed, endúbé Yesuɛ. 
\c 11  
\s1 Kwééd eche Lazarɔsɛ 
\p  
\v 1 Mod nhɔ́g ambɛ́ awě béchə́géʼáá bán Lazarɔsɛ, akǒnléʼáá. Lazarɔsɛ ne baányaŋ bé bebaád, Maria ne Mataa bédyɛ́ɛ́ʼáá á dyad á Bɛtani.  
\v 2 Anɛ́n Maria awě mwǎnyaŋ Lazarɔsɛ ákónléʼáá, mɔ̂ anwɔ́géd Yesuɛ dyɔ̌g dé elod é bwâm á mekuu, boŋ apínnéd échē esid.  
\v 3 Né-ɔɔ́, Maria bɔ́ Mataa bɔ́ bénlōm nsəl wɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ bán, “A-Sáŋ, awoŋ nsón a nlém akonleʼ.”  
\v 4 Áde Yesuɛ áwógé ḿmɛ́n nlébtéd anhɔ́b aá, “Ḿmɛ́n nkole méesógké ne kwééd. Nɛ́n ábɛ́nlédé âbɛ Dyǒb ehúmé, âbɛl boŋ Mwǎn a Dyǒb ákud edúbé.”  
\v 5 Yesuɛ andə̌ŋ Mataa, Maria ne Lazarɔsɛ.  
\v 6 Ké nɛ̂, áde áwógé bán, Lazarɔsɛ akonle andíi ambɛ́ wɛ́ɛ ámbɛ̄ɛ̄ eʼpun éʼbɛ.  
\v 7 Hɛ́ɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ ábē bembapɛɛ aá, “Détim ámbīd á Judeya.”  
\v 8 Dɔ́ɔ ábe bembapɛɛ bélâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ bán “A-meléed, kíné saá áwed dɔ́ɔ bad béhɛ́déʼáá wɛ meláá awúɛn súútə́ŋʼɛ?”  
\v 9 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Éesaá mbále bán mǔte ńwóó dyôm á háwa ne ébɛ-yɛ? Bad ábe békag mǔte béekwagké áyə̄le bédé ne ane awě adé eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde bé nkǒŋsé.  
\v 10 Boŋ nzé békag nkuu, dɔ́ɔ békwagké áyə̄le eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde béesaá.”  
\v 11 Áde Yesuɛ ámáá ahɔ́b nɛ́n ambád ámpē aá, “Awɛd nsón Lazarɔsɛ akúne, boŋ nkag mɔ́ anyem ásē.”  
\v 12 Ábē bembapɛɛ bénlāā mɔ́ bán, “A-Sáŋ, nzé akúne né ǎdyɛɛ́ bwâm.”  
\v 13 Yesuɛ ahɔ́béʼáá nɛ́n áyə̄le ambíí aá, Lazarɔsɛ awédé, boŋ ábē bembapɛɛ bénwēmtɛ̄n bán, ahɔ́be aá, akúne kúnɛ́n.  
\v 14 Né-ɔɔ́, Yesuɛ ampanléd bɔ́ áte aá, “Lazarɔsɛ awédé,  
\v 15 boŋ á yə̌l echɛ̂n, ndé menyiŋge nɛ́n mɛɛ́ meebédɛɛ́ áhed âbɛl boŋ nyédúbe. Syánē dékag-kɔɔ́ áwed bɔɔb.”  
\v 16 Hɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ Tɔmasɛ (awě bênchuúʼɛ́ bán, Nhɛ́d) álâŋgɛɛ́ baáb bembapɛɛ aá, “Syánē ámpē dékag áwed âbɛl boŋ nzé kwééd chɔ́ edé déwɛ̂ ne Meléede.” 
\s1 Yesuɛ mɔ́ adé mpuu ne aloŋgé 
\p  
\v 17 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, áde Yesuɛ ápédé á Bɛtani, antán nɛ́ɛ bémáá Lazarɔsɛ alíme. Ene póndé né ḿmê ndim ńkébɛ̄ á soŋ-tê eʼpun éʼniin.  
\v 18 Bootya á Bɛtani âpɛ á Jerusalɛm ábédé dyam máyl mébɛ.  
\v 19 Ekud é bad bé Israɛl ênhyɛ̌ wɛ́ɛ Mataa bɔ́ Maria âwenned bɔ́ áyə̄le kwééd eche awab mwǎnyaŋ.  
\v 20 Áde Mataa áwógé bán, Yesuɛ ahúɛʼ, ankɛ̌ mɔ́ abomɛn á nzii, boŋ Maria anlyə̌g á ndáb.  
\v 21 Dɔ́ɔ Mataa álâŋgɛɛ́ Yesuɛ aá, “A-Sáŋ, nzé wembɛ́ hɛ́n né mwǎnned eewédɛɛ́.  
\v 22 Boŋ ké nɛ̂, mbíí mɛɛ́ ké bɔɔb kéchéé éche ésɛ́dté Dyǒb, Dyǒb dɛ́bɛ̌ wɛ.”  
\v 23 Yesuɛ anláá mɔ́ aá, “Mwǎnyoŋ ǎbɛ̄ á aloŋgé ámpē.”  
\v 24 Mataa antimtɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Mbíí mɛɛ́ ǎpuú á póndé e mpuu mbwɛ mé asóg.”  
\v 25 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ aláŋgé mɔ́ aá, “Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé mpuu né aloŋgé. Nzé mod adúbpé mɛ, ké anwɛ́, ǎbɛ̄ abɛ́ á aloŋgé.  
\v 26 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adé á aloŋgé boŋ adúbé-ʼɛ mɛ, éewáá mbêd. Edúbpé né-yɛ?”  
\v 27 Hɛ́ɛ Mataa ákwɛntanné aá, “Ɛɛ, A-Sáŋ, ndúbpé mɛɛ́ wɛ-ɛɛ́ edé Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté, Mwǎn a Dyǒb awě Dyǒb áhɔ́bé aá, ǎpɛ̄ á nkǒŋsé.” 
\s1 Yesuɛ achií 
\p  
\v 28 Áde Mataa áhɔ́bé nɛ̂, antǐm ámbīd, ákɛ̄ áchəg mwǎnyaŋ Maria kun, aláá mɔ́ aá, “Meléede adé hɛ́n, asɛdte-ʼɛ wɛ.”  
\v 29 Áde Maria áwógé nɛ̂, anhidé ásē mehélé, ákɛ atán Yesuɛ.  
\v 30 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, Yesuɛ enkêmpaá asɔ́l á dyad-tê, andíi ambɛ́ wɛ́ɛ Mataa ántānnē mɔ́.  
\v 31 Áde bad bé Israɛl ábe bébédé á ndáb-te ne Maria âwenned mɔ́, bényíné nɛ́ɛ ábídé á ndáb-te ne mehélé, anyəgte á soŋ, bénwēmtɛ̄n bán, akag achii. Né-ɔɔ́, bénhīd mɔ́. 
\p  
\v 32 Áde Maria ápédé wɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ámbɛ̄ɛ̄ boŋ anyín mɔ́, ankwɛ̌ mɔ́ á mekuu, ahɔ́b aá, “A-Sáŋ, nzé wembɛ́ hɛ́n, né mwǎnned eewédɛɛ́.”  
\v 33 Anyín áde Yesuɛ ányíné nɛ́ɛ Maria áchyɛɛʼɛ́, anyín-nɛ nɛ́ɛ bad ábe bénhīd mɔ́ béchyɛɛʼɛ́, ngɔl enkonnéd mɔ́, átāg-kɛ áte á nlém-tê bwâmbwam.  
\v 34 Ansɛdéd aáken, “Héé nyélímmé mɔ́?” Bênkwɛntɛ́n bán, “A-Sáŋ, hyɛ̌ ényîn.”  
\v 35 Yesuɛ anchií.  
\v 36 Hɛ́ɛ bad bé Israɛl béhɔ́bɛɛ́ bán, “Nɛ́dē ankǒŋ mɔ́ adəŋ-óó!”  
\v 37 Boŋ bɔ́ doŋge á bad bénhɔ̄b bán, “Ngɔ́mē ambɛ̌l mod awě ankwɛ ndím ányīnne. Eéhɛleʼaá-sɛ ábɛl Lazarɔsɛ eewág-ɛ?” 
\s1 Yesuɛ apuúdté Lazarɔsɛ 
\p  
\v 38 Ngɔl enkonnéd Yesuɛ á nlém ámpē. Né-ɔɔ́, ankɛ̌ á soŋ. Ene soŋ ebédɛ́ɛ soŋ echě bépwɔ́gé aláá áte, boŋ békútɛ́n chɔ́ nsəl ne aláá.  
\v 39 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ ábê bad aá, “Nyéhûd ádê aláá.” Dɔ́ɔ Mataa, mod awě awédé mwǎnyaŋ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “A-Sáŋ, ndim mɛ́mǎd abooted dé achum bɔɔb áyə̄le ńkídémbɛ́ á soŋ-tê bɔɔb eʼpun éʼniin.”  
\v 40 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá “Meelâŋgɛɛ́ wɛ mɛɛ́ nzé edúbpé né wɛ̌nyīn Ngum e Dyǒb-ɛ?”  
\v 41 Né-ɔɔ́, ábê bad bénhūd ádê aláá á nsəl ń soŋ. Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ ánɔ́né ámīn boŋ áhɔ̄bē aá, “A-Tɛ̂, nságnɛ́né wɛ áyə̄le éwógé mɛ mekáne.  
\v 42 Mbíí mɛɛ́ eyɔ̌gké mɛ mekáne awóg, boŋ nhɔ́be nɛ́n âbɛl boŋ ábɛ́n bad ábe bédé hɛ́n bédúbe bán, wɛ-ɛɛ́ elómé mɛ.”  
\v 43 Áde ámáá ahɔ́b nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ áchə́gté ehɔ́b ámīn boŋ áchɛ̄nlē Lazarɔsɛ aá, “A-Lazarɔs, bíd áwed!”  
\v 44 Ane mod awě ammǎd awɛ́ abíd-tɛ áwed. Mbɔ́m éche bênkaánné mɔ́ mekuu ne mekáá ne tumbe echě bênkaánné mɔ́ eʼsó, émbɛ̄ ébɛ̄ mɔ́ á yə̌l. Yesuɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nyéhune mɔ́ ábê bwěm á yə̌l, ákag.” \fig Yesuɛ apuúdté Lazarɔsɛ|src="CN01768C.tif" size="col" ref="11.38-44" \fig* 
\s1 Béhəgke Yesuɛ 
\r (Mat 26.1-5; Mak 14.1-2; Luk 22.1-2) 
\p  
\v 45 Bad bé Israɛl ábe bênkɛ̌ Maria á mewenned bényīn mekan ḿme Yesuɛ âmbɛnlé, béndūbē-ʼɛ Yesuɛ.  
\v 46 Boŋ bɔ́ doŋge á bad bênkɛ̌ Befarisia atán, béláá bɔ́ mam ḿme Yesuɛ ábɛ́lé.  
\v 47 Hɛ́ɛ beprisɛ bémbáá ne Befarisia béchɛ́nlé mbom ń káánsɛl. Bénhɔ̄b bán, “Cheé dɛ́bɛnlé bɔɔb? Detə́ŋgɛ́né dyam abɛl áyə̄le anɛ́n mod abɛle menyáké bwâmbwam!  
\v 48 Nzé detɛ̌dté bán, ákɛɛne ḿmɛ́n mekan áʼsō né moosyəə́l ǎdūbē mɔ́. Nzé moosyəə́l adúbpé-ʼɛ mɔ́, né bad bé Roma bɛ́pɛ̌, békōbɛ̄n-nɛ syánē echɛd Ndáb-e-Dyǒb, békōbɛ̄n-nɛ syánē ádɛ̄d aloŋ.”  
\v 49 Dɔ́ɔ mod nhɔ́g átîntê echâb awě béchə́géʼáá bán Kaifasɛ, awě abédé prisɛ ambáámbáa ḿmê mwɛ̌, áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “Nyéebíiʼɛ́ dyamdyam.  
\v 50 Nyéenyínɛ́ɛ́ nɛ́n bán ébóó bán, mod nhɔ́g áwɛ̂ á nló ḿ moosyəə́l tómaa aloŋ ásyə̄ə̄l ábɔ́ɔ?”  
\v 51 Kénɛ́ɛ áhɔ́béʼáá nɛ̂, saké ḿmē mewêmtɛn měn mɔ́ɔ áhɔ́bnéʼáá nɛ̂. Ngáne ábédé prisɛ ambáámbáa ḿmê mwɛ̌, ahɔ́béʼáá dyam áde dɛ́bɛnléd, áʼsō éʼ póndé, aá Yesuɛ ǎwɛ̄ á nló ḿ bad bé Israɛl.  
\v 52 Saá-kaá á nló ḿ bad bé Israɛl bénpɛn, boŋ kə́ŋne âlad bad bé Dyǒb bésyə̄ə̄l ábe bémáá ahɛnted áte hǒm ahɔ́g, âbɛl bébɛ̂ mod nhɔ́g. 
\p  
\v 53 Bootya échê epun bad bémbáá bé Israɛl bêmbootéd Yesuɛ ahəge, âwúu mɔ́.  
\v 54 Nɛ́n dêmbɛ̌l Yesuɛ eebídeʼaá á nhɛ́né ámpē átîntê e bad bé Israɛl. Bɔ́ɔbɛ ábē bembapɛɛ bênhidé békɛ̄ á dyad áde béchəgɛɛ́ bán Efrem, bédyɛ̄ɛ̄-ʼɛ áwed. Ádê dyad ábédé bɛnbɛn ne ehyáŋge.  
\v 55 Póndé e ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn embɛ́ bɛnbɛn. Né-ɔɔ́, bad híin bémbīd myad ne myad, békɛ̄ á akuu á Jerusalɛm âwobe échab yə̌l ngáne mbéndé e Mosɛɛ éhɛ́déʼáá, âboŋsɛn ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn.  
\v 56 Ábê bad bé Israɛl bémbɛ̄ béhɛdé Yesuɛ. Áde béládné á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb bésɛ́dtéʼáá, nhɔ́g ne aníníí bánken, “Chán nyéwémtɛ́né, nyêdúbpé bán, ǎhyɛ ngande-yɛ?”  
\v 57 Beprisɛ bémbáá ne Befarisia béntōmēd ehə́ŋgé bán, kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě anyíné Yesuɛ áhyɛ áláa bɔ́, âbɛl boŋ békōb mɔ́. 
\c 12  
\s1 Béwɔ́gté Yesuɛ á Bɛtani 
\r (Mat 26.6-13; Mak 14.3-9) 
\p  
\v 1 Áde ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn élyə́gé eʼpun ntóób, Yesuɛ ankɛ̌ á Bɛtani wɛ́ɛ Lazarɔsɛ awě âmpuúdté ádyɛ́ɛ́ʼáá.  
\v 2 Bêmbɛlé Yesuɛ ndyééd áhed. Mataa mɔ́ antómēd ene ndyééd. Lazarɔsɛ ambɛ́ nhɔ́g átîntê e bad ábe bɔ́ɔbɛ Yesuɛ bébédé á tébelɛ âdyɛ́ ndyééd.  
\v 3 Hɛ́ɛ Maria átédé epom é dyɔ̌g dé elod á bwâm áde álɛ́lé nkun bwâmbwam. Ádê dyɔ̌g bébɛ́nlé dɔ́ nâd.\f + \fr 12:3 \fk Nâd: \ft Nâd edíi mbonja echě ewóó elod é bwâm eche bébɛnlɛɛ́ mɔ̌g mé elod é bwâm.\f* Anwɔ́géd Yesuɛ á mekuu, apíné-ʼɛ mɔ́ mekuu ne échē esid é nló. Elod é bwâm énlɔ̄g ndáb áte esyəə́l.  
\v 4 Dɔ́ɔ Judas Iskariɔdɛ, mbapɛɛ nhɔ́g awě émbɛ̄ɛ̄ bán mɔ́ ǎsōm Yesuɛ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá,  
\v 5 “Cheé bénkênsómmé ádɛ́n dyɔ̌g, bétéd ḿmɛ́n mɔné békɛ̄ bébɛ̄ betóótōkɛ̄ bé bad? Béhɛ́léʼáá-sɛ bésóm ádê dyɔ̌g dyam-ɛ́ɛ áde nsábe ḿ mwɛ̌ nhɔ́g.”  
\v 6 Judasɛ anhɔ́b nɛ̂, saké áyə̄le abédé betóótōkɛ̄ bé bad ngɔl, boŋ áyə̄le abédɛ́ɛ nchîb. Ngáne ábédé mod awě awánládtáá bɔ́bɔ̄ɔ ekwɛ é mɔné, ayɔ̌gkéʼáá mɔné atéd ámbīd.  
\v 7 Boŋ Yesuɛ anhɔ́b aá, “Tɛdé mɔ́, ákoo áde ályə́gé ásē âbɛl boŋ ábɛnled dɔ́ mbwɛ ḿme bɛ́līmɛ̄ɛ̄ mɛ.  
\v 8 Betóótōkɛ̄ bé bad bédé ne nyé póndé tɛ́ɛ́ boŋ mɛ pɛn méebáá ne nyé póndé ésyə̄ə̄l.” 
\s1 Béhəgke Lazarɔsɛ 
\p  
\v 9 Ene póndé-ɔɔ́, bad bé Israɛl híin bénwōg bán, Yesuɛ adé á Bɛtani. Né-ɔɔ́, bênkɛ̌ áwed. Saké Yesuɛ mwěmpɛn mɔ́ ankə̌ŋ boŋ békɛ̄ áwed, boŋ bênkɛ̌ Lazarɔsɛ anyín awě Yesuɛ âmpuúdté.  
\v 10 Né-ɔɔ́, Beprisɛ bémbáá béhə́gkéʼáá kə́ə́ŋne Lazarɔsɛ âwúu mɔ́,  
\v 11 áyə̄le bad bé Israɛl bétɛ́dtéʼáá bɔ́, bédūbpē Yesuɛ. Béndūbē Yesuɛ áyə̄le dyam áde dêmbɛnléd ne Lazarɔsɛ. 
\s1 Yesuɛ asɔ́lé á Jerusalɛm nɛ́ɛ kə̂ŋ 
\r (Mat 21.1-11; Mak 11.1-11; Luk 19.28-40) 
\p  
\v 12 Nɛ́ɛ bǐn éʼsáŋgé, ndun e mod echě enhyɛ̌ á Ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn bénwōg bán Yesuɛ apag á Jerusalɛm.  
\v 13 Hɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ bésɛ́lé eʼkikag éʼ mií boŋ békǎg mɔ́ abomɛn á nzii. Béhágéʼáá eʼsaád bán, “Hosána! Nnam ḿbɛ̂ ne ane awě apedé á dǐn áde Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́. Nnam ḿbɛ̂ ne kə̂ŋ e bad bé Israɛl!” 
\p  
\v 14 Yesuɛ ankǔd etum é ésɛl, ádīī-ʼɛ chɔ́. Nɛ́n dêmbɛnléd ngáne éténlédé á kálag e Dyǒb nɛ́n bán, 
\q1  
\v 15 “Á-bad bé Zayɔn, nyéebááʼ, 
\q1 nyénɔneʼ echɛn kə̂ŋ ehúɛʼ, 
\q1 ediídé-ʼɛ etum é ésɛl.” 
\p  
\v 16 Á póndé echě ḿmɛ́n mekan mébɛ́nlédé, bembapɛɛ ábe Yesuɛ bénkênsóŋtɛ́nné. Boŋ áde Yesuɛ âmpuúʼɛ́ ne ehúmé é Dyǒb, dɔ́ɔ bênchemmé bán mam ḿme mébɛ́nlédé tə̂ŋgɛne Yesuɛ mɔ́ɔ mêntenléd, á yə̌l echê. 
\p  
\v 17 Ndun e mod echě embɛ́ ne Yesuɛ áde áchɛ́nlé Lazarɔsɛ á soŋ-tê boŋ ápuudté mɔ́, embɛ́ ékaléʼ ḿmê nkalaŋ.  
\v 18 Né-ɔɔ́ ndun e mod enkɛ̌ Yesuɛ abomɛn áyə̄le ábɛ́n eʼchemléd bé menyáké ábe âmbɛnlé.  
\v 19 Hɛ́ɛ Befarisia bélâŋgɛɛ́ nhɔ́g ne aníníí bán, “Nyénɔneʼ! Kə́ŋne bɔɔb deéhɛ́lɛ́ɛ́ dyamdyam abɛl. Nkǒŋsé ńsyə̄ə̄l ńhide mɔ́.” 
\s1 Bad bé Grikia béhɛde Yesuɛ 
\p  
\v 20 Doŋge á bad bé Grikia bémbɛ̄ átîntê e bad ábe bênkɛ̌ ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn á Jerusalɛm, âkɛ dé abɛ Dyǒb edúbé.  
\v 21 Bêmpɛ̌ wɛ́ɛ Filibɛ. Filibɛ awě ambíd á dyad á Betsaida á mbwɔ́g e Galilia. Bénlāā mɔ́ bán, “A-Sáŋ, sêdəə́ Yesuɛ anyín.”  
\v 22 Filibɛ ankɛ̌ Andreya aláa. Dɔ́ɔ bɔ́ bad bébɛ békíí Yesuɛ aláa.  
\v 23 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Póndé epedé echě ehúmé e Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ énnyīnēdtē.  
\v 24 Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, mbum e ngun pɔ́g edíi mbum e ngun pɔ́g, kə́ə́ŋ né béwéné chɔ́ á ndɔɔb-tê boŋ ewɛ́. Ewâg-káa, boŋ echyáá mbum é ngun émpēe éche ébúú áte.  
\v 25 Mod awě adəə́ ádē aloŋgé, ǎbɔ̄d dɔ́. Mod awě mɔ́-ʼɛ akɔɔ́ ádē aloŋgé, á nkǒŋsé-te wɛ́n, ǎkəə́ dɔ́ á aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ.  
\v 26 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě abɛnle mɛ, atə́ŋgɛ́né awêm mbəledɛ abɛ́. Ké héé-ʼɛ wɛ́ɛ ńdíí, awêm mbəledɛ atə́ŋgɛ́né abɛ́ áhed. Echem Sáŋ ǎbɛ̌-ʼɛ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě abɛnle mɛ edúbé. 
\s1 Yesuɛ ahɔ́bé tə̂ŋgɛne eche kwééd 
\p  
\v 27 “Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, nlém ńtage mɛ áte. Cheé-ɔ̄ mɛ́hɔ̄bpē? Ńhɔ̂b mɛɛ́, ‘A-Tɛ̂, weémwāg-sɛ metake ḿme méhúɛʼ métán mɛ-yɛ?’ Aáy, méehɔ́bpé nɛ̂, áyə̄le enɛ́n póndé e metake chɔ̂ ekəə́ boŋ ḿpag wɛ́n.  
\v 28 A-Tɛ̂, lúméd echôŋ ngum.” Hɛ́ɛ ehɔ́b ébídɛɛ́ á Dyǒb nɛ́n bán, “Nlúmté echêm ngum, mɛ̌lūmēd-tɛ chɔ́ ámpē.”  
\v 29 Ene ndun e mod echě embɛ́ áhed enwóg échê ehɔ́b. Bénhɔ̄b bán dyǒb dɔ́ɔ ákúmé áte. Bad bémpēe bénhɔ̄b bán, ángɛl chɔ́ ehɔ́bé áwē.  
\v 30 Yesuɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Áyə̄le echɛ̂n dɔ́ɔ échɛ́n ehɔ́b ébídé, saké áyə̄l echêm.  
\v 31 Póndé epedé echě Dyǒb dɛ́kāādtē ḿmɛ́n nkǒŋsé. Nkamlɛn ḿme nkamlɛnɛ á nkǒŋsé mɛ́kwɛ̌ bɔɔb.  
\v 32 Boŋ áde bɛ́madté mɛ anyen ámīn, mɛ̌dǒl bad bésyə̄ə̄l áwêm.”  
\v 33 (Yesuɛ anhɔ́b nɛ̂ âlúmed ndín e kwééd echě áwɛ̄ɛ̄.)  
\v 34 Ndun e mod echě embɛ́ áhed enkwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ bán, “Sêwógé á mbéndé-te bán Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté ǎbɛ̄ á ngíndé ne á ngíndé. Chán-nɔ̄ éhɔ́bɛɛ́ wɛɛ́ ‘Bétə́ŋgɛ́né bényēn Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ ámīn.’ Nzɛ́ɛ́ adé anɛ́n ‘Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ?’ ”  
\v 35 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “Eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde bɛ́bē ne nyé á esóŋ e póndé ngɛ̂n. Nyékag bɔɔb áde eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde éʼdíi éʼdíí, âbɛl boŋ ehíntɛ́n éēkōbē nyé. Mod awě akag á ehíntɛ́n-tê eebyɛ́ɛ́ʼɛ́ wɛ́ɛ ákagké.  
\v 36 Nyédúbe eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde bɔɔb áde éʼdíí ne nyé, âbɛl nɛ́n nyébɛ̂ bǎn bé eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde.” 
\s1 Bad bé Israɛl béedíi béedúbpɛɛ́ Yesuɛ 
\p Áde Yesuɛ ámáá ḿmɛ́n mekan mésyə̄ə̄l ahɔ́b, antɛdé bɔ́, ákɛ ásɔ̄ɔ̄m wɛ́ɛ béenyínné mɔ́.  
\v 37 Kénɛ́ɛ ene ndun e mod énnyīnnē ábɛ́n eʼchemléd bé menyáké éʼsyə̄ə̄l ábe Yesuɛ âmbɛnlé, bénkêndúbɛ́ɛ́ mɔ́.  
\v 38 Nɛ́n dêmbɛnléd âlóned eʼyale ábe nkal éʼdəə́dəŋ Yesayaa ánhɔ̄bpē aá, 
\q1 “A-Sáŋ, nzɛ́ɛ́ adúbpé eyale éche sékálé, 
\q1 nzɛ́-módɛ́ akidényīn ngum echôŋ áchēm-mɛ chɔ́?” 
\m  
\v 39 Né-ɔɔ́, béehɛleʼaá-sɛ bédúbe. Yesayaa ahɔ́bé hǒm démpēe aá, 
\q1  
\v 40 “Dyǒb ákwídé bɔ́ ndím, ábɛ̄-ʼɛ bɔ́ nlém mé aláá, 
\q1 âbɛl nɛ́n ḿmab mǐd méēnyīnnēʼ, 
\q1 béēsóŋtánne. 
\q1 Nzé bébɛ́lé-ʼɛ nɛ̂, né bɛ́timɛ́n mɛ, né mɛ̌choód-tɛ bɔ́.” 
\m  
\v 41 Yesayaa anhɔ́b nɛ́n áyə̄le annyín ehúmé éche Yesuɛ, anhɔ́b-pɛ áyə̄l echê.  
\v 42 Ké nɛ̂, bad híin béndūbē Yesuɛ, kə́ə́ŋne doŋge á bad bémbáá. Boŋ ngáne bébááʼáá Befarisia, bénkênlúmédté yə̌l, âbáŋ nɛ́n bán béēbídté bɔ́ á ndáb é mekáne.  
\v 43 Bébɛ́léʼáá nɛ̂ áyə̄le bêndə̌ŋ mekɛnag mé baányoŋ tómaa mé Dyǒb. 
\s1 Eʼyale ábe Yesuɛ bɛ́kāād bad 
\p  
\v 44 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ áchə́gté ehɔ́b ámīn áhɔ̄bē aá, “Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adúbpé mɛ, eedúbpɛɛ́ mměmpɛn, adúbpé kə́ə́ŋne ane awě alómé mɛ.  
\v 45 Kénzɛ́ɛ́-ʼɛ awě anyíné mɛ, anyíné ane awě alómé mɛ.  
\v 46 Mpedé á nkǒŋsé nɛ́ɛ eʼnyínɛn bé ekíde, âbɛl boŋ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adúbpé mɛ, eélyə̄gē á ehíntɛ́n-tê.  
\v 47 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě awógé ábêm eʼyale, boŋ eékoŋge bɔ́, saké mɛ nkáadte mɔ́. Meekáádtɛ́ɛ́ mɔ́ áyə̄le meépedɛɛ́ âkaad nkǒŋsé boŋ mpedé âsoŋ bad bé nkǒŋsé.  
\v 48 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě abáá mɛ á yə̌l boŋ eékobe-ʼɛ ábêm eʼyale, awóó mod awě ǎkāād mɔ́. Ábêm eʼyale běn bɔ́ɔ bɛ́kāād mɔ́ á mbwɛ mé asóg.  
\v 49 Ébɛ̂ nɛ̂, áyə̄le meehɔ́bɛɛ́ ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l ne echêm kunze. Boŋ Titɛ́ɛ awě alómé mɛ, áláŋgé mɛ chǒm éche ńtə́ŋgɛ́né ahɔ́b.  
\v 50 Mbíí mɛɛ́ kéchéé éché áláŋgé mɛ aá ńhɔ̂b épɛɛne aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ. Né-ɔɔ́, kéchéé éche ńhɔ́bɛɛ́, nhɔ́beʼ chɔ́ ngáne Titɛ́ɛ áláŋgé mɛ.” 
\c 13  
\s1 Yesuɛ awǒbpé ábē bembapɛɛ mekuu 
\p  
\v 1 Epun é ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn ênlyə̌g nɛ́ɛ chǎn. Yesuɛ ambíí aá eche póndé emaá apɛ echě mɔ́tə́ŋgɛ́né nkǒŋsé atɛde, âkɛ wɛ́ɛ eche Sáŋ. Andə̌ŋ bad bé nkǒŋsé ábe béndūbē mɔ́, alúméd-tɛ échê edəŋge kə́ə́ŋne á asóg. 
\p  
\v 2 Yesuɛ ne ábē bembapɛɛ bédyágéʼáá ndyééd ngukɛ́l, Satanɛ-ʼɛ ammǎd Judas Iskariɔdɛ mwǎn awě Simɔnɛ mewêmtɛn mé mbéb ásɔ́led áte âsóm Yesuɛ.  
\v 3 Yesuɛ ambíí aá eche Sáŋ abagé mekan mésyə̄ə̄l áwe mekáá. Ambíí-ʼɛ aá mɔ́hūū wɛ́ɛ Dyǒb mɔ́time-ʼɛ ámbīd wɛ́ɛ Dyǒb.  
\v 4 Áde bédyágkē ndyééd nɛ̂, Yesuɛ anhidé ásē, ahúd nkob á yə̌l, atád tábɛlɛ á nkog.  
\v 5 Hɛ́ɛ áhédé mendíb á kúmbe-tê, boŋ ábootéd ábē bembapɛɛ mekuu awobe, ápīnnād tábɛlɛ awě ánwāāʼɛ́ á nkog.  
\v 6 Áde ápédé wɛ́ɛ Simɔn Petro dɔ́ɔ Simɔnɛ ásɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “A-Sáŋ, ehɛde mɛ mekuu awobe-yɛ?”  
\v 7 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Weéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ esóŋtɛ́n dyam áde ḿbɛlɛɛ́ bɔɔb, boŋ ámbīd e ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l dɔ́ɔ wɛ́sōŋtɛ̄nnē.”  
\v 8 Hɛ́ɛ Petro áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “Aáy, weéwóbpɛ́ɛ́ mɛ mekuu mbêd.” Yesuɛ antimtɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Nzé meéwobpe wɛ mekuu né wéewóŋgé dyamdyam abɛlɛn ne mɛ.”  
\v 9 Simɔn Petro anláá mɔ́ aá, “A-Sáŋ, né saké mekuu měmpɛn-ɛɛ́ wɛ́wobɛ́ɛ́ mɛ. Wɛ̌wobé mɛ kə́ə́ŋne mekáá ne nló!”  
\v 10 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Mod awě amaá mendíb awɔg, yə̌l esyəə́l emaá mɔ́ asáŋ, eetə̂ŋgɛnɛɛ́ mendíb awɔ́g ámpē, étōmɛɛ́ âwobe mekuu.\f + \fr 13:10 \ft Doŋge á kálag déʼsó déewóoʼɛ́ \fq éetómɛɛ́ âwobe mekuu.\f* Nyêmaá asáŋ, boŋ saké nyé moosyəə́l nyêsáá.”  
\v 11 Yesuɛ ammǎd abíi mod awě ǎsōm mɔ́. Nɛ́ɛ dênkə̌ŋ boŋ ahɔ́b aá saké moosyəə́l asáá. 
\p  
\v 12 Áde ámáá bɔ́ mekuu awobe, anhɛ́ ḿmē nkob á yə̌l, átīm ámbīd áwē eʼdii. Hɛ́ɛ ásɛdtɛɛ́ bɔ́ aáken, “Nyêsóŋtɛ́né dyam áde ḿbɛ́nlé nyé-yɛ?  
\v 13 Nyêchəge mɛ Meléede, nyêchəge-ʼɛ mɛ Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́. Nyêtə́ŋgɛ́né, áyə̄le nɛ̂ děn dɔ́ɔ ńdíí.  
\v 14 Né-ɔɔ́, nzé mɛ awě ndé nyé Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́ mbɛ́-ʼɛ nyé Meléede nwǒbpé nyé mekuu, né nyémpē nyêtə́ŋgɛ́né nhɔ́g ne aníníí mekuu awobe.  
\v 15 Nlúmté nyé eláŋsɛ́n éche nyétə́ŋgɛ́né ahíd âbɛl nɛ́n nyémpē nyébɛl ngáne ḿbɛ́nlé nyé.  
\v 16 Ne mbále nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, mbəledɛ eetómɛ́ɛ́ eche sáŋ, mod awě bélómé-ʼɛ eetómɛ́ɛ́ mod awě alómé mɔ́.  
\v 17 Bɔɔb áde nyébíí ḿmɛ́n mam, nnam mɛ́bɛ̄ ne nyé nzé nyêbɛle mɔ́. 
\p  
\v 18 “Meehɔ́bɛ́ɛ́ nyé moosyəə́l. Mbíí bad ábe ḿpwɛ́dé. Boŋ eʼyale ábe éʼténlédé á Kálag e Dyǒb éʼtə́ŋgɛ́né alón. Éténlédé nɛ́n bán, ‘Mod awě súmɔ̄ sêdyâg ndyééd akǔnnɛ́né mɛ yə̌l.’  
\v 19 Nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n bɔɔb, áde éēbɛ̄nlēdɛ̄ɛ̄ âbɛl nɛ́n nzé ébɛ́nlédé, nyédúbe nɛ́n bán, ‘Ndíi mɔ́ Awě Ńdíí.’  
\v 20 Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě akobé mod awě ńlómé, akobé mɛ. Kénzɛ́ɛ́-ʼɛ awě akobé mɛ né akobé ane awě alómé mɛ.” 
\s1 Yesuɛ ahɔ́bé áʼsō éʼ póndé aá bɛ́sōm mɔ́ 
\r (Mat 26.20-25; Mak 14.17-21; Luk 22.21-23) 
\p  
\v 21 Áde Yesuɛ ámáá ḿmɛ́n mekan ahɔ́b ndutul enlɔ́g mɔ́ á nlém-tê, ápanléd-tɛ ábē bembapɛɛ áte aá, “Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, nyé mod nhɔ́g ǎbɛ̌ mɛ á mekáá mé bad bé ekɔyí.”  
\v 22 Hɛ́ɛ ábē bembapɛɛ bénɔ́nné á mesó, áyə̄le bénkêmbííʼɛ́ mod awě áhɔ́bɛɛ́.  
\v 23 Mbapɛɛ nhɔ́g, awě Yesuɛ ândəŋgé, andyɛ̌ mɔ́ á akéb.  
\v 24 Dɔ́ɔ Simɔn Petro ápebtanné ane mbapɛɛ mǐd, áhɔ̄bē aá, “Sɛdéd mɔ́ mod awě áhɔ́bɛɛ́.”  
\v 25 Dɔ́ɔ ane mbapɛɛ ásídté Yesuɛ á yə̌l-tê, ásɛdté mɔ́ aáken, “A-Sáŋ, nzɛ́ɛ́ éhɔ́bɛɛ́?”  
\v 26 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Mod awě mɛ́tɔdɛ́ɛ́ ewɛle á dǐsɛ-tê boŋ ḿbɛ mɔ́, mɔ́ adé ane mod.” Hɛ́ɛ átédé ewɛle, átɔdté á dǐsɛ-tê, ábagé Judasɛ, mwǎn awě Simɔn Iskariɔdɛ.  
\v 27 Akob áde Judasɛ ákóbé échê ewɛle, Satanɛ ansɔ́l mɔ́ áte. Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Dyam áde éhɛdɛɛ́ abɛl bɛ̌l dɔ́ á mehélé-te.”  
\v 28 Boŋ mod ké nhɔ́g awě bɔ́bɔ̄ɔ bédyágéʼáá ndyééd enkênsóŋtɛ́nné chǒm-ɛ́ɛ ékə́ə́ boŋ Yesuɛ aláá Judasɛ nɛ̂.  
\v 29 Ngáne édíí bán Judasɛ mɔ̂ akǒŋgéʼáá ekwɛ é mɔné, doŋge á bembapɛɛ bénwēmtɛ̄n bán Yesuɛ alâŋge mɔ́ aá ákɛ áchan bwěm ábe bɛ́bɛnlédté á ngande, kéʼɛ chǒm éche bɛ́bɛɛ́ betóótōkɛ̄ bé bad.  
\v 30 Áde Judasɛ ákóbé ewɛle éche Yesuɛ ábágé mɔ́ kobɛ́n, ambíd ebwɔ́g. Ehíntɛ́n ênkwɛ̌. 
\s1 Yesuɛ abagé mbéndé e ekɔ́ɔ́lé 
\p  
\v 31 Áde Judasɛ ámáá abíd dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́ ehúmé e Mwǎn-a-Moonyoŋ ényínnédé. Ehúmé é Dyǒb-pɛ ámpē ényīnnēd mbwiined ne mwǎn.  
\v 32 Nzé Dyǒb ákúdé ehúmé ámbīd e Mwǎn, né Dyǒb děn ámpē dɛ́bɛ̌l ehúmé é Mwǎn ényînned. Ǎbɛ̌l-lɛ nɛ̂ ábwɔ̄g-ábwɔ̄g.  
\v 33 A-baányaŋ, echem póndé âbɛ́ ne nyé, edé esóŋ. Nyɛ́ɛ̄hɛ̌d mɛ, boŋ ngáne ménlāāʼɛ́ bad bé Israɛl, melemlem nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ ńlâŋgɛɛ́ nyé bɔɔb, mɛɛ́, ‘Wɛ́ɛ ńkagké, nyéehɛnlé apɛ áhed.’  
\v 34 Mbage nyé mbéndé ekɔ́ɔ́lé bɔɔb, nɛ́n nyédəŋ nhɔ́g ne aníníí. Ngáne ńdə́ə́ nyé, nyémpē nyédəŋ nhɔ́g ne aníníí.  
\v 35 Nzé nyêdəə́ nhɔ́g ne aníníí, né mod tɛ́ɛ́ ǎbīī aá nyêdíi ábêm bembapɛɛ.” 
\s1 Yesuɛ ahɔ́bé ngáne Petro ábāŋgē mɔ́ á yə̌l 
\r (Mat 26.31-35; Mak 14.27-31; Luk 22.31-34) 
\p  
\v 36 Simɔn Petro ansɛdéd Yesuɛ aáken, “A-Sáŋ, héé éhɛdɛɛ́ akɛ?” Yesuɛ antimtɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Weéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ ehíd mɛ bɔɔb wɛ́ɛ ńkagké, boŋ ámbīd e póndé wɛ̌hīd mɛ.”  
\v 37 Petro ansɛdéd mɔ́ aá, “A-Sáŋ, cheé ékə́ə́ boŋ meéhɛ̄lē se nhíd wɛ bɔɔb? Mbǒŋsɛ́né âwɛ́ á nló ḿmôŋ.”  
\v 38 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ákwɛntanné mɔ́ aá, “Ekoó aboŋsɛn dé awɛ́ á nló ḿmêm-ɛ? Ne mbále, nlâŋge wɛ mɛɛ́, nchóm-a-kúb adɛ̂hɔ́b aá mɔ́tōoʼ, wɛ̌bāŋ mɛ á yə̌l ngen éláán.” 
\c 14  
\s1 Yesuɛ mɔ́ adé Nzii e mbále  //  echě epɛɛne aloŋgé 
\p  
\v 1 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ ábádɛɛ́ ábē bembapɛɛ aláa aá, “Nyéētagté nlém á abum. Nyésum nlém wɛ́ɛ Dyǒb, nyésum-mɛ kə́ə́ŋne áwêm.  
\v 2 Toŋ ébúú áte á ndáb echě echem Sáŋ. Nkag-kɛ áwed âboŋsɛn nyé hǒm. Nzé énkêmbɛ́ nɛ̂, né menkênlááʼɛ́ nyé mɛɛ́ nkag nyé hǒm aboŋsɛn.  
\v 3 Nzé nkií-ʼɛ nyé hǒm aboŋsɛn, mɛ̌tǐm ámbīd, ńhyɛ ntéd nyé âbɛ́ ne mɛ, âbɛl nyémpē nyébɛ̂ hǒm áde ńdíí.  
\v 4 Nyêbíí nzii echě etimeʼ wɛ́ɛ ńkagké.”  
\v 5 Hɛ́ɛ Tɔmasɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “A-Sáŋ, séebíiʼɛ́ wɛ́ɛ ékagké. Chán-nɔ̄ sɛ́bwɛɛ́ nzii abíi echě etime áwed?”  
\v 6 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Mɛ́ɛ ndé nzii eché ekag wɛ́ɛ echem Sáŋ, mbále ehúɛʼ ne mɛ, mɛ-ʼaá mbage aloŋgé. Modmod eéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ ápɛ wɛ́ɛ echem Sáŋ, ésebán abwedé áwêm.”  
\v 7 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ ábē bembapɛɛ aá, “Bɔɔb áde nyébíí mɛ, nyɛ́ɛ̄bīī kə́ə́ŋne echem Sáŋ.\f + \fr 14:7 \fq Bɔɔb áde nyébíí mɛ, nyɛ́ɛ̄bīī kə́ə́ŋne echem Sáŋ; \ft doŋge á kálag déʼsó áwóó \fq nzé nyênkǒŋ mɛ abíi, né nyɛ́ɛ̄bīī kə́ə́ŋne echem Sáŋ.\f* Bootya bɔɔb nyênyíné mɔ́, nyêbíí-ʼɛ mɔ́.” 
\p  
\v 8 Filibɛ anláá mɔ́ aá, “A-Sáŋ, lúméd-tɛ sé Titɛ́ɛ. Chǒm ésyə̄ə̄l éche séhɛdɛɛ́ éetómɛɛ́ nɛ̂.”  
\v 9 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “A-Filib, nkémbɛ̄ ne nyé á etûn é póndé, chán-nɔ̄ éhɛlɛɛ́-sɛ ehɔ́b wɛɛ́ mɔ̂bííʼɛ́ mɛ? Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě anyíné mɛ né anyíné Titɛ́ɛ. Chán-nɔ̄ éhɛlɛɛ́-sɛ ehɔ́b wɛɛ́ ‘Lúméd sé Titɛ́ɛ?’  
\v 10 Weedúbpɛɛ́ wɛɛ́ echem Sáŋ adíī mɛ áte, mɛ-ʼɛ mbɛ́ mɔ́ áte-yɛ?” Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ ábē bembapɛɛ aá, “Mam ḿme ńlâŋgɛɛ́ nyé méebídɛɛ́ áwêm děn. Boŋ echem Sáŋ awě adé mɛ áte mɔ̂ abɛle ḿmê nsɔ́n.  
\v 11 Nyédúbe mɛ ngáne ńhɔ́bé mɛɛ́ echem Sáŋ adíi mɛ áte, mɛ-ʼɛ mbɛ́ mɔ́ áte. Nzé nyéedúbpe nɛ̂, nyêdúbé ké áyə̄le mam mé menyáké ḿme ḿbɛlɛɛ́.  
\v 12 Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adúbpé mɛ, ǎbɛ̌l mam ḿmě ḿbɛlɛɛ́. Ǎbɛ̌l-lɛ kə́ə́ŋne mekan ḿme métómé ḿmɛ́n áyə̄le nkag wɛ́ɛ Titɛ́ɛ.  
\v 13 Mɛ̌bɛ̌l-lɛ kéchéé éche nyésɛ́dté á dǐn ádêm âbɛl nɛ́n ngum echě Titɛ́ɛ ényînned ámbīd e Mwǎn.  
\v 14 Nzé nyêsɛdté mɛ kéchéé á dǐn ádêm, mɛ̌bɛl chɔ́.” 
\s1 Yesuɛ aá mɔ́ɔ̄lōm Edəə́dəŋ éche Ésáá 
\p  
\v 15 Yesuɛ ambád ahɔ́b aá, “Nzé nyêdəə́ mɛ, né nyɛ́ɛ̄hīd échem mbéndé.  
\v 16 Mɛ̌lāā Titɛ́ɛ, ǎbɛ̌-ʼɛ nyé Nwôŋgɛne ampée, awě ǎbɛ̄ ne nyé á ngíndé ne á ngíndé.  
\v 17 Ane Nwôŋgɛne mɔ̂ adé Edəə́dəŋ échě ébídteʼ mbále áwed tə̂ŋgɛne Dyǒb. Bad bé nkǒŋsé béehɛlɛ́ɛ́-sɛ békob mɔ́, áyə̄le béēnyīnɛ̄ɛ̄ mɔ́, béēbíi-ʼaá mɔ́. Boŋ nyêbíí mɔ́ áyə̄le adé ne nyé, ǎbɛ̄-ʼɛ nyé áte.\f + \fr 14:17 \fq Ǎbɛ̄-ʼɛ nyé áte; \ft doŋge á kálag déʼsó áwóó \fq adɛ́-ʼɛ nyé áte.\f* 
\v 18 Nzé nkií, méetɛdɛ́ɛ́ nyé menyuu. Mɛ̌tǐm ámbīd áwɛ̄n.  
\v 19 Mwǎmpīn ḿ póndé, nkǒŋsé méenyínné mɛ ámpē. Boŋ nyépɛn nyɛ́ɛ̄nyīn mɛ. Ngáne mɛ́bɛ̄ɛ̄ á aloŋgé, nyémpē nyɛ́ɛ̄bɛ̄.  
\v 20 Nzé échê epun épédé, nyɛ́ɛ̄bīī bán ndé echem Sáŋ áte, nyé-ʼɛ nyêbɛ́ mɛ áte, melemlem ngáne mɛ-ʼɛ ńdíí nyé áte.  
\v 21 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě akobé échem mbéndé, áhīdē-ʼɛ chɔ́, mɔ̂ adé mod awě adəə́ mɛ. Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adəə́-ʼɛ mɛ, echem Sáŋ mɔ́-ʼɛ ǎdəŋ mɔ́. Mɛ́mpē mɛ̌dəŋ mɔ́ nlúméd-tɛ mɔ́ yə̌l.”  
\v 22 Dɔ́ɔ Judasɛ (saké Judas Iskariɔdɛ) áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “Boŋ A-Sáŋ, chán wɛ́lūmēdtē sé yə̌l boŋ weelúmté nkǒŋsé pɛn?”  
\v 23 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Nzé mod adəə́ mɛ, ǎhīd ábêm eʼyale. Echem Sáŋ ǎdəŋ mɔ́, sé echem Sáŋ-ʼɛ sɛ́ɛ̄pɛ̌ áwē, sédyɛ̄ɛ̄-ʼɛ ne mɔ́.  
\v 24 Nzé mod eédəə mɛ, eehídɛ́ɛ́ ádêm ayə́ge. Ádɛ́n ayə́ge áde nyéwógé déesaá ádêm. Ádíi áde Titɛ́ɛ awě alómé mɛ. 
\p  
\v 25 “Nláŋgé nyé ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l áde ńdíí ndé ne nyé.  
\v 26 Nwôŋgɛne, Edəə́dəŋ éche Ésáá awě Titɛ́ɛ álōmmē á dǐn ádêm, ǎyə̄gēd nyé mekan mésyə̄ə̄l ǎbɛ̌l-lɛ nyékamtán mekan mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme ńláŋgé nyé.  
\v 27 Nsaŋ mɔ́ɔ ńlyə́gnédé nyé. Ḿmêm nsaŋ mɔ́ɔ ḿbagɛɛ́ nyé. Meébāgɛ̄ɛ̄ nyé mɔ́ ngáne nkǒŋsé ḿbagɛɛ́. Nyéētagté nlém á abum, nyéewógé mbwɔ́g.  
\v 28 Nyênwóg nɛ́ɛ ńhɔ́bé mɛɛ́ ‘Mɛ̌tɛdé nyé boŋ mɛ̌tǐm ámbīd áwɛ̄n.’ Nzé nyêndə̌ŋ mɛ né nyɛ́ɛ̄wóg menyiŋge bán nkag wɛ́ɛ Titɛ́ɛ áyə̄le Titɛ́ɛ atómé mɛ.  
\v 29 Nláŋgé nyé nɛ́n bɔɔb áde éēbɛ̄nlēdɛ̄ɛ̄, âbɛl nɛ́n nzé ébɛ́nlédé, nyédúbe.  
\v 30 Syánē déebudté póndé awóŋ âkal ámpē, áyə̄le nkamlɛnɛ a nkǒŋsé ahúɛʼ. Eewóoʼɛ́ ngíne ké pɔ́g ámīn echêm.  
\v 31 Boŋ kénɛ̂ mɛ̌chennéd mɔ́ yə̌l ḿbɛ̄l ngáne echem Sáŋ áhɔ́bé aá ḿbɛl, âbɛl boŋ nkǒŋsé ḿbíi nɛ́n bán, ndəə́ echem Sáŋ. Né-ʼaá ákə́ə́ boŋ ḿbɛlé kéchéé éche áhɔ́bé aá ḿbɛl. 
\p “Nyéhyag syánē déhide hɛ́n. 
\c 15  
\s1 Yesuɛ mɔ̂ akoó alín dé epum á bwɛl abɛ́ 
\p  
\v 1 “Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé alín dé epum é bwɛl, alín dé epum é bwɛl děn děn. Echem Sáŋ-ʼɛ abɛ́ mbɛlé-nzag.  
\v 2 Ahúdeʼ ngɛn ké ehéé echě edé mɛ á yə̌l, echě eechyááʼ eʼpum, ápagké-ʼɛ ké ehéé echě echyáaʼ eʼpum, âbɛl boŋ éboŋ yə̌l ébude-ʼɛ achyáa.  
\v 3 Ayə́ge áde ń'yə́gté nyé ábɛ́lé nyêmaá asáŋ.  
\v 4 Nyélyəg nyébɛ̂ ne mɛ, mɛ́mpē mɛ̌lyə̌g mbɛ́ ne nyé. Ngɛn chěn eéhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ echyáá eʼpum áde éesaá á alín á bwɛl. Melemlem nɛ́ɛ nyémpē nyéehɛlɛ́ɛ́-sɛ nyêchyáá eʼpum ésebán nyêdé ne mɛ. 
\p  
\v 5 “Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé alín dé epum é bwɛl, nyé-ʼɛ nyêbɛ́ ngɛn. Nzé mod adíí adé ne mɛ boŋ mɛ-ʼɛ ndé ne mɔ́ ǎchyāā eʼpum bwâmbwam. Nyéēhɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄-sɛ nyébɛ̄l dyamdyam ésebɛ́ ne mɛ.  
\v 6 Nzé mod eésɛ̄ ne mɛ, bɛ́hūd mɔ́ nɛ́ɛ ngɛn. Ene ngɛn ebɛlé ekíntéd. Béladɛɛ́ échê ndín é ngɛn áte, bébwém chɔ́ á muú-te, éhyáŋ-ʼɛ.  
\v 7 Nzé nyêdíi nyêdé ne mɛ, boŋ ádêm ayə́ge-ʼɛ ádíi ádé nyé áte, kéchéé éche nyésɛ́dté, nyɛ́ɛ̄kǔd.  
\v 8 Edúbé éche echem Sáŋ ényînnad nzé nyêbudé eʼpum achyáa, nɛ̂-ʼaá dɛ́bɛ̌l nyêbɛ́ ábêm bembapɛɛ.  
\v 9 Ngáne echem Sáŋ ádə́ə́ mɛ, melemlem nɛ́ɛ mɛ́mpē ńdə́ə́ nyé. Né-ɔɔ́ nyédíi nyébɛ̂ ne mɛ âbɛl boŋ ḿbɛ̂ ńdəŋ nyé.  
\v 10 Nzé nyêhídé échêm mbéndé, né mɛ̌bɛ̄ ńdəŋ nyé. Melemlem nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ ńhídɛɛ́ mbéndé échě echem Sáŋ, adíi adəə́-ʼɛ mɛ.  
\v 11 Nlâŋge nyé ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l âbɛl nɛ́n nyémpē nyéwôg nyaa e menyiŋge echě ńwogɛɛ́, ḿmɛ̄n menyiŋge mélôn-nɛ mbon.  
\v 12 Echem mbéndé edíi nɛ́n, nyédəŋ nhɔ́g ne aníníí melemlem nɛ̂ŋgáne ńdə́ə́ nyé.  
\v 13 Nzé mod awédé á nló ḿ baáb, né alúmté edəŋge éche étómtɛ́né achab ámīn.  
\v 14 Nzé nyêbɛleʼ mekan ḿme ńláŋgé nyé mɛɛ́ nyébɛl né nyêdíi ábêm besón.  
\v 15 Meéchə̄gɛ̄ɛ̄ nyé bembəledɛ ámpē, áyə̄le bembəledɛ béēbyɛ̄ɛ̄ʼɛ́ mam ḿme echab sáŋ ábɛlɛɛ́. Boŋ ńchəgɛɛ́ nyé mɛɛ́ ábêm besón áyə̄le nláŋgé nyé mam mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme echem Sáŋ áláŋgé mɛ.  
\v 16 Nyéēpwɛdɛɛ́ mɛ, boŋ mɛ-ɛɛ́ mpwɛdé nyé, nlóm-mɛ nyé âbɛl mekan ḿme méchyáa eʼpum éʼ bwâm. Nyaa é mekan échě ébɛ̄ abɛ́ ne abɛ́. Nzé nyêbɛlé-ʼɛ nɛ̂, echem Sáŋ ǎbɛ̌ nyé kéchéé éche nyésɛ́dté á dǐn ádêm.  
\v 17 Ḿmɛ́n mam mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme ńlâŋgɛɛ́ nyé-ɔɔ́, médíi nɛ́n mɛɛ́, nyédəŋ nhɔ́g ne aníníí.”\fig Alín á bwɛl ne ábē eʼpum|src="hk00112c.tif" size="span" ref="15.1-17" \fig* 
\s1 Bad bé nkǒŋsé bɛ́kɔɔ́ nyé 
\p  
\v 18 Yesuɛ ambád ábē bembapɛɛ aláa aá, “Nzé nkǒŋsé ńkɔ́ɔ́ nyé, nyébíi nɛ́n bán mɛɛ́ bésébpé akɔɔ.  
\v 19 Nzé nyêmbɛ́ nɛ̂ŋgáne bad bé nkǒŋsé, né nkǒŋsé mɛ́tēd nyé nɛ̂ŋgáne ábē bad. Boŋ mpwɛdé nyé átîntê e bad bé nkǒŋsé. Nyéēsaá bad bé nkǒŋsé. Né-ʼaá ákə́ə́ boŋ nkǒŋsé ńkɔ̄ɔ̄ nyé.  
\v 20 Nyéwêmtɛn ehɔ́b éche ménlāāʼɛ́ nyé mɛɛ́ ‘Mbəledɛ eetómɛ́ɛ́ eche sáŋ.’ Nzé bêmbané mɛ á metake-tê né bɛ́bané nyémpē á metake-tê. Nzé bénhīd ádêm ayə́ge né bɛ́hīd-tɛ ádɛ̄n ámpē.  
\v 21 Bɛ́bɛl nyé ḿmɛ́n mekan mésyə̄ə̄l á yə̌l á dǐn ádêm, áyə̄le béēbíiʼɛ́ ane awě alómé mɛ.  
\v 22 Nzé menkêmpɛ̌ boŋ nláá bɔ́ ḿmɛ́n mam, né ḿmab mbéb méenyînnedɛɛ́. Boŋ bɔɔb, béewóoʼɛ́ nzɔm ké pɔ́g áyə̄le ḿmab mbéb.  
\v 23 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě akɔɔ́ mɛ, akɔɔ́ kə́ə́ŋne echem Sáŋ.  
\v 24 Nzé menkêmbɛl ndín é mam átîntê echâb éche mod ampée éēbɛ̄lɛ̄ɛ̄ mbêd, né ḿmab mbéb méenyînnedɛɛ́. Boŋ bɔɔb bényíné mekan mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme ḿbɛ́lé, ké nɛ̂ bédíi békɔ́ɔ́ mɛ, békɔ̄ɔ̄-ʼɛ echem Sáŋ.  
\v 25 Nɛ́n ádé âlóned eʼyale ábe éʼténlédé á mbéndé echâb bán, ‘Nzɔm ké pɔ́g enkêmbáá eche békɔ́ɔ́né mɛ.’  
\v 26 Nwôŋgɛne ǎbīd wɛ́ɛ Titɛ́ɛ. Adíi Edəə́dəŋ éche ébɛleʼ boŋ bad bésóŋtɛ́n mbále. Ádě mɛ́bɛ̄ɛ̄ ne Titɛ́ɛ mɛ̌lōmē nyé mɔ́, mɔ́-ʼaá ǎlāā nyé mam tə̂ŋgɛne mɛ.  
\v 27 Nyémpē nyɛ́ɛ̄hɔ̄b mam tə̂ŋgɛne mɛ áyə̄le nyêdé ne mɛ se á mbooted. 
\c 16  
\p  
\v 1 “Nlâŋge nyé ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l âbɛl boŋ nyéētimné mbíd.  
\v 2 Bɛ́bīdēd nyé á ndáb é mekáne. A mbále póndé ehúɛʼ eche kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě ǎwūū nyé áwēmtɛ̄nnē aá mɔ́bɛnle Dyǒb.  
\v 3 Bɛ́bɛ̌l ḿmɛ́n mam áyə̄le béēbíiʼɛ́ echem Sáŋ béēbíi-ʼaá mɛ.  
\v 4 Nláŋgé nyé ḿmɛ́n mam mésyə̄ə̄l âbɛl boŋ nzé póndé epedé echě ḿmɛ́n mekan mébɛnladté, nyɛ́ɛ̄kamtɛ́n bán menlááʼ nyé. 
\s1 Nsɔ́n ḿme Edəə́dəŋ ébɛnlé 
\p “Menkênlááʼɛ́ nyé ḿmɛ́n mekan á mbooted, áyə̄le membɛ́ ne nyé.  
\v 5 Boŋ bɔɔb, nkag wɛ́ɛ mod awě alómé mɛ. Ké nɛ̂, nyé modmod nyéesɛdtɛɛ́ mɛ bánken ‘Héé ékagké?’  
\v 6 Aláa ádé ńláŋgé nyé ḿmɛ́n mekan ábɛ́lé ndutul elɔ́gé nyé á nlém-tê.  
\v 7 Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́, édé mboŋ nɛ́n bán ńkɛ. Áyə̄le nzé meékii, né Nwôŋgɛne éepaá áwɛ̄n. Boŋ nzé nkií, mɛ̌lōmē nyé mɔ́.  
\v 8 Áde ápɛɛ́, álūmēd bad bé nkǒŋsé nɛ́n aá ḿmab nsôŋtɛn ḿme béwánlé tə̂ŋgɛne abɛl dé mbéb ne âbɛl mekan ḿme mésáá méetə̂ŋgɛnɛɛ́. Béēsôŋtɛnɛɛ́-ʼɛ nyaa echě Dyǒb ákáadtɛɛ́.  
\v 9 Ḿmab nsôŋtɛn méetə̂ŋgɛnɛɛ́ tə̂ŋgɛne mbéb, áyə̄le béedúbpɛɛ́ mɛ.  
\v 10 Méetə̂ŋgɛnɛɛ́ tə̂ŋgɛne abɛl dé mekan ḿme mésáá, áyə̄le nkag wɛ́ɛ Titɛ́ɛ, nyéenyín-naá mɛ ámpē.  
\v 11 Méetə̂ŋgɛnɛɛ́ tə̂ŋgɛne nyaa echě Dyǒb ákáadtɛɛ́, áyə̄le amaá nkamlɛnɛ a nkǒŋsé akáad. 
\p  
\v 12 “Ndíi nwóó ekud é mekan âláa nyé boŋ ḿmê mekan mɛ́tom nyé áte.  
\v 13 Boŋ áde Edəə́dəŋ é mbále épɛɛ́, ǎbɛ̌l nyêbíí mbále esyəə́l. Éehɔ́bénné echě kunze chěn. Dyam áde bɛ́lāāʼɛ́ mɔ́ dɔ́ɔ áhɔ̄bpē, ǎlāā-ʼɛ nyé mam ḿme mɛ́bɛnléd póndé echě ehúɛʼ áʼsō.  
\v 14 Ǎchə̄gēd échêm edúbé ámīn áyə̄le kéchéé éche áwógé áwêm chɔ́ɔ mɔ́-ʼɛ álāāʼɛ́ nyé.  
\v 15 Kéchéé éche echem Sáŋ áwóó édíi échêm. Nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ ákə́ə́ boŋ ńhɔ̄bē mɛɛ́ Edəə́dəŋ étēd kéchéé éche ńhɔ́bé, éláá nyé.” 
\s1 Ndutul ětǐm menyiŋge 
\p  
\v 16 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ábádɛɛ́ aá, “Mwǎmpīn ḿ póndé nyéenyínné mɛ ámpē, mwǎmpīn ḿ póndé-ʼɛ ámbīd enɛ̂ nyɛ́ɛ̄nyīn mɛ.”  
\v 17 Dɔ́ɔ doŋge dé bembapɛɛ bésɛdtɛɛ́ nhɔ́g ne aníníí bánken, “Cheé áwémtɛ́né ahɔ́b, âláa syánē aá, ‘Mwǎmpīn ḿ póndé nyéenyínné mɛ ámpē, mwǎmpīn ḿ póndé-ʼɛ ámbīd e nɛ̂ nyɛ́ɛ̄nyīn mɛ?’ Ahɔ́b-pɛ ámpē aá, ‘Áyə̄le nkag wɛ́ɛ Titɛ́ɛ.’ ”  
\v 18 Bémbɛ̄ bésɛdté bánken, “Cheé áwémtɛ́né ahɔ́b, âhɔ́b aá, ‘Mwǎmpīn ḿ póndé?’ Séesôŋtɛnɛɛ́ dyam áde áhɔ́bɛɛ́.” 
\p  
\v 19 Yesuɛ ammǎd abíi aá, béhɛde mɔ́ dyam asɛded. Né-ɔɔ́, anláá bɔ́ aá, “Dyam áde ńhɔ́bé mɛɛ́, ‘Mwǎmpīn ḿ póndé nyéenyínné mɛ ámpē, mwǎmpīn ḿ póndé-ʼɛ ámbīd e nɛ̂, nyɛ́ɛ̄nyīn mɛ,’ dɔ́ɔ nyésɛdtɛɛ́ nhɔ́g ne aníníí-yɛ?  
\v 20 Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé mɛɛ́, nyɛ́ɛ̄chií, nyélēb-pɛ, boŋ nkǒŋsé mɛ́wōg menyiŋge. Nyɛ́ɛ̄sudɛ́n, boŋ ḿmê nsudɛn mɛ́tǐm menyiŋge.  
\v 21 Mmwaád awě ahɛde achyáá abɛlé ásudɛn áyə̄le eche póndé e metake epedé. Boŋ nzé amaá achyáa abɛlé awóg menyiŋge, áyə̄le moonyoŋ achyáádté á nkǒŋsé.  
\v 22 Nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ édíí ne nyé. Nyêsǔdné bɔɔb, boŋ mɛ̌nyīn nyémpē. Ene póndé ḿmɛn nlém mɛ́lōn ne menyiŋge, modmod éehɛnlé-ʼaá nyé ḿmê menyiŋge akobɛn.  
\v 23 Áde échê epun épɛɛ́, nyéesɛdédté mɛ dyamdyam. Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛɛ́ Titɛ́ɛ ǎbɛ̌ nyé kéchéé échě nyésɛ́dté á dǐn ádêm.\f + \fr 16:23 \fq Titɛ́ɛ ǎbɛ̌ nyé kéchéé échě nyésɛ́dté á dǐn ádêm: \ft doŋge á kálag áwóó \fq Nzé nyêsɛ̌dté Titɛ́ɛ kéchéé, ǎbɛ̌ nyé chɔ́ á dǐn ádêm.\f* 
\v 24 Kə́ə́ŋne bɔɔb nyéēhɛ̄dnɛ̄ɛ̄ mɔ́ chǒmchǒm á dǐn ádêm. Nyéhɛdɛn mɔ́, nyɛ́ɛ̄kǔd âbɛl nɛ́n ḿmɛ̄n menyiŋge mélɔ̂g mbon.” 
\s1 Yesuɛ atómé nkǒŋsé áte 
\p  
\v 25 Yesuɛ ambád ábē bembapɛɛ aláa aá, “Mbɛ̌nlédé ngan âláa nyé ekud é mekan. Póndé ehúɛʼ echě méebɛnlédté ngan. Mɛ́lāā-ʼɛ nyé mekan tə̂ŋgɛne Titɛ́ɛ, nyaa echě nyɛ́sōŋtɛ̄nnē.  
\v 26 Échê epun, nyɛ́ɛ̄hɛdɛ́n mɔ́ kéchéé á dǐn ádêm. Méetɔgɛ́n-naá mɔ́ aláa mɛɛ́ áwôŋgɛn nyé,  
\v 27 áyə̄le Titɛ́ɛ mwěn adəə́ nyé. Adəə́ nyé áyə̄le nyêdəə́ mɛ, nyêdúbpé-ʼɛ bán mbídé áwē.  
\v 28 Membíd wɛ́ɛ Titɛ́ɛ, ḿpɛ̄ á nkǒŋsé-te, bɔɔb-pɛ ntɛdte nkǒŋsé, ntime ámbīd wɛ́ɛ Titɛ́ɛ.” 
\p  
\v 29 Hɛ́ɛ ábē bembapɛɛ béhɔ́bɛɛ́ bán, “Ehɔ́be bɔɔb ngáne sɛ́sōŋtɛ̄nnē, weébɛnládté ngan.  
\v 30 Sêbíí bɔɔb bán ebíí mekan mésyə̄ə̄l, éehɛdnád-taá bán modmod ásɛded wɛ dyamdyam. Nɛ́n ábɛ́lé sêdúbpé bán ebídé wɛ́ɛ Dyǒb.”  
\v 31 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ ákwɛntanné bɔ́ aá, “Nyêdúbpé bɔɔb-ɛ?  
\v 32 Nyénɔneʼ! Póndé ehúɛʼ, emaá-ʼɛ apɛ, áde nyɛ́pāŋtēdtē áte. Mod tɛ́ɛ́ atóm mehélé wɛ́ɛ ábídé, nyétɛ̄dē mměmpɛn. Boŋ ké nɛ̂, meésaá mměmpɛn, Titɛ́ɛ adé ne mɛ.  
\v 33 Nlâŋge nyé ḿmɛ́n mekan âbɛl nɛ́n nyébɛ̂ nsaŋ abɛ́ ádě nyédíí ne mɛ. Nyɛ́ɛ̄kǔd metake á nkǒŋsé-te boŋ nyéwêd nlém á abum. Ntómé nkǒŋsé áte.” 
\c 17  
\s1 Yesuɛ akánnédé eche yə̌l 
\p  
\v 1 Áde Yesuɛ ámáá ḿmɛ́n mekan mésyə̄ə̄l ahɔ́b, dɔ́ɔ ánɔ́né ámīn boŋ áhɔ̄bē aá, “A-Tɛ̂, póndé emaá apɛ. Lúméd bad ehúmé échě awoŋ Mwǎn, âbɛl nɛ́n awoŋ Mwǎn mɔ́mpē álúmed ehúmé échôŋ.  
\v 2 Ebágé mɔ́ kunze âkamlɛn moosyəə́l, âbɛl nɛ́n ábɛ bad bésyə̄ə̄l ábe ébágé mɔ́ aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ.  
\v 3 Aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ ádíi nɛ́n bébíi wɛ, mmǒn awě edé Dyǒb á mbále, ne âbíi Yesu Krǐstəə, awě élómé.  
\v 4 Mbídté échoŋ ehúmé áwed á nkǒŋsé amad ádé ḿmádé nsɔ́n ḿme ébágé mɛ.  
\v 5 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́ a-Sáŋ, bídéd échêm ehúmé áwed, wɛ́ɛ mmǒŋ édíí. Melemlem mé edúbé ḿme ménwōŋgē ne wɛ, nkǒŋsé ńdé ahɔ́b bán ḿbootad. 
\s1 Yesuɛ akánnédé ábē bembapɛɛ 
\p  
\v 6 “Mbɛlé bad bé nkǒŋsé ábe ébágé mɛ bébíí wɛ. Bébédɛ́ɛ ábôŋ, wembɛ̌ mɛ bɔ́, bébɛ́lé-ʼɛ ngáne ehɔ́bé wɛɛ́ bébɛl.  
\v 7 Bébíí bɔɔb bán kéchéé éche ébágé mɛ, ébídé áwôŋ.  
\v 8 Nláŋgé bɔ́ mam mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme éláŋgé mɛ wɛɛ́ ńláa bɔ́, bédúbpé-ʼɛ ḿmê mam. Bébíí ne mbále bán áwôŋ dɔ́ɔ ḿbídé, bédúbpé-ʼɛ bán wɛ-ɛɛ́ elómé mɛ.  
\v 9 Nkânnad bɔ́. Meekánnádté bad bé nkǒŋsé. Boŋ nkânnad bad ábe ébágé mɛ, áyə̄le bédíi ábôŋ.  
\v 10 Bad bésyə̄ə̄l ábe bédé ábêm bédíi ábôŋ, ábôŋ-ʼɛ bésyə̄ə̄l bédíi ábêm, bébídté-ʼɛ échêm ehúmé áwed.  
\v 11 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, mwǎmpīn ḿ póndé méebáá á nkǒŋsé-te ámpē. Boŋ bédíi bédé á nkǒŋsé-te. Nhyag áwôŋ. Titɛ́ɛ awě Asáá, kəə́ bɔ́ á ngíne e dǐn ádôŋ, dǐn áde ébágé mé. Ngíne echě ébágé mɛ âbɛl nɛ́n bébɛ̂ mod nhɔ́g, melemlem ngáne sóo-ʼɛ ámpē dédíí mod nhɔ́g.  
\v 12 Áde ḿbédé ne bɔ́, menkəə́ bɔ́ á ngíne e dǐn ádôŋ, dǐn áde wêmbɛɛ́ mɛ.\f + \fr 17:12 \fq Menkəə bɔ́ á ngíne e dǐn áde wêmbɛɛ́ me: \ft doŋge a kálag awóó \fq á ngíne e dǐn ádoŋ ménkə́ə́ bad ábê ébágé me.\f* Nkə̌ŋgé bɔ́, bɔ́ mod ké nhɔ́g-kɛ eebɔ́ɔʼɛ́ étōmɛɛ́ mod awě êmmadté abɛ́ bán ǎbɔ̄ɔ âbɛl boŋ ébɛnled ngáne éténlédé á kálag e Dyǒb.  
\v 13 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, nhyag áwôŋ. Nhɔ́be-ʼɛ ḿmɛ́n mekan ngáne ndíi ńdé á nkǒŋsé âbɛl boŋ ḿmāb menyiŋge mélôn mbon, melemlem ngáne ḿmêm-mɛ mélóné mbon.  
\v 14 Nláŋgé bɔ́ mam mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme éláŋgé mɛ wɛɛ́ ńláa bɔ́. Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́ bad bé nkǒŋsé békɔ́ɔ́ bɔ́ áyə̄le béesaá bad bé nkǒŋsé ámpē, melemlem ngáne mɛ ámpē méesaá mod a nkǒŋsé.  
\v 15 Meehɔ́bɛ́ɛ́ mɛɛ́ éhûd bɔ́ á nkǒŋsé-te, boŋ nhɔ́beʼ mɛɛ́ ékəəʼ bɔ́ âbɛl boŋ Mod e Ebébtéd eébɛ̄lēʼ bɔ́ mbéb.  
\v 16 Béesaá bad bé nkǒŋsé melemlem nɛ̂ŋgáne méesaá mod a nkǒŋsé.  
\v 17 Bɛnléd echoŋ mbále âbɛl boŋ béhɛl wɛ abɛle. Échôŋ eyale édé mbále.  
\v 18 Nlómé bɔ́ á nkǒŋsé-te melemlem nɛ̂ŋgáne wɛ́mpē wénlōmmē mɛ á nkǒŋsé-te.  
\v 19 Á etútú échâb membɛ̌ echem yə̌l âbɛle wɛ âbɛl boŋ bɔ́mpē bébɛ échab yə̌l âbɛl boŋ békoŋ wɛ abɛle. 
\s1 Yesuɛ akánnédé bad ábê béedúbé mɔ́ bésyə̄ə̄l 
\p  
\v 20 “Meekánnádté ábêm bembapɛɛ běnpɛn boŋ nkânnad kə́ə́ŋne bad ábe bédúbpé mɛ áyə̄le mam ḿme béwógé áwāb.  
\v 21 Nkânneʼ mɛɛ́ bɔ́ moosyəə́l bébɛ̂ mod nhɔ́g. A-Tɛ̂, bɔ́ moosyəə́l bébɛ̂ mod nhɔ́g ne sóo, melemlem nɛ̂ŋgáne édíí ne mɛ, mɛ-ʼɛ mbɛ́ ne wɛ. Bébɛ̂ mod nhɔ́g âbɛl nɛ́n nkǒŋsé ńdúbe bán wɛ-ɛɛ́ elómé mɛ.  
\v 22 Ehúmé éche ébágé mɛ, mɛ-ʼɛ mbagé bɔ́. Mbagé bɔ́ âbɛl boŋ bébɛ̂ mod nhɔ́g melemlem nɛ̂ŋgáne sóo dédíí mod nhɔ́g.  
\v 23 Ńdé mod nhɔ́g ne bɔ́, wɛ-ʼɛ edé mod nhɔ́g ne mɛ. Nɛ́n dɛ́bɛ̌l békōŋ mod nhɔ́g abɛ́. Békoŋ mod nhɔ́g abɛ́ âbɛl boŋ nkǒŋsé ḿbíi bán wɛ-ɛɛ́ elómé mɛ, bébíi-ʼɛ bán edəə́ bɔ́ melemlem nɛ̂ŋgáne édə́ə́ mɛ.  
\v 24 A-Tɛ̂, ebagé mɛ bɔ́, bébɛ̂ wɛ́ɛ ńdíí, âbɛl boŋ bényîn echêm ehúmé. Wembɛ̌ mɛ ehúmé áyə̄le wendə̌ŋ mɛ se á mbooted mé nkǒŋsé.  
\v 25 A-Tɛ̂, wɛ-ɛɛ́ ebɛle mam ḿmě mésáá. Nkǒŋsé méebíiʼɛ́ wɛ, boŋ mbíí wɛ, ábɛ́n-nɛ ámpē bébíí bán wɛ-ɛɛ́ elómé mɛ.  
\v 26 Mbɛlé bébíí wɛ, mɛ̌bɛ̌l-lɛ ámpē âbɛl nɛ́n edəŋge échě édə́ə́ mɛ ébɛ̂ bɔ́ áte, mɛ-ʼɛ ámpē ḿbɛ̂ ne bɔ́.” 
\c 18  
\s1 Békóbé Yesuɛ 
\r (Mat 26.47-56; Mak 14.43-50; Luk 22.47-53) 
\p  
\v 1 Áde Yesuɛ amáá akáne, bɔ́ɔbɛ ábē bembapɛɛ bênhidé, béchābē mwǎ edíb a Kidrɔn ámīn. Nzag embɛ́ áhed, bénsɔ̄l áwēd-te.  
\v 2 Judasɛ, ntúrɛ́ awě Yesuɛ ambíí ádê abwɔ́g á hǒm, áyə̄le Yesuɛ ne ábē bembapɛɛ bêmmɛntɛ́n aladɛn áhed.  
\v 3 Né-ɔɔ́, Judasɛ antómɛ́n echoŋ é sə́nze ne bembəledɛ bé Ndáb-e-Dyǒb ábe beprisɛ bémbáá ne Befarisia bénlōmmē, békɛ̄ wɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ábédé. Ábê bad bênchǒd eʼkag, béwálé eʼtrúkáŋ ne bwěm éʼ nzum.  
\v 4 Yesuɛ ammǎd mam mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme mɛ́bɛnléd ne mɔ́ abíi, ké nɛ̂, ambídéd yə̌l áwed, ásɛ̄dēd bɔ́ aáken, “Nzɛ́ nyéhɛdɛɛ́?”  
\v 5 Bênkwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ bán, “sêhɛde Yesuɛ, mod a dyad á Nazarɛt.” Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé mɔ́.” Judasɛ ntúrɛ́ awě Yesuɛ ambɛ́ áhed ne ábê bad.  
\v 6 Áde Yesuɛ áhɔ́bé aá, “Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé mɔ́,” bêntimɛ́n mbíd, békwɛ̄ ásē.  
\v 7 Hɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ ásɛdtɛɛ́ bɔ́ ámpē aáken, “Nzɛ́ nyéhɛdɛɛ́?” Bênkwɛntɛ́n bán, “Yesuɛ a dyad á Nazarɛt.”  
\v 8 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ ákwɛntanné bɔ́ aá, “Nláŋgé nyé mɛɛ́, mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé mɔ́. Né-ɔɔ́, nzé nyêhɛde mɛ, nyétɛ̄dē ábén bad ábe bédé ne mɛ, békag.”  
\v 9 Nɛ́n dêmbɛnléd âlóned eʼyale ábe ánhɔ̄bpē aá, “A-Sáŋ, átîntê e bad ábe wêmbɛɛ́ mɛ, meebɔ́dɛɛ́ ké nhɔ́g.”  
\v 10 Simɔn Petro anwálé nkwáté. Hɛ́ɛ ádólé ḿmê nkwáté boŋ átōmtēʼ, ásɛ̄lē etúu é ekáá é mbáá é mbəledɛ awě prisɛ ambáámbáa. Ane mbəledɛ abédé dǐn bán, Malkusɛ.  
\v 11 Yesuɛ anláá Petro aá, “Timéd nkwáté á abám. Nɛ́dē, meetêŋgɛnɛɛ́ metuné ḿme echem Sáŋ átíínédé mɛ akud-ɛ?” 
\s1 Békɛ́ɛ́né Yesuɛ wɛ́ɛ Anasɛ 
\p  
\v 12 Hɛ́ɛ échê echoŋ é sə́nze ne awâb mod ambáá nchoo ne bembəledɛ bé bad bé Israɛl békóbé Yesuɛ béhaŋ mɔ́.  
\v 13 Bénsēbē mɔ́ akɛɛn wɛ́ɛ Anasɛ. Anasɛ abédɛ́ɛ sáŋ-kə́lé awě Kaifasɛ awě abédé prisɛ ambáámbáa ḿmê mwɛ̌.  
\v 14 Kaifasɛ ne, mɔ́ ambɛ̌ bad bémbáá bé Israɛl elébé aá ébóó bán mod nhɔ́g áwɛ̂ á nló ḿ bad bésyə̄ə̄l. 
\s1 Petro abáá Yesuɛ á yə̌l 
\r (Mat 26.69-70; Mak 14.66-68; Luk 22.55-57) 
\p  
\v 15 Simɔn Petro ne mbapɛɛ ampée béhídéʼáá Yesuɛ. Prisɛ ambáámbáa ambíí ane mbapɛɛ, né-ɔɔ́ ane mbapɛɛ ansɔ́l eyáde éche prisɛ ambáámbáa wɛ́ɛ bénsɔ̄lɛ̄nnē Yesuɛ.  
\v 16 Petro pɛn anlyə̌g á mmwɛ mé eʼkɛ́. Dɔ́ɔ ane mbapɛɛ awě prisɛ ambáámbáa ámbīīʼɛ́ átímé ámbīd á mmwɛ, ákālɛ̄n ngɔndérɛ echě enɔnéʼáá mmwɛ boŋ ásɔ̄ltē Petro á eyáde-tê.  
\v 17 Ene ngɔndérɛ ansɛdéd Petro aáken “Kíné wɛ́mpē weésaá mbapɛɛ nhɔ́g awě ane mod-ɛ?” Petro ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Aáy, meésaá.”  
\v 18 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, ahéb démbɛ̄. Né-ɔɔ́, bembəledɛ ábe prisɛ ambáámbáa ne bembəledɛ bé Ndáb-e-Dyǒb bênkonéd muú bétyéém áhed béwāleʼ. Petro mɔ́mpē ambɛ́ áhed, atyéém áwālē muú. 
\s1 Prisɛ ambáámbáa akáadte Yesuɛ 
\r (Mat 26.59-66; Mak 14.55-64; Luk 22.66-71) 
\p  
\v 19 Prisɛ ambáámbáa esɛ̌dtéʼáá Yesuɛ tə̂ŋgɛne ábē bembapɛɛ ne ádē ayə́ge.  
\v 20 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Mam mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme ńláŋgéʼáá bad nhɔ́béʼáá mɔ́ á nhɛ́né. Ayə́ged ádêm ásyə̄ə̄l-ʼɛ, ábédé á Ndáb é mekáne ne á Ndáb-e-Dyǒb wɛ́ɛ bad bé Israɛl bésyə̄ə̄l béladnɛɛ́. Meéhɔ́bɛ́ɛ́-ʼɛ dyamdyam á kun-tê.  
\v 21 Cheé-ɔ̄ ésɛdtɛɛ́ mɛ ámpē. Sɛdéd bad ábe bénwōg mam ḿme ńláŋgé bɔ́. Bébíí mam ḿme ńhɔ́bé.”  
\v 22 Áde Yesuɛ áhɔ́bé nɛ̂, mbəledɛ nhɔ́g ambɔ̌m mɔ́ abɛ́n ahɔ́b aá, “Chán éhɛle éhɔ̄bēʼ nɛ̂ wɛ́ɛ prisɛ ambáámbáa?”  
\v 23 Yesuɛ antimtɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Nzé nhɔ́bé dyam áde déetə̂ŋgɛne, ehɔ́b dɔ́ moosyəə́l áwôg. Boŋ nzé édé bán nhɔ́bé dyam áde átə́ŋgɛ́né, cheé ékə́ə́ boŋ ébɔmé mɛ?”  
\v 24 Dɔ́ɔ Anasɛ áhɔ́bé aá, békɛɛn Yesuɛ wɛ́ɛ Kaifasɛ, prisɛ ambáámbáa. Yesuɛ ambɛ́ abɛ́ á mehaŋ. 
\s1 Petro abáá Yesuɛ á yə̌l ámpē 
\r (Mat 26.71-75; Mak 14.69-72; Luk 22.58-62) 
\p  
\v 25 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, Simɔn Petro ambɛ́ atyéém áhed áwālē muú. Hɛ́ɛ bad ábe bémbɛ̄ áhed bésɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ bán, “Kíné wɛ́mpē weésaá mbapɛɛ nhɔ́g awě ane mod-ɛ?” Petro antáŋ aá, “Aáy, meésaá.”  
\v 26 Mbəledɛ awě prisɛ ambáámbáa nhɔ́g, mwǎnyaŋ mɔ́ɔ Petro ánsɛ̄nlē etúu, anchə́géd ehɔ́b ámīn, aláá Petro aá, “Kíné meenyínɛɛ́ nyúmɔ̄ á nzag-tê-yɛ?”  
\v 27 Petro antáŋ ámpē. Ábwɔ̄g-ábwɔ̄g, nchóm a kúb antóŋ. 
\s1 Payledɛ akáádté Yesuɛ 
\r (Mat 27.1-2, 11-14; Mak 15.1-5; Luk 23.1-5) 
\p  
\v 28 Bad bé Israɛl bênhidnéd Yesuɛ á ndáb wɛ́ɛ Kaifasɛ békɛ̄ɛ̄n mɔ́ á eyáde e nkamlɛnɛ ambáá. Nɛ́n ábédé epɔg é mbwɛmbwɛ. Běn bénkênsɔ́nlé á ndáb-te âbáŋ nɛ́n béenyínnád mbinde áʼsō éʼ Dyǒb \f + \fr 18:28 \ft Bad bé Israɛl béndūbē nɛ́n bán nzé mod asɔ́lé á ndáb e mod awě eésɛ̌ mod a Israɛl, né awɔ́gté yə̌l mbinde. Ne bɔ́, enɛ́n ndín e mod ebágáá mbinde áʼsō éʼ Dyǒb epun saámbé. Enɛ́n póndé esyəə́l eéhɛleʼaá-sɛ adyɛ́ Ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn.\f* âbɛl bédyɛ̂ Ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn.  
\v 29 Né-ɔɔ́, Payledɛ nkamlɛnɛ ambáá a bad bé Roma, ambíd e ebwɔ́g ákɛ atán bɔ́, ásɛdté bɔ́ aáken, “Awusé áhéé nyéhɔ́bé bán anɛ́n mod abɛlé?”  
\v 30 Bênkwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ bán, “Nzé anɛ́n mod enkêmbɛ́ ebébtéd é mod, né séēbagɛɛ́ mɔ́ áwôŋ mekáá.”  
\v 31 Payledɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nyé běn nyétêd mɔ́, nyébɛnled mbéndé echɛ̂n nyékáad mɔ́.” Hɛ́ɛ bad bé Israɛl bélâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ bán, “Séewóoʼɛ́ kunze âwúu mod.”  
\v 32 Nɛ́n dêmbɛnléd âlóned eʼyale ábe Yesuɛ ánhɔ̄bpē âlúmed nyaa e kwééd eche áwɛ̄ɛ̄.  
\v 33 Payledɛ ansɔ́l á ndáb-te ámpē, áchə̄g Yesuɛ, ásɛ̄dēd mɔ́ aá, “Wɛ-ɛɛ́ edé kə̂ŋ e bad bé Israɛl-lɛ?”  
\v 34 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Mmǒn-ɛɛ́ ehɔ́be nɛ̂ ngé bad bémpēe bɔ́ɔ bélāŋgē wɛ mam á yə̌l echêm?”  
\v 35 Payledɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Ndé mod a Israɛl-lɛ? Ábôŋ bad ne beprisɛ bémbáá bɔ́ɔ bébágé wɛ áwêm mekáá. Cheé ébɛ́lé?”  
\v 36 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Ḿmêm nkamlɛn méesaá á nkǒŋsé wɛ́n. Nzé ḿmêm nkamlɛn mémbɛ̄ á nkǒŋsé wɛ́n, né ábêm bembəledɛ bɛ́wǎn, âbɛl nɛ́n bad béebagé mɛ á mekáá mé bad bé Israɛl. Boŋ ḿmêm nkamlɛn méesaá mé nkǒŋsé.”  
\v 37 Dɔ́ɔ Payledɛ ásɛdtɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Nɛ́dē edé kə̂ŋ-ɛ?” Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Wɛ-ɛɛ́ ehɔ́bé wɛɛ́ ndé kə̂ŋ. Nzɔm echě ekəə́ boŋ béchyáá mɛ, ḿpɛ̄ á nkǒŋsé wɛ́n, edíi âbíd mbóŋ e mbále. Mod ké ahéé awě adé mod a mbále awóglan mɛ.”  
\v 38 Payledɛ ansɛdéd mɔ́ aá, “Cheé édé mbále?” 
\s1 Bán Yesuɛ atə́ŋgɛ́né awɛ́ 
\r (Mat 27.15-31; Mak 15.6-20; Luk 23.13-25) 
\p Áde Payledɛ amáá mɔ́ asɛded nɛ́n, ambíd á ebwɔ́g ámpē akɛ atán bad bé Israɛl, anláá bɔ́ aá, “Meekóbnɛɛ́ anɛ́n mod awusé ké ahɔ́g áde mɛ́hɔ̄bpē mɛɛ́ béwúu mɔ́.  
\v 39 Boŋ nyêwóó elem nɛ́n bán, ntə́ŋgɛ́né nyé mod a mbwɔg nhɔ́g abídted á póndé e Ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn. Nyêdəə́ bán ḿbídted nyé kə̂ŋ e bad bé Israɛl-lɛ?”  
\v 40 Bênkwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ ne eʼsaád bán, “Aáy! Séēhɛ̄dɛ̄ɛ̄ mɔ́. Bídtéd sé Barabasɛ.” (Barabasɛ abédé-ʼɛ nchîb ambáá.) 
\c 19  
\p  
\v 1 Dɔ́ɔ Payledɛ áhɔ́bé aá békɛ bébɔm Yesuɛ.  
\v 2 Sə́nze éntēd ngɛn é mechə̌ bélóŋ ekóté éche émbɛ̄ nɛ́ɛ ekóté é kə̂ŋ, béhɛ̄ mɔ́ chɔ́ á nló, béhɛ́-ʼɛ mɔ́ mengombe ḿme méyəgeʼ á yə̌l, ḿmě méwágné mengombe mé kə̂ŋ.  
\v 3 Bésídtéʼáá mɔ́ bɛnbɛn, béhɔ̄bē bán, “A kə̂ŋ e bad bé Israɛl, edúbé ébɛ̂ ne wɛ.” Bébɔ́méʼáá mɔ́ kə́ə́ŋne mebɛ́n.  
\v 4 Payledɛ ambíd á ebwɔ́g ámpē, aláá ábê bad aá, “Nyénɔneʼ, mbídtaad nyé mɔ́ á ebwɔ́g, âbɛl nɛ́n nyébíi bán, meekóbnɛɛ́ mɔ́ awusé ké ahɔ́g.”  
\v 5 Né-ɔɔ́, Yesuɛ ambíd á ebwɔ́g ne ekóté e mechə̌ á nló, megombe ḿmě méyəgeʼ mɔ́-ʼɛ mébɛ́ mɔ́ á yə̌l. Hɛ́ɛ Payledɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “Nyénɔneʼ awedé mod-e nɛ́n!”  
\v 6 Áde beprisɛ bémbáá ne bembəledɛ bé Ndáb-e-Dyǒb bényíné mɔ́, bêmbootéd abón bán, “Bomé mɔ́ á awɔg! Bomé mɔ́ á awɔg!” Payledɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nyé běn nyétêd mɔ́, nyébome mɔ́ á awɔg, áyə̄le meekóbnɛɛ́ mɔ́ awusé ké ahɔ́g.”  
\v 7 Ábê bad bêntimtɛ́n Payledɛ bán, “Sêwóó mbéndé echě ehɔ́be nɛ́n bán atə́ŋgɛ́né awɛ́ áyə̄le ahɔ́bé aá mɔ́díi Mwǎn a Dyǒb.” 
\p  
\v 8 Áde Payledɛ áwógé nɛ́n, mbwɔ́g mênnabé mɔ́ akób.  
\v 9 Antǐm ámbīd á eyáde-tê ámpē, ásɛ̄dēd Yesuɛ aá, “Héé ébídé?” Boŋ Yesuɛ enkênkədɛ́nné mɔ́.  
\v 10 Né-ɔɔ́, Payledɛ anláá mɔ́ aá, “Weéhɛ̄dɛ̄ɛ̄ mɛ akwɛntɛn-ɛ? Weebíiʼɛ́ nɛ́n wɛɛ́ nwóó kunze âhɔ́b mɛɛ́ béchene wɛ, nwóŋ-ʼɛ kunze âhɔ́b mɛɛ́ bébome wɛ á awɔg-ɛ?”  
\v 11 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Weewóoʼɛ́ kunze ké pɔ́g ámīn echêm ésebán Dyǒb ábágé wɛ ene kunze. Né-ɔɔ́, mod awě abagé mɛ áwōŋ mekáá abɛlé mbéb ḿme ńtómtɛ́né achab ámīn.”  
\v 12 Áde Payledɛ áwógé nɛ̂ anhɛ̌d nzii âtɛde Yesuɛ, boŋ ábê bad bénhɛ̄ eʼsaád bán, “Nzé etɛ̌dté anɛ́n mod né weésaá nsón awě Kaisɛɛ. Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě ahɔ́bé aá, mɔ́dē kə̂ŋ né atə̂ŋgan Kaisɛɛ.” 
\p  
\v 13 Áde Payledɛ áwógé nɛ́n, ambídɛ́n Yesuɛ á ebwɔ́g, ádyɛ̄ɛ̄ atii dé nkamlɛn. Ádê hǒm wɛ́ɛ ândyɛɛ́ʼɛ́ béchə́géʼáá dɔ́ bán, Eyáde éche bénábnédé Meláá. Á ehɔ́b é Hibru béchəge bán, Gabata.  
\v 14 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, nɛ́n ábédé á epun é mboŋsɛ́n é Ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn, dyam kəd. Payledɛ anláá ábê bad bé Israɛl aá, “Echɛn kə̂ŋ chɔ̂ nɛ́n!”  
\v 15 Ábê bad bénhɛ̄ eʼsaád bán, “Wúú mɔ́! Wúú mɔ́! Bomé mɔ́ á awɔg!” Hɛ́ɛ Payledɛ ásɛdtɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “Ḿbome echɛn kə̂ŋ á awɔg-ɛ?” Beprisɛ bémbáá bênkwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ bán, “Séewóoʼɛ́ kə̂ŋ empée étōmɛɛ́ Kaisɛɛ.”  
\v 16 Dɔ́ɔ Payledɛ ábágé Yesuɛ áwab mekáá âbome mɔ́ á awɔg. 
\s1 Bébómmé Yesuɛ á awɔg 
\r (Mat 27.32-44; Mak 15.21-32; Luk 23.26-43) 
\p Né-ɔɔ́, bênhidnéd Yesuɛ.  
\v 17 Yesuɛ mwěn ampém ádē awɔg bootya á dyad-tê ákɛ̄ɛ̄n dɔ́ hǒm áde béchəgɛɛ́ bán, “Hǒm dé Ebóŋgɛ́l é Nló,” áde béchəgɛɛ́ á ehɔ́b é Hibru bán Golgota.  
\v 18 Áhed-taá bêmbomɛ́ɛ́ mɔ́ á awɔg. Bêmbomé bad bébɛ bémpēe á awɔg áhed, nhɔ́g pɛd pɔ́g, aníníí-ʼɛ pɛd eníníí, Yesuɛ abɛ́ átîntê. 
\p  
\v 19 Payledɛ antěl á abámbé aá, “Yesuɛ, mod a dyad á Nazarɛt, kə̂ŋ e bad bé Israɛl,” abádé á awɔg á nló-mîn wɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ.  
\v 20 Wɛ́ɛ bêmbomɛ́ɛ́ Yesuɛ á awɔg démbɛ̄ bɛnbɛn ne Jerusalɛm. Né-ɔɔ́, bad híin bénlāŋ chǒm éche bêntenlé. Chǒm éche ântenlé, antel chɔ́ á ehɔ́b é Hibru, átēl é ehɔ́b é Latin, ne é ehɔ́b é Grikia.  
\v 21 Beprisɛ bémbáá bénlāā Payledɛ bán, “Wɛɛ́tēlē wɛɛ́ ‘Kə̂ŋ e bad bé Israɛl,’ těl wɛɛ́, ‘Anɛ́n mod ahɔ́bé aá, mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé kə̂ŋ e bad bé Israɛl.’ ”  
\v 22 Payledɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Chǒm éche ńtélé mmaá atel.” 
\p  
\v 23 Áde sə́nze émáá Yesuɛ abome á awɔg, béntēd éche mbɔ́té, békabtéd chɔ́ áte moŋge méniin, bɔ́ mod tɛ́ atéd akab ahɔ́g. Béntēd kə́ə́ŋne mbɔ́té eche béhágkē áte. Ene mbɔ́té bénkêmbaáʼɛ́ chɔ́ hǒmhǒm. Embɛ́ bootya ámīn âpɛ ásē enkênwóŋgé mbom.  
\v 24 Hɛ́ɛ bélâŋgɛɛ́ nhɔ́g ne aníníí bán, “Syánē deésālē chɔ́. Désid mbambú ânyín mod awě ǎtēd chɔ́.” Nɛ́n dêmbɛnléd âlóned eʼyale ábe éʼténlédé á Kálag e Dyǒb nɛ́n bán, 
\q1 “Běn ne běn bênkǎb échêm mbɔ́té. 
\q1 Bênsǐd-tɛ mbambú âkab ḿmêm nsob.” 
\m Né-ɔɔ́, nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ échê sə́nze êmbɛnlé.  
\v 25 Yesuɛ nyaá, nyaá mwǎnyaŋ, Maria awě abédé Klopasɛ mwaád ne Maria Magdalɛnɛ béntyēēm bɛnbɛn ne á awɔg áde Yesuɛ.  
\v 26 Áde Yesuɛ ányíné nyaá ne mbapɛɛ awě ádə́ə́ bétyéémé áhed, anláá nyaá aá, “Á-nyaŋ, mwǎn wɛ nɛ.”  
\v 27 Hɛ́ɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ ane mbapɛɛ mɔ́mpē aá, “Nyoó ne.” Bootya ene póndé ane mbapɛɛ antéd Yesuɛ nyaá, átīmɛ̄n mɔ́ áwē ndáb. 
\s1 Yesuɛ awédé 
\r (Mat 27.45-56; Mak 15.33-41; Luk 23.44-49) 
\p  
\v 28 Ámbīd e nɛ̂, Yesuɛ annyín aá mekan mésyə̄ə̄l mémáá. Âlóned-tɛ ngáne éténlédé á Kálag e Dyǒb anhɔ́b aá“Píd ekóbé mɛ.”  
\v 29 Kúmbe embɛ́ áhed, ebɛ́ntéd é mǐm énlɔ̄g áwēd-te. Né-ɔɔ́ bêntɔdé kuchá á ebɛ́ntéd é mǐm-tê wɛ̂, bésɔ̄m á ntóŋ ń ngɛn e hísɔb, béhɛ̄ mɔ́ á nsəl.  
\v 30 Áde Yesuɛ ámwédé ebɛ́ntéd é mǐm chê, anhɔ́b aá, “Émáá.” Hɛ́ɛ ámɔ́gé nló, awɛ́-ʼɛ. 
\s1 Bésóó Yesuɛ akoŋ á aheb 
\p  
\v 31 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, échê epun ébédé Mbwɛ mé mboŋsɛ́n mé mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me-áte. Bad bé Israɛl-lɛ béehɛdeʼaá bán ndim ḿbɛ́ ḿbɛ̂ á awɔg á mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me-áte, taŋge ngáne échê epun é nkɔ́me áte étōmtɛ̄nnē edúbé abɛ́. Né-ɔɔ́ béntān Payledɛ bán, ábɛ bɔ́ kunze âbóg bad ábɛ bébómmé á awɔg mekuu ne âhúd bɔ́ á awɔg.  
\v 32 Né-ɔɔ́, échê sə́nze ênkɛ̌ ébóg mekuu ḿme bad ábe bêmbomɛ́ɛ́ bɔ́ɔbɛ Yesuɛ á awɔg. Bénsēbē ḿme nhɔ́g abóg, bébóg-kɛ ḿme aníníí.  
\v 33 Boŋ áde bépédé wɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ béntān nɛ́ɛ ámáá awɛ́. Né-ɔɔ́, bénkêntɔgɛ́nné mɔ́ mekuu abóg.  
\v 34 Ké nɛ̂, sə́nze pɔ́g ensoŋ mɔ́ akoŋ á aheb. Ábwɔ̄g-ábwɔ̄g mekií ne mendíb bémbīd.  
\v 35 Mod awě annyín nɛ́ɛ ḿmɛ́n mekan mébɛ́nlédé, abídé mbóŋ, eche mbóŋ edé-ʼɛ mbále. Abíí nɛ́n aá, mɔ́kaleʼ mbále, ahɔ́be-ʼɛ ḿmɛ́n mam âbɛl nɛ́n nyémpē nyédúbe.  
\v 36 Ḿmɛ́n mam mébɛ́nlédé âlóned eʼyale ábɛ éʼténlédé á Kálag e Dyǒb nɛ́n bán, “Béebógké ehid échē ké ehɔ́g.”  
\v 37 Éténlédé á kálag e Dyǒb ámpē nɛ́n bán, “Bɛ́nɔ̌n ane awě bésóó akoŋ.” 
\s1 Bélímmé Yesuɛ 
\r (Mat 27.57-61; Mak 15.42-47; Luk 23.50-56) 
\p  
\v 38 Ámbīd enɛ̂, Josɛbɛ awě ambíd á dyad á Arimatia, anláá Payledɛ aá, ábɛ mɔ́ kunze âted ndim ḿme Yesuɛ. Josɛbɛ abédɛ́ɛ mbapɛɛ awě Yesuɛ, boŋ énkêmbídédté yə̌l áwed áyə̄le abááʼáá bad bé Israɛl. Payledɛ ambɛ̌ mɔ́ kunze âtéd ndim ḿme Yesuɛ. Né-ɔɔ́, ankɛ̌ Yesuɛ ndim atéd.  
\v 39 Nikodemusɛ awě ansébé Yesuɛ akɛ dé anyín nkuu, bɔ́ Josɛb bênkɛ̌. Bédɛ̂kɛ̌ anwálé mekúle ḿme bénabnadté ndim ḿmé bébɛ́nlé Mía ne Álɔs.\f + \fr 19:39 \fq Álɔs: \ft Abédɛ́ɛ mekúle ḿme bébɛ́nládtáá ânabned ndim.\f* Ádê dyɔ̌g ábédé dyam móom mé kílo meláán ne kílo étáan.  
\v 40 Béntēd ndim ḿme Yesuɛ, békāān mɔ́ mbɔ́m ne ḿme mekúle. Nɛ́n dɔ́ɔ elem é bad bé Israɛl âboŋsɛn ndim émbɛ̄ɛ̄.  
\v 41 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́, nzag embɛ́ wɛ́ɛ bénwūūʼɛ́ Yesuɛ. Soŋ e ekɔ́ɔ́lé ebédé á nzag-tê wɛ̂, echě bénkêmpaá ndim ké nhɔ́g abane áte.  
\v 42 Né-ɔɔ́, ngáne échê epun ebédé mbwɛ mé mboŋsɛ́n mé mbwɛ-mé-nkɔ́me áte, ene soŋ-ʼɛ ebɛ́ bɛnbɛn, bêmbané Yesuɛ ndim áwēd-te. 
\c 20  
\s1 Yesuɛ apuúdé 
\r (Mat 28.1-8; Mak 16.1-8; Luk 24.1-12) 
\p  
\v 1 Á Sɔ̂ndɛ́, epɔg é mbwɛmbwɛ, áde ehíntɛ́n émbɛ̄ɛ̄ ébɛ́, Maria Magdalɛnɛ ankɛ̌ á soŋ wɛ́ɛ bénlīmɛ̄ɛ̄ Yesuɛ. Áde ápédé áhed, antán nɛ́ɛ béhúdé aláá áde bénkɔ̄lɛ̄nnē nsəl ń soŋ.\fig Ndim ḿme Yesuɛ mékɛ̂mbáá á soŋ-tê|src="cn01850C.tif" size="span" ref="20.1" \fig* 
\v 2 Hɛ́ɛ átómé mehélé, boŋ ákɛ atán Simɔn Petro ne mbapɛɛ ampée awě búmɔ̄ bébédé. Ane mbapɛɛ abédɛ́ɛ mbapɛɛ awě Yesuɛ ândəŋgé. Dɔ́ɔ Maria álâŋgɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “Béhúdé Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́ ndim á soŋ-tê, séebíi-ʼáa wɛ́ɛ bébánné mɔ́.”  
\v 3 Dɔ́ɔ Petro bɔ́ ane mbapɛɛ béhídté boŋ békǎg á soŋ.  
\v 4 Bɔ́ moosyəə́l bényə́gtéʼáá, boŋ mbapɛɛ aníníí anyə̌gtéʼáá tómaa Petro. Né-ɔɔ́, ansébé apɛ á soŋ.  
\v 5 Anwúlɛ́n ásē ásad dǐd á soŋ-tê, anyín mbɔ́m éche bênkaánné Yesuɛ, boŋ enkênsɔ́nlé á soŋ-tê.  
\v 6 Simɔnɛ ahúɛ́ʼáá mɔ́ ámbīd, apedé-ʼaá pɛɛ́n asɔ́l-lɛ á soŋ-tê. Antán mbɔ́m éche bênkaánné Yesuɛ áhed.  
\v 7 Antán-nɛ abad áde bênkaánné Yesuɛ nló. Ádê abad déēbédɛɛ́ hǒm ahɔ́g ne mbɔ́m, déndə̄ə̄n áte pɛd pɔ́g.  
\v 8 Hɛ́ɛ aníníí mbapɛɛ awě ansébé apɛ á soŋ mɔ́mpē ásɔ́lé áwēd-te. Annyín ábê bwěm, adúbé-ʼɛ.  
\v 9 Ké nɛ̂, bénkênsóŋtɛ́nné chǒm éche éténlédé á Kálag e Dyǒb nɛ́n bán Yesuɛ atə́ŋgɛ́né apuu.  
\v 10 Ámbīd é nɛ̂, ábê bembapɛɛ bêntǐm ámbīd á ndáb. 
\s1 Yesuɛ alúmté Maria Magdalɛnɛ yə̌l 
\r (Mat 28.9-10; Mak 16.9-11) 
\p  
\v 11 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́ Maria anlyə̌g á nsəl ń soŋ, áchyɛɛ́ʼ. Áde áchyɛɛʼɛ́ nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ áwúnlé ásē, boŋ ásadé dǐd á soŋ-tê.  
\v 12 Asad áde ásádé dǐd, annyín ángɛl ébɛ. Échê ángɛl énhɛ̄ eʼpúpe éʼ mbɔ́té, édyɛ̄ɛ̄ wɛ́ɛ bênnaádté ndim ḿme Yesuɛ. Nhɔ́g andyɛɛ́ á pɛd e nló, aníníí-ʼɛ á pɛd e mekuu.  
\v 13 Échê ángɛl ênsɛdéd Maria bán, “Á-mmwaád, cheé échyɛʼɛ́?” Anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nchyɛʼ áyə̄le bétédé ndim ḿme awem Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́, meebíi-ʼáa wɛ́ɛ bébánné mɔ́.”  
\v 14 Áde ámáá ahɔ́b nɛ̂, ankunnéd, anyín nɛ́ɛ mod átyéémé áhed. Ane mod abédɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ boŋ enkêmbííʼɛ́ aá Yesuɛ mɔ́ adé.  
\v 15 Yesuɛ asɛdéd mɔ́ aá, “Á-mmwaád, cheé échyɛʼɛ́? Nzɛ́ɛ́ éhɛdɛɛ́?” Maria anwémtɛ́n aá mod awě abɛle nsɔ́n á nzag-tê wɛ̂ mɔ́ adé. Né-ɔɔ́, anláá mɔ́ aá, “A-sáŋ, nzé wɛ-ɛɛ́ etédé mɔ́ ndim, eláá mɛ wɛ́ɛ ébánné, âbɛl boŋ ńkɛ ńtêd mɔ́.”  
\v 16 Hɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ áchəgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Á-Maria!” Dɔ́ɔ Maria ákúnné yə̌l áwē boŋ áhɔ́bé á ehɔ́b é Hibru aá, “Rabɔ́ni!” (awě adé nɛ́n bán, “Meléede”).  
\v 17 Yesuɛ anláá mɔ́ aá, “Weésitán mɛ, áyə̄le meétímɛ́ɛ́ ámbīd wɛ́ɛ Titɛ́ɛ. Boŋ kǎg wɛ́ɛ ábêm bembapɛɛ, ábêm baányaŋ, éláa bɔ́ wɛɛ́, ntimeʼ ámbīd wɛ́ɛ echem Sáŋ, awě adé kə́ə́ŋne echɛn Sáŋ. Mɔ́ adé Dyǒb ádêm, abɛ́-ʼɛ ádɛ̄n.”  
\v 18 Né-ɔɔ́, Maria Magdalɛnɛ ankɛ̌, aláá bembapɛɛ aá, mɔ́nyīnē Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́. Anláá-ʼɛ bɔ́ mam mésyə̄ə̄l ḿme áláŋgé mɔ́. 
\s1 Yesuɛ alúmté ábē bembapɛɛ yə̌l 
\r (Mat 28.16-20; Mak 16.14-18; Luk 24.36-49) 
\p  
\v 19 Échê epun é Sɔ̂ndɛ́ chěn, ngukɛ́l, bembapɛɛ ábe Yesuɛ bênladɛ́n áte á ndáb-te bépēn-nɛ ekob áyə̄le bébááʼáá bad bé Israɛl. Yesuɛ ampɛ̌, atyéém átîntê echâb, aláá bɔ́ aá, “Nsaŋ ḿbɛ̂ ne nyé.”  
\v 20 Áde ámáá ahɔ́b nɛ̂, anlúméd bɔ́ ḿmē mekáá, alúméd-tɛ bɔ́ aheb. Bembapɛɛ bébédé menyiŋge bwâmbwam ânyín Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́.  
\v 21 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ bɔ́ ámpē aá, “Nsaŋ ḿbɛ̂ ne nyé. Ngáne Titɛ́ɛ álómé mɛ, melemlem nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ mɛ́mpē ńlómɛɛ́ nyé.”  
\v 22 Áde ámáá ahɔ́b nɛ̂, anhébé bɔ́ pemɛ, aláá-ʼɛ bɔ́ aá, “Nyékob Edəə́dəŋ éche Ésáá.  
\v 23 Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě nyélágsɛ́né mbéb, né ḿme mbéb ńkúdé alagsɛn. Kénzɛ́ɛ́-ʼɛ awě nyéelagsɛ́nɛɛ́ ḿmē mbéb, né méekudɛɛ́ alagsɛn.” 
\s1 Yesuɛ alúmté Tɔmasɛ yə̌l 
\p  
\v 24 Tɔmasɛ mbapɛɛ nhɔ́g átîntê e bembapɛɛ dyôm ne bébɛ ábe Yesuɛ, awě béchə́géʼáá bán Nhɛ́d, enkêmbáá ne baáb áde Yesuɛ ápédé.  
\v 25 Né-ɔɔ́, áde ahúú baáb bénlāā mɔ́ bán, “Sênyíné Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́.” Boŋ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Ésebán ńnyíné mebaŋ ḿme bêmbomɛ́ɛ́ mɔ́ tɔnɛ á mekáá boŋ ńsɔ̄m-mɛ eʼmii á mebaŋ-tê áwed, ḿbīd-tɛ ekáá áwē aheb, méedúbɛ́ɛ́ mbêd.” 
\p  
\v 26 Ámbīd e eʼpun waam, bembapɛɛ bênladɛ́n áte á ndáb-te ámpē. Tɔmasɛ mɔ́mpē ambɛ́ áhed. Bêmpěn eʼkob, boŋ Yesuɛ ampɛ̌, atyéém átîntê echâb. Anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nsaŋ ḿbɛ̂ ne nyé.”  
\v 27 Hɛ́ɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ Tɔmasɛ aá, “Sɔ̌m eʼmii á mebaŋ hɛ́n. Nɔnéʼ mɛ mekáá, éhyɛne-ʼɛ ekáá, ébid mɛ chɔ́ á aheb. Sóg mod abɛ́ awě eedúbpéʼ, dúbé!”  
\v 28 Tɔmasɛ ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “A-Sáá awêm, a-Dyǒb ádêm.”  
\v 29 Yesuɛ anláá mɔ́ aá, “Saá áyə̄le ényíné mɛ dɔ́ɔ édúbpé-yɛ? Nnam ne bad ábe béenyíne boŋ kénɛ̂, bédúbe.” 
\s1 Nzɔm echě ekəə́ boŋ bétéleʼ enɛ́n kálag 
\p  
\v 30 Yesuɛ ambɛ̌l ekud é menyáké émpēe éche ábē bembapɛɛ bémbɛ̄ɛ̄ ásē éche béetelɛɛ́ á kálag-tê wɛ́n.  
\v 31 Boŋ ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l méténlédé âbɛl nɛ́n nyédúbe\f + \fr 20:31 \fq Nyédúbe; \ft doŋge á Kálag dé eʼsó awóó \fq nyébɛ̂ nyédúbe.\f* bán, Yesuɛ mɔ́ adé Ane-awě-Béwɔ́gté, Mwǎn a Dyǒb. Nzé nyêdúbpé-ʼɛ mɔ́, né nyêkudé aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ á dǐn ádē. 
\c 21  
\s1 Yesuɛ alúmté ábē bembapɛɛ yə̌l ámpē 
\p  
\v 1 Ámbīd e ḿmɛ́n mésyə̄ə̄l, anlúméd ábē bembapɛɛ yə̌l ámpē á nkin mé edib é Tiberia. Nyaa echě ánlūmēdtē bɔ́ yə̌l ebédɛ́ɛ nɛ́n,  
\v 2 epun ehɔ́g Simɔn Petro, Tɔmasɛ (awě béchə́géʼáá Nhɛ́d), Nataniɛlɛ (awě ambíd á dyad á Kana á mbwɔ́g e Galilia), bǎn ábe Zɛbɛdiɛ, ne bembapɛɛ ábe Yesuɛ bémpēe bébɛ, bênladɛ́n hǒm ahɔ́g.  
\v 3 Hɛ́ɛ Simɔn Petro álâŋgɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “Nkag súu akób.” Bêntimtɛ́n mɔ́ bán, “Sémpē sɛ́ɛ̄hīd wɛ.” Né-ɔɔ́, bênhidé békɛ bésɔ́l á bɔ̌lɛ-tê. Boŋ ḿmê nkuu ńsyə̄ə̄l bénkênkóbpé chǒmchǒm. 
\p  
\v 4 Áde bǐn éʼbóótédé akɛ́le, Yesuɛ antyéém á nkin mé edib. Boŋ ábê bembapɛɛ bénkêmbííʼɛ́ bán mɔ́ adé.  
\v 5 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ ásɛdtɛɛ́ bɔ́ aá, “A-bɛ̌d, nyéēkōbɛ̄ɛ̄ chǒmchǒm-ɛ?” Bênkwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ bán, “Aáy, séēkōbɛ̄ɛ̄.”  
\v 6 Anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nyébwêm mbínzé á pɛd e ekáá é mbáá é bɔ̌lɛ, nyɛ́ɛ̄kɔ̄b.” Né-ɔɔ́, bémbwēm mbínzé ene pɛd. Bénkênhɛnlé ene mbínzé adol áyə̄le súu émbɛ̄ áwēd-te bwâmbwam.  
\v 7 Dɔ́ɔ mbapɛɛ awě Yesuɛ ândəŋgé áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́ mɔ́ adé!” Awóg áde Simɔn Petro áwógé bán, Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́ mɔ́ adé, anhɛ́ megombe á yə̌l (áyə̄le anhūd bwěm á yə̌l). Dɔ́ɔ áhébé á edíb-te.  
\v 8 Boŋ ábíníí bembapɛɛ bêmpɛ̌ á nkin á bɔ̌lɛ-tê, bédolé mbínzé. Ene mbínzé enlón ne súu. Wɛ́ɛ bémbīdɛ̄nnē bɔ̌lɛ âpɛ á nkin dénkênchabpé, ábédé dyam mbwɔ́kɛl e méta pɔ́g.  
\v 9 Áde bépédé á nkin béntān muú mé mekâŋled. Súu ébédé áwed ámīn ne ewɛle.  
\v 10 Yesuɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nyéhyɛɛneʼ doŋge á súu áde nyékóbé bɔɔb.”  
\v 11 Né-ɔɔ́, Simɔn Petro ansɔ́l á bɔ̌lɛ-tê, âdol ene mbínzé á nkin. Súu émbáá énlōn ene mbínzé áte. Ébédé mbwɔ́kɛl móom métáan ne éláán. Kénɛ́ɛ échê súu êmbuúʼɛ́ áte, ene mbínzé enkênsalɛ́ɛ́.  
\v 12 Yesuɛ anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nyéhyɛ nyédyɛ̂ ndyééd.” Ábê bembapɛɛ bɔ́ modmod enkênchuʼɛ́ mɔ́ asɛded aáken, “Nzɛ́-módɛ́ édíí?” Bémbīī bán, Sáŋgwɛ́ɛ́ mɔ́ adé.  
\v 13 Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ átédé ewɛle boŋ ábagé bɔ́. Ambɛ̌l melemlem ne súu.  
\v 14 Nɛ́n ábédé ngen echě élóntɛ́né éláán, echě Yesuɛ álúmté ábē bembapɛɛ yə̌l á póndé echě ámáá apuu. 
\s1 Yesuɛ asɛ̌dté Petro ké adəə́ mɔ́ 
\p  
\v 15 Áde bémáá ndyééd adyɛ́, Yesuɛ asɛdéd Simɔn Petro aá, “A-Simɔn, mwǎn a Jɔn, edəə́ mɛ tómaa ábén bembapɛɛ-yɛ?” Simɔnɛ ankwɛntɛ́n aá, “Ɛɛ, a-Sáŋ, ebíí wɛɛ́ ndəə́ wɛ.” Yesuɛ anláá mɔ́ aá, “Tɔgɛ́n ábêm bǎn bé ńdyɔŋ ḿ mbód.”  
\v 16 Yesuɛ ansɛdéd mɔ́ ngen éche élóntɛ́né ébɛ aá, “A-Simɔn, mwǎn a Jɔn, edəə́ mɛ-yɛ?” Petro antimtɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Ɛɛ, a-Sáŋ, ebíí wɛ̌ ndəə́ wɛ.” Yesuɛ anláá mɔ́ aá, “Tɔgɛ́n ḿmêm ńdyɔŋ ḿ mbód.”  
\v 17 Yesuɛ asɛdéd mɔ́ ngen échě élóntɛ́né éláán aá, “A-Simɔn, Mwǎn é Jɔn edəə́ mɛ-yɛ?” Yə̌l enhɔ́ɔ́ Petro áte áde Yesuɛ ásɛ́dté mɔ́ ngen échě élóntɛ́né éláán aáken, “Edəə́ mɛ-yɛ?” Né-ɔɔ́, anláá Yesuɛ aá, “A-Sáŋ, ebíí mam mésyə̄ə̄l. Ebíí wɛɛ́ ndəə́ wɛ.” Yesuɛ anláá mɔ́ aá “Tɔgɛ́n ḿmêm ńdyɔŋ ḿ mbód.  
\v 18 Ne mbále, nlâŋge wɛ nɛ́n mɛɛ́, áde ébédé etum, mmǒn epúdéʼáá abad, ékǎg-kɛ kéhéé wɛ́ɛ édə́ə́. Boŋ áde wɛ́chunné wɛ̌sǎd mekáá, mod ampée awáád wɛ abad, ákɛ̄ɛ̄n-nɛ wɛ wɛ́ɛ wéedəəʼɛ́ akɛ.”  
\v 19 (Yesuɛ anhɔ́b nɛ̂ âlúmed nyaa e kwééd echě Petro áwɛ̄ɛ̄, âlúmed ehúmé é Dyǒb.) Ámbīd e nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ álâŋgɛɛ́ mɔ́ aá, “Hídé mɛ.” 
\s1 Yesuɛ ne mbapɛɛ awě ádə́ə́ 
\p  
\v 20 Dɔ́ɔ Petro ánɔ́né ámbīd boŋ ányīnēʼ nɛ́ɛ mbapɛɛ ampée áhídɛɛ́ bɔ́. Ane mbapɛɛ abédɛ́ɛ mbapɛɛ awě Yesuɛ ândəŋgé. Mɔ́ɔ andyɛɛ́ Yesuɛ á akéb á póndé éche bédyágéʼáá ndyééd ngukɛ́l, boŋ ásɛ̄dēd Yesuɛ aá ken, nzɛ́-módɛ́ ǎsōm mɔ́.  
\v 21 Anyín áde Petro ányíné-ʼaá mɔ́, anhɔ́b aá, “A-Sáŋ, chán-náa anɛ́n mod?”  
\v 22 Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Nzé nhɛde mɛɛ́ ábɛ̂ á aloŋgé kə́ə́ŋne póndé echě mɛ́pɛɛ́, chán nɛ̂ ánɔ́né wɛ? Hídé mɛ.”  
\v 23 Né-ɔɔ́, énkanléd átîntê e bad ábe béhídéʼáá Yesuɛ hǒm ásyə̄ə̄l nɛ́n bán ane mbapɛɛ éewáá, kénɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ énkênhɔ́bpé aá, éewáá. Anhɔ́b dásɔ̄ aá, “Nzé nhɛde mɛɛ́ ábɛ̂ á aloŋgé kə́ə́ŋne póndé echě mɛ́pɛɛ́, chán nɛ̂ ánɔ́né wɛ?” 
\p  
\v 24 Ane mbapɛɛ mɔ́ abíde mbóŋ áyə̄l e ḿmɛ́n mekan, mɔ́-ʼaá atelé mɔ́ ásē. Debíí-ʼɛ bán, kéchéé echě áhɔ́bé édé mbále. 
\s1 Asóg á kálag echě Jɔnɛ 
\p  
\v 25 Ekud é mam émpēe édé éche Yesuɛ ábɛ́lé. Nzé bénhɔ̄b bán bételeʼ mésyə̄ə̄l ásē, ahɔ́g ámbīd e ádíníí, nwêmtan mɛɛ́ né nkǒŋsé méekwogké échê kálag ahɛ́ áte.